#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:14
msgid "Wanderer"
msgstr "Vagabundo"

#. [message]: speaker=fence_wanderer
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:22
msgid "Hello, young prince. A lovely day for wandering, isn’t it?"
msgstr "Ola, mozo príncipe. Un día encantador para pasear, non si?"

#. [message]: speaker=fence_wanderer
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:26
msgid ""
"I once wandered my way past a loose board set in the fence between the wood "
"and the bay. I’ve forgotten exactly where, but I’m sure you could find it if "
"you wandered back and forth, back and forth enough times."
msgstr ""
"Unha vez pasei por diante dunha táboa solta colocada na cerca entre o bosque "
"e a baía. Esquecín exactamente onde, pero estou seguro de que poderías "
"atopala se andaches de aquí para alá, de aí para alá, abondo veces."

#. [message]: speaker=fence_wanderer
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:30
msgid ""
"Of course, wandering too far afield could be dangerous. Especially if you "
"don’t already know what’s out there..."
msgstr ""
"Por suposto, afastarse demasiado pode ser perigoso. Sobre todo se aínda non "
"sabes o que hai por aí..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:42
msgid "Hey, look! There’s a loose board in the fence here."
msgstr "Ei, mira! Hai unha táboa solta na cerca aquí."

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:86
msgid ""
"Well done, Konrad! Fresh air at last; we have escaped the smoke and fire."
msgstr "Ben feito, Konrad! Aire fresco por fin; escapamos do fume e do lume."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:90
msgid ""
"But the rest of the elves have not; they’re still trapped in the battle! And "
"look — even our friends at Blackwater Port are being attacked!"
msgstr ""
"Pero o resto dos elfos non o fixeron; aínda están atrapados na batalla! E "
"mirade... mesmo os nosos amigos do Porto de Augas Negras están a ser "
"atacados!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:94
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "With the support of Elensefar and the Aethenwood, it is true that the "
#| "western reaches have suffered less of the dark queen’s tyrrany than have "
#| "the rest of the realm. But it seems now even this has come to an end."
msgid ""
"With the support of Elensefar and the Aethenwood, it is true that the "
"western reaches have suffered less of the dark queen’s tyranny than have the "
"rest of the realm. But it seems now even this has come to an end."
msgstr ""
"Co apoio de Elensefar e do Bosque de Aethenwood, é certo que as terras "
"occidentais sufriron menos da tiranía da raíña escura que o resto do reino. "
"Pero agora semella que mesmo isto chegou ao seu fin."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:98
msgid ""
"Then we must do something! Delfador, we can’t keep running away while others "
"get hurt."
msgstr ""
"Entón temos que facer algo! Delfador, non podemos seguir fuxindo mentres "
"outros resultan feridos."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:102
msgid ""
"You’re quite right, Konrad. I’m afraid there is nothing for it; we shall "
"have to start our campaign against Asheviere sooner than planned. I had "
"hoped to wait until you were older... Hmph, I remember my own master telling "
"me that once."
msgstr ""
"Tes toda a razón, Konrad. Temo que non hai outra opción; teremos que comezar "
"a nosa campaña contra Asheviere antes do previsto. Agardaba poder esperar a "
"que foses máis vello... Hmph, lembro que o meu propio mestre me dixo iso "
"unha vez."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:106
msgid ""
"Don’t worry Delfador, I’m ready. Now come on, let’s go save the kingdom!"
msgstr "Non te preocupes, Delfador, estou listo. Agora imos salvar o reino!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:124
#, fuzzy
msgid "Aethenwood"
msgstr "Bosque do éter"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:134
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Flight of the Elves - 2 season remaining"
msgid "Flight of the Elves - 2 turns remaining"
msgstr "Voo dos Elfos - 2 tempadas restantes"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:135
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Flight of the Elves - 1 season remaining (last chance!)"
msgid "Flight of the Elves - 1 turn remaining (last chance!)"
msgstr "Voo dos Elfos - 1 tempada restante (última oportunidade!)"

#. [message]: race=elf
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:194
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Konrad, our war is lost! We have tried to flee but human forces encircle "
#| "us all around. If you don’t act now, none of us may escape!"
msgid ""
"Konrad, our war is lost! We have tried to flee but human forces encircle us. "
"If you don’t act now, none of us may escape!"
msgstr ""
"Konrad, a nosa guerra está perdida! Tentamos fuxir, pero as forzas humanas "
"rodéannos por todas partes. Se non actúas agora, ningún de nós poderá "
"escapar!"

#. [message]: race=elf
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:203
msgid ""
"I’m glad you have escaped the attack, Konrad, but we cannot! Help us evade "
"the human armies and flee our burning forest!"
msgstr ""
"Alégrome de que escaparas do ataque, Konrad, pero non podemos! Axúdanos a "
"escapar dos exércitos humanos e fuxir do noso bosque en chamas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:224
msgid ""
"The forest is silent. All the elves have perished or else been captured, and "
"the human army has returned to Weldyn... if only I had acted sooner, some of "
"them might still have been saved."
msgstr ""
"O bosque está en silencio. Todos os elfos pereceron ou foron capturados, e o "
"exército humano volveu a Weldyn... se eu actuase antes, algúns deles aínda "
"poderían terse salvado."

#. [message]: role=s02_speaker_1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:250
msgid ""
"Thank you, Konrad! Many of our number have escaped the fires, and the human "
"army has exhausted its supplies and returned to Weldyn. Lord Kalenz was "
"truly wise when he asked us to raise you as our own; he must have known you "
"would someday save us."
msgstr ""
"Grazas, Konrad! Moitos dos nosos escaparon dos incendios e o exército humano "
"esgotou os seus subministros e volveu a Weldyn. Lord Kalenz foi "
"verdadeiramente sabio cando nos pediu que vos criásemos como nosos; debía "
"saber que algún día nos salvaríades."

#. [message]: role=s02_speaker_2
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:254
msgid ""
"Of course, raising Konrad is part of the reason we were attacked in the "
"first place..."
msgstr ""
"Por suposto, criar a Konrad é parte da razón pola que nos atacaron en "
"primeiro lugar..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:262
msgid ""
"The elves have gone into hiding; safely escaped into the southern "
"Aethenwood! May they prosper again once Asheviere is overthrown."
msgstr ""
"Os elfos agocháronse; escaparon a salvo ao sur de Aethenwood! Que prosperen "
"de novo unha vez que Asheviere sexa derrocado."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:272
msgid "Blackwater Port"
msgstr "Puerto de Augas Negras"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:291
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Blackwater Port - 2 seasons remaining"
msgid "Blackwater Port - 2 turns remaining"
msgstr "Puerto Blackwater - faltan 2 tempadas"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:292
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Blackwater Port - 1 season remaining (last chance!)"
msgid "Blackwater Port - 1 turn remaining (last chance!)"
msgstr "Porto de Blackwater - 1 tempada restante (última oportunidade!)"

#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:369
msgid ""
"Konrad, I am hard-pressed by the dark queen’s forces! Without your aid, "
"Blackwater Port shall soon fall to ruin!"
msgstr ""
"Konrad, as forzas da raíña escura me afogan moito! Sen a túa axuda, o Porto "
"de Augas Negras pronto caerá en ruínas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:379
msgid ""
"Konrad, you know Sir Kaylan — one of the mightiest of the horse lords, and "
"one of the few who is willing to oppose the Dark Crown. Rumor has it that "
"his lance has slain fifty men and a hundred orcs."
msgstr ""
"Konrad, coñeces a Sir Kaylan, un dos señores cabaleiros máis poderosos e un "
"dos poucos que está disposto a opoñerse á Coroa Escura. Corre o rumor de que "
"a súa lanza matou cincuenta homes e cen orcos."

#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:383
msgid ""
"Delfador, your timing is impeccable. The dark queen’s forces press me all "
"’round, but with your aid we can rout their attack and re-secure Blackwater "
"Port!"
msgstr ""
"Delfador, o teu tempo é impecable. As forzas da raíña escura presiónanme por "
"todas partes, pero coa túa axuda podemos derrotar o seu ataque e recuperar o "
"porto de Augas Negras!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:417
msgid ""
"Blackwater Port has fallen, and poor Sir Kaylan is either a prisoner or "
"dead. If only I had acted sooner, we might have saved him..."
msgstr ""
"O Porto de Augas Negras caeu, e o pobre Sir Kaylan ou está prisioneiro ou "
"está morto. Se eu actuase antes, poderiamos salvalo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:451
msgid ""
"Alas, poor Sir Kaylan has perished! At least the good people of Blackwater "
"Port are safe."
msgstr ""
"Ai, o pobre Sir Kaylan pereceu! Polo menos a boa xente de Porto de Augas "
"Negras está a salvo."

#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:457
msgid ""
"Gratitude for your aid, young heir! Our port is now open, and what remains "
"of Garard’s Royal Cavalry stands at your service. May they serve you well, "
"as you ride to claim your rightful place on the throne!"
msgstr ""
"Gratitude pola túa axuda, mozo herdeiro! O noso porto xa está aberto, e o "
"que queda da Cabalería Real de Garard está ao teu servizo. Que che sirvan "
"ben mentres cabalgas para reclamar o teu lexítimo lugar no trono!"

#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:465
msgid ""
"Thanks again for your aid, young Konrad! May my horsemen serve you well on "
"your journey."
msgstr ""
"Grazas de novo pola túa axuda, mozo Konrad! Que os meus xinetes che sirvan "
"ben na túa viaxe."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:475
msgid "Bay of Pearls"
msgstr "Baía de Perlas"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:480
msgid "The Bay of Pearls"
msgstr "A Baía das Perlas"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:492
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:435
msgid "Nepba"
msgstr "Nepba"

#. [message]: speaker=Nepba
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:508
msgid ""
"Help! When Asheviere’s army marched west, her orcs and their naga allies "
"overran our homes and took us prisoner! Now we slave away all day, pearl "
"diving for the queen."
msgstr ""
"Axuda! Cando o exército de Asheviere marchou cara ao oeste, os seus orcos e "
"os seus aliados naga invadiron os nosos fogares e fixéronnos prisioneiros! "
"Agora escravizamos todo o día, buscando perlas para a raíña."

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:512
msgid "Shut it, fish!"
msgstr "Cala, peixe!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:525
msgid "Midiriel"
msgstr "Midiriel"

#. [message]: speaker=Midiriel
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:537
msgid ""
"We swim free once more! Thank you Konrad. May our warriors serve you well on "
"your quest."
msgstr ""
"Nadamos libres unha vez máis! Grazas, Konrad. Que os nosos guerreiros che "
"sirvan ben na túa procura."

#. [message]: speaker=Midiriel
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:543
msgid "Thank you again, Konrad! Good luck on your quest."
msgstr "Grazas de novo, Konrad! Moita sorte na túa misión."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:553
msgid "Aldril"
msgstr "Aldril"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:559
msgid "Woodsman"
msgstr "Cortador de madeira"

#. [message]: speaker=aldril_woodsman
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:570
msgid "Don’ mind me. I’m jus’ a woodsman keeping ’is head down."
msgstr "Non me fagas caso. Son só un leñador coa cabeza baixa."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:574
msgid ""
"Asheviere is an evil queen, woodsman. This is a time for action — join me "
"and help fight for liberty and justice!"
msgstr ""
"Asheviere é unha raíña malvada, leñador. É hora de actuar: únete a min e "
"axuda a loitar pola liberdade e a xustiza!"

#. [message]: speaker=aldril_woodsman
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:578
msgid ""
"She’s supposin’ to be the evil one, but here you are asking me to fight and "
"die. Funny, that. If you’ll excuse me, it’s huntin’ season and I have a "
"family to feed."
msgstr ""
"Suponse que é a malvada, pero aquí estás pedíndome que loite e morra. É "
"curioso. Se me desculpas, é tempada de caza e teño unha familia que "
"alimentar."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:585
msgid ""
"Please? They say there’s more magic in one kind word than in all of "
"Delfador’s enchantments put together."
msgstr ""
"Por favor? Din que hai máis maxia nunha palabra amable que en todos os "
"encantamentos de Delfador xuntos."

#. [message]: speaker=aldril_woodsman
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:589
msgid "Get lost."
msgstr "Perderse."

#. [message]: speaker=aldril_woodsman
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:594
msgid ""
"... okay, fine, here’s a few pieces from the town treasury. Go spend ’em on "
"drink or girls or whatever you soldiers do."
msgstr ""
"... vale, ben, aquí tes unhas cantas moedas do tesouro da vila. Vai "
"gastándoas en bebida ou en mozas ou no que sexa que fagades vós, soldados."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:602
msgid "You have gained 8 gold!"
msgstr "Gañaches 8 ouro!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:611
msgid ""
"If the people all banded together, they could easily depose Asheviere and "
"make life better for everyone. But most just keep quietly to themselves... I "
"guess I can’t blame them."
msgstr ""
"Se toda a xente se unise, poderían derrocar facilmente a Asheviere e "
"mellorar a vida de todos. Pero a maioría simplemente manténse á marxe... "
"Supoño que non os podo culpar."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:615
msgid ""
"Maybe that’s what’s so important about being the heir — hope, and a symbol "
"people can rally behind."
msgstr ""
"Quizais iso sexa o importante de ser o herdeiro: a esperanza e un símbolo "
"polo que a xente poida unirse."

#. [event]
#. [side]: type=Arch Mage, id=Seimus
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:626
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/06_The_Isle_of_Alduin.cfg:104
msgid "Isle of Alduin"
msgstr "Illa de Alduin"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:633
msgid "The Isle of Alduin"
msgstr "A Illa de Alduin"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:637
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:551
msgid "<b>-OR-</b> (choose one reward)"
msgstr "<b>-OU-</b> (escoller unha recompensa)"

#. [unit]: id=Elrian, type=Mage
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:645
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/06_The_Isle_of_Alduin.cfg:176
msgid "Elrian"
msgstr "Elrian"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:648
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/06_The_Isle_of_Alduin.cfg:52
msgid "Aenic"
msgstr "Aenic"

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:654
msgid "Where are you taking him? None of them have done anything wrong!"
msgstr "Onde o levas? Ningún deles fixo nada mal!"

#. [message]: speaker=Aenic
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:658
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The queen will be the judge of that. Asheviere doesn’t look kindly on "
#| "treasnous sentiment. Especially not from apprentices!"
msgid ""
"The queen will be the judge of that. Asheviere doesn’t look kindly on "
"treasonous sentiment. Especially not from apprentices!"
msgstr ""
"A raíña será a xuíza diso. Asheviere non ve con bos ollos os sentimentos "
"traidores. Especialmente non de aprendices!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:664
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Delfador has told me much about Alduin; Wesnoth’s great academy of magic. "
#| "It’s controlled by Asheviere now, but is isolated from most of her "
#| "armies. Perhaps we can find allies among the faculty or pupils."
msgid ""
"Delfador has told me much about Alduin; Wesnoth’s great academy of magic. "
"It’s policed by Asheviere now, but is isolated from most of her armies. "
"Perhaps we can find allies among the faculty or pupils."
msgstr ""
"Delfador faloume moito sobre Alduin, a gran academia de maxia de Wesnoth. "
"Agora está controlada por Asheviere, pero está illada da maioría dos seus "
"exércitos. Quizais poidamos atopar aliados entre o profesorado ou os alumnos."

#. [side]: type=Arch Mage, id=Seimus
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:678
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/06_The_Isle_of_Alduin.cfg:97
msgid "Seimus"
msgstr "Seimus"

#. [message]: role=alduin_mage_leader
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:719
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Take care of yourself, Delfador. We will liberate the Isle and finish "
#| "what you and Konrad started!"
msgid ""
"Farewell, Delfador. We will liberate the Isle and finish what you and Konrad "
"started!"
msgstr ""
"Coida de ti, Delfador. Liberaremos a Illa e remataremos o que ti e Konrad "
"comezastes!"

#. [message]: role=alduin_justcompleted_mage
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:731
msgid ""
"Thank you, Konrad! Asheviere won’t forget what happened here today, and "
"neither will we."
msgstr ""
"Grazas, Konrad! Asheviere non esquecerá o que pasou aquí hoxe, e nós "
"tampouco."

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:741
msgid ""
"I know we have no right to ask you for anything more after what you’ve "
"already done for us, but... I’ve been speaking with the others, and not "
"everyone is ready to join your army."
msgstr ""
"Sei que non temos dereito a pedirche nada máis despois de todo o que xa "
"fixeches por nós, pero... estiven falando cos demais, e non todos están "
"preparados para unirse ao teu exército."

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:745
msgid ""
"You’re a soldier, but most of us are just students. And some of us are "
"afraid. Asheviere targets the families of those who oppose her."
msgstr ""
"Ti es un soldado, pero a maioría de nós só somos estudantes. E algúns temos "
"medo. Asheviere apunta ás familias daqueles que se opoñen a ela."

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:747
msgid ""
"Can you find it in your heart to help us one more time, by releasing some of "
"us from our duty to you?"
msgstr ""
"Podes atopar no teu corazón axudarnos unha vez máis, liberando a algúns de "
"nós do noso deber contigo?"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:761
msgid "Dismiss Elrian from your army"
msgstr "Expulsa a Elrian do teu exército"

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:765
msgid ""
"I knew you’d understand. My friends will gladly stay and fight knowing that "
"I’ve left to warn their families. Thank you, and good luck."
msgstr ""
"Sabía co entenderías. Os meus amigos quedarán encantados de loitar sabendo "
"que eu marchei para avisar ás súas familias. Grazas, e boa sorte."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:775
msgid "Dismiss your other Mages (and lose recruitment)"
msgstr "Expulsa aos teus outros Meigos (e perde o recrutamento)"

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:783
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:834
msgid ""
"Thank you for understanding, Konrad. I’ll gladly stay and fight knowing my "
"friends are safe elsewhere."
msgstr ""
"Grazas por comprendelo, Konrad. Quedarei encantado de loitar sabendo cos "
"meus amigos están a salvo noutro lugar."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:795
msgid ""
"Konrad can no longer recruit Mages. Except for Elrian and Seimus, his "
"existing Mages, Red Mages, etc have been dismissed."
msgstr ""
"Konrad xa non pode recrutar Meigos. Agás Elrian e Seimus, os seus Meigos "
"existentes, Meigos Vermellos, etc., foron expulsados."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:802
msgid ""
"Konrad can no longer recruit Mages. Except for Elrian, his existing Mages, "
"Red Mages, etc have been dismissed."
msgstr ""
"Konrad xa non pode recrutar Meigos. Agás Elrian, os seus Meigos existentes, "
"Meigos Vermellos, etc., foron expulsados."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:826
msgid "Dismiss your other Mages (not your White Mages)"
msgstr "Expulsa aos teus outros Meigos (non aos teus Meigos Brancos)"

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:839
msgid ""
"Konrad can no longer advance Mages to Red Mages. Except for Elrian, his "
"existing Mages, Red Mages, etc (not White Mages) have been dismissed."
msgstr ""
"Konrad xa non pode ascender Meigos a Meigos Vermellos. Agás Elrian, os seus "
"Meigos existentes, Meigos Vermellos, etc. (non os Meigos Brancos) foron "
"expulsados."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:857
msgid "Refuse Elrian’s request"
msgstr "Rexeitar a petición de Elrian"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:864
msgid ""
"I came here to help these people, not to force them to die for me. Refusing "
"their request would make me little better than Asheviere."
msgstr ""
"Vin aquí para axudar a esta xente, non para obrigala a morrer por min. "
"Rexeitar a súa petición faríame pouco mellor ca Asheviere."

#. [message]: role=alduin_justcompleted_mage
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:880
msgid ""
"I admit that at first, some of us were unsure about joining your army "
"outright. We’re immensely grateful for your help, but you’re a soldier, and "
"we’re just students."
msgstr ""
"Admito co principio, algúns de nós non estabamos seguros de unirnos ao teu "
"exército directamente. Estamos enormemente agradecidos pola túa axuda, pero "
"ti es un soldado, e nós só somos estudantes."

#. [message]: role=alduin_justcompleted_mage
#. Elrian was another student Mage, who died in the previous scenario.
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:885
msgid ""
"But after what Asheviere’s soldiers did to Elrian? We’d be cowards if we "
"asked you to let us leave now. Let us take revenge against the dark queen."
msgstr ""
"Pero despois do que os soldados de Asheviere lle fixeron a Elrian? Seríamos "
"covardes se che pedísemos marchar agora. Déixanos vingarnos da raíña escura."

#. [message]: role=alduin_mage_leader
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:901
msgid "Good luck, Konrad! The Isle of Alduin stands behind you."
msgstr "Boa sorte, Konrad! A Illa de Alduin está detrás de ti."

#. [message]: role=alduin_mage_leader
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:906
msgid "You’ve caused enough trouble here. Off with you!"
msgstr "Xa causaches abondo de problemas aquí. Fuera de aquí!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:910
msgid ""
"Delfador may have understood these people, but to them I’m just another "
"outlaw..."
msgstr ""
"Delfador pode que entendese a esta xente, pero para eles eu son só outro "
"foraxido..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:922
msgid "Muff Malal’s Peninsula"
msgstr "A Península de Muff Malal"

#. [side]: type=Dark Sorcerer, id=Muff Malal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:931
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/07_Muff_Malals_Peninsula.cfg:42
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/07_Muff_Malals_Peninsula.cfg:49
msgid "Muff Malal"
msgstr "Muff Malal"

#. [message]: speaker=Moremirmu
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:945
msgid ""
"The Light rebukes you, foul necromancer! Flee as you may, you cannot escape "
"my wrath!"
msgstr ""
"A Luz repréndete, necromante vil! Fuxas como poidas, non poderás escapar da "
"miña ira!"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Malal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:949
msgid ""
"Well well, aren’t you a squeaky little toy! I wonder what new noises you’ll "
"make after I kill you and raise your corpse."
msgstr ""
"Pois pois, non es ti un xoguete pequeno e rechamador! Pregúntome que novos "
"ruídos farás despois de que che mate e resucite o teu cadáver."

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Malal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:955
msgid "Can’t you see I’m busy? Stay out of this or you’ll regret it!"
msgstr "Non ves que estou ocupado? Manténte á marxe disto ou arrepentiráste!"

#. [message]: speaker=Moremirmu
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:976
msgid ""
"Lo! We have cleansed a great evil here today, my friend. Together we shall "
"fight onwards against evil!"
msgstr ""
"Velaquí! Hoxe limpamos un gran mal aquí, meu amigo. Xuntos loitaremos contra "
"o mal!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:983
msgid ""
"With Muff Malal defeated, in time this land may heal. We did a good deed "
"here."
msgstr ""
"Con Muff Malal derrotado, co tempo esta terra poderá sanar. Fixemos aquí un "
"bo acto."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1007
msgid "The Three Sisters"
msgstr "As Tres Irmás"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1008
msgid "Elensefar Reef"
msgstr "Rafai de Elensefar"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1068
msgid ""
"I see stormclouds ahead. These boats aren’t built to maneuver in rough "
"weather — if we continue westwards we may have trouble getting back without "
"a fight."
msgstr ""
"Vexo nubes de tormenta máis adiante. Estes barcos non están construídos para "
"manobrar con mal tempo; se continuamos cara ao oeste, pode que teñamos "
"problemas para volver sen loitar."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1077
msgid "Isle of the Damned"
msgstr "Ilha dos Condenados"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1114
msgid ""
"We’re caught in the storm! The wind is blowing us towards that island. Brace!"
msgstr ""
"¡Estamos atrapados na tormenta! O vento está a levarnos cara esa illa. "
"¡Abrigádevos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1125
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Whew, we survived ...but the boats are smashed to bits. Where is this "
#| "place?"
msgid ""
"Whew, we survived... but the boats are smashed to bits. Where is this place?"
msgstr ""
"Uf, sobrevivimos... pero as barcas están feitas pedazos. Onde está este "
"lugar?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1132
msgid "I suppose we may as well explore while we’re marooned."
msgstr "Supoño que tamén podemos explorar mentres estamos abandonados."

#. [unit]: type=Outlaw, id=Delurin, gender=male
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1140
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/08a_Isle_of_the_Damned_part1.cfg:172
msgid "Delurin"
msgstr "Delurin"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1146
msgid ""
"I’m glad I could help make safe your home, but... why choose to live here, "
"of all places? There must be safer hideouts than foggy islands crawling with "
"undead!"
msgstr ""
"Alégrome de poder axudar a facer do teu fogar un lugar seguro, pero... por "
"que elixir vivir aquí, de entre todos os lugares? Debe haber agochos máis "
"seguros que illas brumosas cheas de mortos viventes!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delurin
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1150
msgid ""
"Naw, weren’t always like this. The Three Sisters’ve always been good to us — "
"tough, but fair. These undead be a new thing."
msgstr ""
"Non, non sempre foron así. As Tres Irmás sempre foron boas con nós... duras, "
"pero xustas. Estes mortos viventes son algo novo."

#. [message]: speaker=Delurin
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1154
msgid ""
"There’s some old crypts on the west side of the island, see? Our leader went "
"down, hunting for weapons, treasure, magic and what have ye. But instead of "
"her coming back out, all we got was hordes of the dead."
msgstr ""
"Hai unhas vellas criptas no lado oeste da illa, ves? A nosa líder baixou alí "
"en busca de armas, tesouros, maxia e o que fose. Pero en vez de saír de "
"novo, todo o que recibimos foron hordas de mortos."

#. [message]: speaker=Delurin
#. "If’n" here just means "If"
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1159
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Our leader an’ some o’ her hunters are still down there undergroud, "
#| "trapped — or dead. If’n you can help, we’d all be in yer debt."
msgid ""
"Her and some of her girls are still down there, trapped — or dead. If’n you "
"can help, we’d all be in yer debt."
msgstr ""
"A nosa líder e algúns dos seus cazadores aínda están aí abaixo, atrapados... "
"ou mortos. Se nos puideses axudar, todos estaríamos en débeda contigo."

#. [message]: speaker=Delurin
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1161
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Her and some of her girls are still down there, trapped — or dead. If’n "
#| "you can help, we’d all be in yer debt.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "If not... well, there’s our port. I’ve got some ships to take ye back to "
#| "the mainland. We owe you that much."
msgid ""
"If not... well, there’s our port. I’ve got some ships to take ye back to the "
"mainland. We owe you that much."
msgstr ""
"Ela e algunhas das súas fillas aínda están alí abaixo, atrapadas... ou "
"mortas. Se podes axudar, todos estaríamos en débeda contigo.\n"
"\n"
"Se non... ben, alí está o noso porto. Teño uns barcos para levarte de volta "
"ao continente. Débeseche iso."

#. [scenario]: id=08b_Isle_of_the_Damned_part2
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1175
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/08b_Isle_of_the_Damned_part2.cfg:16
msgid "Isle of the Damned II"
msgstr "Ilha dos Condenados II"

#. [message]: speaker=Delurin
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1193
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Our leader an’ some o’ her hunters are still down there undergroud, "
#| "trapped — or dead. If’n you can help, we’d all be in yer debt."
msgid ""
"Our leader an’ some o’ her hunters are still down there underground, trapped "
"— or dead. If’n you can help, we’d all be in yer debt."
msgstr ""
"A nosa líder e algúns dos seus cazadores aínda están aí abaixo, atrapados... "
"ou mortos. Se nos puideses axudar, todos estaríamos en débeda contigo."

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1211
msgid "... a prince? No kiddin’. Never thought I’d be friends with blue blood."
msgstr ""
"... un príncipe? Non é broma. Nunca pensei que sería amigo de sangue azul."

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1215
msgid ""
"Well. Listen, if you’re fightin’ Asheviere, then me an’ my hunters are with "
"you; we want to help. It’s about time someone did somethin’ ’bout her."
msgstr ""
"Ben. Escoita, se estás loitando contra Asheviere, entón eu e os meus "
"cazadores estamos contigo; queremos axudar. Xa vai sendo hora de que alguén "
"fixese algo con ela."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1217
msgid "Konrad can now recruit Poachers!"
msgstr "Konrad agora pode reclutar furtivos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delurin
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1224
msgid ""
"Thank you again fer how much help you’ve been, Konrad! The Three Sisters’re "
"in your debt, now an’ ferever. Go an’ give Asheviere the thrashing she "
"deserves."
msgstr ""
"Grazas de novo pola axuda que me prestaches, Konrad! As Tres Irmás están en "
"débeda contigo, agora e para sempre. Vai e dálle a Asheviere a malleira que "
"merece."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1234
msgid "Carcyn"
msgstr "Carcyn"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1285
msgid ""
"There is a small port here, but most of the boats have been seized and "
"sailed away! Those that remain are out in the river, filled with soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Hai aquí un pequeno porto, pero a maioría das embarcacións foron incautadas "
"e navegaron mar afora! As que quedan están no río, cheas de soldados."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1289
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1324
msgid ""
"Many of the townsfolk relied on those boats for their livelihood. We have to "
"do something!"
msgstr ""
"Moita xente do pobo dependía deses barcos para o seu sustento. Temos que "
"facer algo!"

#. [message]: role=merman2
#. [message]: role=gryphon1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1298
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1332
msgid "Leave it to us, Your Highness!"
msgstr "Deixa con nós, Vosa Alteza!"

#. [message]: role=merman2
#. [message]: role=gryphon1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1307
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1340
msgid "Now bring the rest of the boats back to port."
msgstr "Agora traede o resto dos barcos de volta a porto."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1320
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1352
msgid ""
"There is a small port here, but most of the ships have been seized and "
"sailed away! Those that remain are out in the river, filled with soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Hai aquí un pequeno porto, pero a maioría dos barcos foron incautados e "
"navegaron mar afóra! Os que quedan están no río, cheos de soldados."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1356
msgid ""
"Many of the townsfolk relied on those boats for their livelihood. We have to "
"do something — and with my magical water-walking sandals, maybe I can."
msgstr ""
"Moita xente do pobo dependía deses barcos para o seu sustento. Temos que "
"facer algo, e coas miñas sandalias máxicas para camiñar pola auga, quizais "
"poida."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1381
msgid ""
"I have chased off the worst of the soldiers, and brought the remaining boats "
"back to port! Doing this by myself was very dangerous and I got very lucky, "
"but I am glad to have taken the risk and helped this town."
msgstr ""
"Espantei os peores soldados e trouxen os barcos restantes de volta a porto! "
"Facer isto eu só foi moi perigoso e tiven moita sorte, pero alégrome de ter "
"asumido o risco e axudar a esta cidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1391
msgid ""
"There is a small port here, but all of the ships have been seized and sailed "
"away! Some hang just out of reach, as if to taunt us. If only I could "
"reclaim them..."
msgstr ""
"Hai un pequeno porto aquí, pero todos os barcos foron incautados e navegaron "
"mar afóra! Algúns colgan xusto fóra do alcance, coma se nos quixesen "
"provocar. Oxalá puidese recuperalos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1416
msgid ""
"There it be — what’s left of Halstead. You woulda been barely a year or two "
"old, Konrad. It were a nasty fight, but in the end we knocked the whole "
"thing down, Baldras and I did. I miss him something fierce."
msgstr ""
"Alí está o que queda de Halstead. Ti terías apenas un ou dous anos, Konrad. "
"Foi unha loita dura, pero ao final Baldras e eu derrubámolo todo. Nósoeño "
"echo moitísimo de menos."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1420
msgid ""
"Baldras was your uncle, is that right? Is he not back with the others on the "
"Three Sisters?"
msgstr ""
"Baldras era o teu tío, non si? Non está de volta cos demais nas Tres Irmás?"

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1424
msgid ""
"No. He an’ some o’ the family went off to try and rescue a bunch of slaves, "
"somewhere out eastways. Do a good deed, an’ maybe make us some new friends "
"too, you know? But it’s been years, and not one of thems that went out has "
"come back."
msgstr ""
"Non. El e algúns membros da familia foron tentar rescatar un grupo de "
"escravos, a algún lugar do leste. Facer unha boa acción, e quizais facernos "
"algúns amigos novos tamén, sabes? Pero pasaron anos, e ningún dos que saíron "
"volveu."

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1428
msgid ""
"Delurin says they’re probably all dead, but I refuse t’ believe it. My uncle "
"Baldras is tougher than that..."
msgstr ""
"Delurin di que probablemente estean todos mortos, pero eu négome a crelo. O "
"meu tío Baldras é máis duro ca iso..."

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1450
msgid ""
"Dallben, my home. Might look like jus’ another ruined town to you, but this "
"place was once full of life an’ adventure!"
msgstr ""
"Dallben, o meu fogar. Pode parecerche outra cidade en ruínas, pero este "
"lugar estivo unha vez cheo de vida e aventuras!"

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1454
msgid ""
"’course everythin’ fell apart come Asheviere. We had to run fer our lives "
"an’ hide, an’ now all’s left is memories. Lotsa stories like ours these days."
msgstr ""
"Claro que todo se derrubou en Asheviere. Tivemos que fuxir polas nosas vidas "
"e agocharnos, e agora todo o que queda son recordos. Moitas historias coma a "
"nosa estes días."

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1458
msgid ""
"Wait a moment, Konrad. I might still be able to scrounge up a li’l gold for "
"us."
msgstr ""
"Espera un momento, Konrad. Quizais aínda poida apañar un pouco de ouro para "
"nós."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1463
msgid "You have gained 25 gold!"
msgstr "Gañaches 25 ouro!"

#. [event]
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1479
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/10_Elensefar_Before.cfg:154
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/10_Elensefar_Before.cfg:175
msgid "Elensefar"
msgstr "Elensefar"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1480
msgid "Halstead"
msgstr "Halstead"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1486
msgid "The Siege of Elensefar - 5 turns remaining"
msgstr "O cerco de Elensefar - 5 quendas restantes"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1494
msgid "The Siege of Elensefar - 4 turns remaining"
msgstr "O cerco de Elensefar - 4 quendas restantes"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1502
msgid "The Siege of Elensefar - 3 turns remaining"
msgstr "O cerco de Elensefar - 3 quendas restantes"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1510
msgid "The Siege of Elensefar - 2 turns remaining"
msgstr "O cerco de Elensefar - 2 quendas restantes"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1518
msgid "The Siege of Elensefar - 1 turn remaining (last chance!)"
msgstr "O cerco de Elensefar - 1 quendas restantes (derradeira oportunidade!)"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1693
msgid ""
"Delfador, I’ve come to Elensefar to help! Together we can fight off the "
"besieging armies!"
msgstr ""
"Delfador, vin a Elensefar para axudar! Xuntos podemos combater os exércitos "
"asediadores!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador {DELFADOR_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1701
msgid ""
"Don’t be daft, Konrad. You must be kept safe! This battle is too dangerous "
"for you — keep your distance and do your good elsewhere."
msgstr ""
"Non sexas parvo, Konrad. Debes manterte a salvo! Esta batalla é demasiado "
"perigosa para ti. Mantén as distancias e fai o teu ben noutro lugar."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1707
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Fighting here is a poor decision, master Konrad. But if you insist on "
#| "joining the battle, Maddock and I can certainly use your help."
msgid ""
"Fighting here is a poor decision, Master Konrad. But if you insist on "
"joining the battle, Maddock and I can certainly use your help."
msgstr ""
"Loitar aquí é unha mala decisión, mestre Konrad. Pero se insiste en unirse á "
"batalla, Maddock e eu precisaremos da súa axuda."

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1744
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/11_Elensefar_After.cfg:18
msgid "The Silver City"
msgstr "A Cidade da Prata"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1748
msgid ""
"Item for Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>full movement and 40% defense on "
"water, swamp, & snow</b></span>"
msgstr ""
"Obxecto para Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>movemento completo e 40% d de "
"defensa en auga, pantano e neve</b></span>"

#. [message]: role=elensefar_orc_leader2
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1805
msgid ""
"Look at all this gold! Tear up the floorboards; don’t let ’em hide a thing."
msgstr ""
"Mirade todo este ouro! Arrancade as táboas do chan; non deixedes que agochen "
"nada."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1809
msgid ""
"Leave Elensefar alone, you villains! Rule under Asheviere would have been "
"bad enough, but orcs?!"
msgstr ""
"Deixade en paz a Elensefar, viláns! O goberno de Asheviere xa tería sido "
"bastante malo, pero orcos?!"

#. [message]: role=elensefar_orc_leader1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1813
msgid ""
"Don’t try anything stupid, wretch. Your queen gave us this place fair and "
"square, and we’re not givin’ it up so easy!"
msgstr ""
"Non intentes nada estúpido, desgraciado. A túa raíña deunos este lugar de "
"boa gana, e non o imos renunciar tan facilmente!"

#. [message]: role=elensefar_orc_leader1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1819
msgid "Get lost, pinkskin! Elensefar is our city now."
msgstr "¡Déixate levar, pel rosa! Elensefar é a nosa cidade agora."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1823
msgid "Not if my sword has anything to say about it!"
msgstr "Non se a miña espada ten algo que dicir ao respecto!"

#. [message]: role=elensefar_completed_thief
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00a_western_wesnoth.cfg:1859
msgid ""
"Thanks again for saving our city, Konrad! Good luck in your fight against "
"the dark queen — for all our sakes."
msgstr ""
"Grazas de novo por salvar a nosa cidade, Konrad! Boa sorte na túa loita "
"contra a raíña escura, polo ben de todos nós."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:10
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:16
msgid "Fort Tahn"
msgstr "Fort Tahn"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Weapon for Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>+3 strikes, <i>slows</i> and "
"<i>arcane</i> specials on bow attacks</b></span>"
msgstr ""
"Arma para Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>+3 golpes, <i>ralentización</i> e "
"especiais <i>arcanos</i> nos ataques con arco</b></span>"

#. [message]: role=fort_tahn_leader1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:40
msgid ""
"Incredible craftsmanship! Just incredible! I’ve never seen a bow like this "
"before in my life! From the Aethenwood, you say?"
msgstr ""
"Artesanía incrible! Simplemente incrible! Nunca vin un arco coma este na "
"miña vida! Do Bosque de Aethen, dis?"

#. [message]: role=fort_tahn_leader2
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:44
msgid ""
"Pulled it out of one of their halls as we was burning it down. When you’ve "
"done testing it, we’re excited to get it back home to Westin along with the "
"rest of our loot."
msgstr ""
"Sacámolo dun dos seus corredores mentres o queimabamos. Cando remates de "
"probalo, estamos emocionados de levalo de volta a casa en Westin xunto co "
"resto do noso botín."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:50
msgid ""
"This archer is holding an Aethenwood Moonbow! It’s a travesty for such a "
"treasure to be even touched by one of Asheviere’s villains, much less "
"pillaged from the ruins of my home! We have to get it back!"
msgstr ""
"Este arqueiro está a suxeitar un Arco Lunar de Aethenwood! É unha aberración "
"que un dos viláns de Asheviere sequera o toque, moito menos que o saquee das "
"ruínas da miña casa! Temos que recuperalo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:70
msgid ""
"Good work, everyone! We have reclaimed a powerful heirloom of the elves, and "
"with the sacking of Fort Tahn we are one step closer to our eventual victory "
"over Asheviere."
msgstr ""
"Bo traballo a todos! Recuperamos unha poderosa reliquia dos elfos e, co "
"saqueo de Forte Tahn, estamos un paso máis preto da nosa vitoria final sobre "
"Asheviere."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:76
msgid ""
"Fort Tahn will rebuild in time, but by driving off the garrison we have "
"dealt a small, yet meaningful blow against Asheviere."
msgstr ""
"O forte Tahn reconstruirase co tempo, pero ao expulsar a guarnición "
"asestámoslle un pequeno pero significativo golpe a Asheviere."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:89
msgid "Dulatus Hills"
msgstr "Colinas Dulatus"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:93
msgid "Merle"
msgstr "Merle"

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:125
msgid "Hullo, stranger. What brings you to these forsaken parts?"
msgstr "Ola, descoñecido. Que te trae a estas terras abandonadas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:129
msgid ""
"I am Konrad, son of Arand and heir to Garard’s throne! I’m on a quest to "
"depose the evil queen Asheviere!"
msgstr ""
"Son Konrad, fillo de Arand e herdeiro ao trono de Garard! Estou nunha misión "
"para derrocar á malvada raíña Asheviere!"

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:133
msgid ""
"Here in the Dulatus, we don’ want no queen. Don’ much want no prince or king "
"neither, though."
msgstr ""
"Aquí no Dulatus, non queremos ningunha raíña. Pero tampouco queremos ningún "
"príncipe nin rei."

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:137
msgid ""
"Once, these hills was rich with gold, an’ granite. King Garard took most o’ "
"it to pay fer his wars, an’ his bride Asheviere took the rest. Now we’ve got "
"nothin’ but empty mines an’ dusty vaults."
msgstr ""
"Noutro tempo, estas montañas eran ricas en ouro e granito. O rei Garard "
"colleu a maior parte para pagar as súas guerras, e a súa noiva Asheviere "
"levou o resto. Agora non temos máis que minas baleiras e bóvedas poeirentas."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:141
msgid ""
"I’m sorry for your misfortunes, friend. Perhaps we can work together for the "
"benefit of us both."
msgstr ""
"Síntoo polas túas desgrazas, amigo. Quizais poidamos traballar xuntos para o "
"beneficio de ambos."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:145
msgid ""
"You have the facilities to store things of value, and we sometimes have more "
"gold and supplies than we wish to carry with us on our march. If you store "
"and guard our excess gold for us now, once I overthrow Asheviere and assume "
"the throne I will be happy to help revitalize the Dulatus."
msgstr ""
"Tendes as instalacións para almacenar obxectos de valor, e ás veces temos "
"máis ouro e provisións das que queremos levar connosco na nosa marcha. Se "
"agora gardades e protexedes o noso ouro excedente, unha vez que derrote a "
"Asheviere e asuma o trono, estarei encantado de axudar a revitalizar Dulatus."

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:149
msgid ""
"Hmm... I suppose we’ve got nothin’ else to do. You’re not worried we’re "
"gonna steal it, or sell ye out to the queen?"
msgstr ""
"Mmm... supoño que non temos nada máis que facer. Non che preocupa que o "
"roubemos ou que te vendamos á raíña?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:153
msgid ""
"You yourself said that you have no love for Asheviere. I am no fool ready to "
"squander my earnings, but I would rather take a risk and make a friend than "
"live my life in distrust."
msgstr ""
"Ti mesmo dixeras que non tes amor por Asheviere. Non son un parvo disposto a "
"malgastar o meu diñeiro, pero prefiro arriscar e facer un amigo a vivir a "
"miña vida desconfiando."

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:157
msgid ""
"Alright, kid. It’s a deal. We’ll hang onto your extra gold, free of charge."
msgstr "Moi ben, rapaz. Trato feito. Conservaremos o teu ouro extra, de balde."

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:166
msgid "Welcome back, prince. What business have you here?"
msgstr "Benvido de novo, príncipe. Que asuntos tes aquí?"

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:178
msgid ""
"So you’s that prince everyone’s so excited about, on his way to fight "
"Asheviere. I don’ want no queen. Don’ much want no prince or king neither, "
"though."
msgstr ""
"Entón, ti es ese príncipe polo que todo o mundo está tan emocionado, camiño "
"de loitar contra Asheviere. Non quero ningunha raíña. Pero tampouco quero "
"ningún príncipe nin rei."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:183
msgid ""
"Konrad, we don’t have time to stop and chat with villagers; especially not "
"ones who scoff at the very idea of royalty. Let’s keep moving."
msgstr ""
"Konrad, non temos tempo para parar e falar cos aldeáns; sobre todo non cos "
"que se burlan da idea da realeza. Sigamos adiante."

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:193
msgid ""
"Hullo again, Konrad! I thought you might have trouble getting back to our "
"old hole in the Dulatus, so me an’ some of the boys set up shop here instead."
msgstr ""
"Ola de novo, Konrad! Pensei que terías problemas para volver ao noso antigo "
"burato no Dulatus, así que algúns dos rapaces e eu instalamos a tenda aquí "
"no seu lugar."

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:201
msgid "Welcome back, prince. Soon I might be calling you “king.”"
msgstr "Benvido de novo, príncipe. Pronto podería chamarte \"rei.\""

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. $bm_merle_stored_gold may be between 0 and 100. $gold may be between 0 and infinity
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:219
msgid ""
"I have $bm_merle_stored_gold gold stored with Merle, and $gold gold in my "
"coffers."
msgstr ""
"Teño $bm_merle_stored_gold ouro gardado con Merle e $gold ouro nos meus "
"cofres."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:224
msgid "Deposit 10 gold"
msgstr "Deposita 10 de ouro"

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:243
msgid ""
"More than one hundred gold? I ain’t comfortable holdin’ onto all that for "
"you, Konrad. I ain’t gonna steal it, but some o’ the boys aren’t so honest "
"as me, an’ these days there’s bandits in th’ countryside too. You carry "
"around the rest o’ yer coin yerself, alright?"
msgstr ""
"Máis de cen ouros? Non me sinto cómodo gardando todo iso para ti, Konrad. "
"Non o vou roubar, pero algúns dos rapaces non son tan honestos coma min, e "
"hoxe en día tamén hai bandidos no campo. Levas ti mesmo o resto da túa "
"moeda, de acordo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:247
msgid ""
"Or, if ye really want, I thinks you’ve got enough money here to hire our "
"whole village into yer army. If that’s the way ye wanted to go, I think most "
"of us’d be willing."
msgstr ""
"Ou, se de verdade queres, creo que tes cartos dabondo aquí para contratar a "
"toda a nosa aldea para o teu exército. Se ese é o camiño que queres seguir, "
"creo que a maioría de nós estaríamos dispostos."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:252
msgid "Hire Merle’s village (lose all stored gold, learn to recruit Ruffians)"
msgstr ""
"Contrata a aldea de Merle (perde todo o ouro almacenado, aprende a recrutar "
"rufiáns)"

#. [message]: speaker=Merle
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:256
msgid ""
"Alright, then, we’re with you. Whether this works out for us or not, at "
"least it’s better than sittin’ around this old town waiting to rot."
msgstr ""
"Moi ben, entón estamos contigo. Tanto se isto nos funciona como se non, polo "
"menos é mellor que estar sentados por aquí, neste pobo vello, esperando a "
"podrecer."

#. [command]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:259
msgid "Konrad can now recruit Ruffians!"
msgstr "Konrad agora pode reclutar matóns!"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:266
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:293
msgid "Leave"
msgstr "Déixao"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:279
msgid "Withdraw 10 gold"
msgstr "Retira 10 de ouro"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:309
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:314
msgid "Gryphon Mountain"
msgstr "Montanha do Grifón"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:335
msgid ""
"I’ve heard stories about the fabled Gryphon Mountain! I would much like a "
"chance to gaze upon the majestic creatures."
msgstr ""
"Xa escoitei historias sobre o lendario Monte Grifón! Gustaríame moito ter a "
"oportunidade de contemplar as maxestosas criaturas."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:361
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/14_Gryphon_Mountain.cfg:169
msgid "Burlin"
msgstr "Burlin"

#. [message]: speaker=Burlin
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:364
msgid ""
"Ah’m glad we could work together on this, kid. You collected the eggs, an’ "
"now I’ll collect my profits!"
msgstr ""
"Alégrome de que puidésemos traballar xuntos nisto, rapaz. Ti recolleches os "
"ovos e agora eu cobrarei os meus beneficios!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:369
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/14_Gryphon_Mountain.cfg:494
msgid ""
"Asheviere’s gold has blinded so many people. It’s how she controls the "
"nobles, the army, the orcs... and it’s why peasants starve to death, their "
"harvest all taken for taxes."
msgstr ""
"O ouro de Asheviere cegou a moita xente. É como controla os nobres, o "
"exército, os orcos... e é a razón pola que os campesiños morren de fame, e "
"as súas colleitas son retiradas para pagar impostos."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:373
msgid ""
"That’s why we have to fight her. Not for my sake, but for the sake of all "
"the peoples suffering under the dark queen’s lash."
msgstr ""
"Por iso temos que loitar contra ela. Non polo meu ben, senón polo ben de "
"todos os pobos que sofren baixo o azoute da raíña escura."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:385
msgid ""
"Gryphon Mountain is at peace once again. I’m glad to see that the matriarch "
"survived, and that her flock is recovering from the fighting..."
msgstr ""
"O Monte Grifón está en paz unha vez máis. Alégrome de ver que a matriarca "
"sobreviviu e que o seu rabaño se está recuperando da loita..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:390
msgid ""
"Gryphon Mountain is at peace once again. If only our fighting hadn’t killed "
"the matriarch and driven away her flock..."
msgstr ""
"O Monte Grifón está en paz unha vez máis. Oxalá as nosas loitas non matasen "
"á matriarca e espantasen o seu rabaño..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:399
msgid "Gryphon Mountain stands silent and empty. We got what we needed."
msgstr ""
"O Monte Grifón permanece silencioso e baleiro. Temos o que necesitabamos."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:416
msgid "Valley of Death"
msgstr "Val da Morte"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:420
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Item for Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>whenever one of Konrad’s living "
#| "soldiers dies,\n"
#| "all others gain regeneration for one turn.</b></span>"
msgid ""
"Item for Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>Regenerate 1 HP each turn. This "
"value doubles\n"
"(2, 4, 8, etc) for each other magic item that Konrad wields.</b></span>"
msgstr ""
"Obxectivo para Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>sempre que un dos soldados "
"vivos de Konrad morra, todos os demais gañan rexeneración durante un turno.</"
"b></span>"

#. [side]: type=Shock Trooper, id=Kaelor
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:427
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/15a_Valley_of_Death_part1.cfg:31
msgid "Brother Kaelor"
msgstr "Irmán Kaelor"

#. [message]: speaker=Kaelor
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:440
msgid ""
"Press forward, brothers! We must vanquish these abominations and summon aid "
"for our brethren, lest they fall to the darkness below!"
msgstr ""
"Adiante, irmáns! Debemos vencer estas abominacións e pedir axuda para os "
"nosos irmáns, para que non caian na escuridade do abaixo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Moremirmu
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:448
msgid ""
"Lo! Konrad, a fellow brother of the order stands in need! Shall we answer "
"the call?"
msgstr ""
"¡Vela! Konrad, un compañeiro irmán da orde necesita axuda! Respondemos á "
"chamada?"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:482
msgid "Valley of Death II"
msgstr "Val da Morte II"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:491
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:552
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/15b_Valley_of_Death_part2.cfg:128
msgid "Sister Myrilell"
msgstr "Irmá Myrilell"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:492
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/15b_Valley_of_Death_part2.cfg:133
msgid "Gwatharry"
msgstr "Gwatharry"

#. [message]: speaker=Myrilell
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:517
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Fear not, Gwatharry, for Brother Kaelor has gone south to fetch help. May "
#| "the light speed him on his journey."
msgid ""
"Fear not, Gwatharry, for Brother Kaelor has gone south to fetch help. May "
"the Light speed him on his journey."
msgstr ""
"Non temas, Gwatharry, porque o irmán Kaelor foi ao sur buscar axuda. Que a "
"luz o axude na súa viaxe."

#. [message]: speaker=Gwatharry
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:521
msgid ""
"And may he return soon. The sacred seal continues to weaken, and undead are "
"starting to slip through..."
msgstr ""
"E que volva pronto. O selo sagrado continúa a debilitarse e os mortos "
"viventes comezan a colarse..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gwatharry
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:526
msgid ""
"The seal is broken! The texts are burned! Yea, the very Light itself has "
"forsaken us..."
msgstr ""
"O selo está roto! Os textos foron queimados! Si, mesmo a propia Luz nos "
"abandonou..."

#. [message]: speaker=Myrilell
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:530
msgid ""
"Doubt not, brother, for our faith is our shield. The warriors have gone for "
"aid, and aid shall soon come."
msgstr ""
"Non o dubides, irmán, porque a nosa fe é o noso escudo. Os guerreiros foron "
"buscar axuda, e a axuda chegará axiña."

#. [message]: speaker=Myrilell
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:538
msgid ""
"Strangers... and do I see Brother Moremirmu among their number? Your are "
"sorely needed, Brother!"
msgstr ""
"Estranxeiros... e vexo ao irmán Moremirmu entre eles? Fai moita falta por "
"ti, irmán!"

#. [message]: speaker=Myrilell
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:543
msgid ""
"Are you the help we have been waiting for, stranger? Your aid would be most "
"welcome."
msgstr ""
"Es ti a axuda que estabamos agardando, estraño? A túa axuda sería moi "
"benvida."

#. [message]: speaker=Myrilell
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:563
msgid ""
"Our home — and all the living of Irdya — are safe thanks to you, righteous "
"prince. May the Lords of Light shine their blessings down upon you as you "
"journey forth on your quest of inheritance."
msgstr ""
"O noso fogar, e todos os vivos de Irdya, están a salvo grazas a ti, príncipe "
"xusto. Que os Señores da Luz iluminen con as súas bendicións mentres viaxas "
"na túa busca da herdanza."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:573
msgid "Grey Wood"
msgstr "Madeira gris"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:578
msgid "Mya"
msgstr "Mya"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:603
msgid ""
"There is a cloaked figure watching me from the edge of the Grey Woods... "
"Hello! Who’s there?"
msgstr ""
"Hai unha figura encapuchada que me observa desde o bordo do Bosque Cinza... "
"Ola! Quen é?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. this is a hint that there's a special event if the player brings Harper here
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:621
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "She’s fled! I’ve no hope of tracking anyone through such an overgrown "
#| "forest."
msgid ""
"She’s fled! I’ve no hope of tracking anyone through such an overgrown "
"forest. We need someone who already knows the way..."
msgstr ""
"Fuxiu! Non teño ningunha esperanza de rastrexar a ninguén nun bosque tan "
"cheo de maleza."

#. [message]: role=grey_woods_explainer
#. this is a hint that there's a special event if the player brings Harper here
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:639
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Konrad, that looked like a Shadow Mage! I heard stories about them from "
#| "Baldras and Harper and some o’ the others. But I never met one. I were "
#| "too young back then."
msgid ""
"Konrad, that looked like a Shadow Mage! I heard stories about them, but I "
"never met one. I were too young back then. Only Baldras and Harper really "
"knew them."
msgstr ""
"Konrad, iso parecía un Mago das Sombras! Oín historias sobre eles a Baldras, "
"Harper e algúns outros. Pero nunca coñecín a ningún. Era demasiado novo "
"naquel entón."

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:660
msgid ""
"Hey, wait! You’re a Shadow Mage! One o’ Helicrom’s. Wait — it’s me, Harper!"
msgstr ""
"Ei, espera! Es un Mago das Sombras! Un dos Helicrom. Espera... son eu, "
"Harper!"

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:664
msgid ""
"Konrad, I’ve told you stories about them Shadow Mages. How they helped "
"Baldras an’ me bring down Halstead?"
msgstr ""
"Konrad, xa che contei historias sobre eses Magos das Sombras. Como axudaron "
"a Baldras e a min a derrocar a Halstead?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mya
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:672
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Little Harper? This is a surprise. You’re marching alongside the prince "
#| "Konrad?"
msgid ""
"Little Harper? This is a surprise. You’re marching alongside Prince Konrad?"
msgstr ""
"Pequena Harper? Isto é unha sorpresa. Marchas xunto ao príncipe Konrad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mya
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:676
msgid ""
"And now you’ve brought him right to our doorstep. Last I remember, you "
"outlaws were helping us destabilize the crown, not fighting to supplant and "
"restore it."
msgstr ""
"E agora trouxéchelo directamente á nosa porta. O último que recordo é que "
"vós, foraxidos, estabades axudándonos a desestabilizar a coroa, non loitando "
"para suplantala e restaurala."

#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:680
msgid ""
"Hey now, it ain’t as bad as all that. Asheviere is the evil one, not Konrad!"
msgstr "Ei, pois non é tan malo como iso. Asheviere é o malvado, non Konrad!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mya
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:684
msgid ""
"Be that as it may, a strong throne is not in the interest of the Grey Woods. "
"I believe Helicrom made that clear when you and he first met."
msgstr ""
"Sexa como for, un trono forte non lles interesa aos Bosques Grises. Creo que "
"Helicrom deixouno claro cando vos coñecestes por primeira vez."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:688
msgid ""
"I understand that you want to be left alone, and I mean you no harm. Harper "
"has vouched for me. Perhaps we can make a deal?"
msgstr ""
"Entendo que queres quedar só, e non teño intención de facerche dano. Harper "
"deu boas referencias de min. Quizais poidamos facer un trato?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:690
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I understand that you want to be left alone, and I mean you no harm. "
#| "Harper has vouched for me. Perhaps we can make a deal?\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Help me overthrow Asheviere now, and once I am king I will ensure that "
#| "none of the crown’s agents interfere with whatever your business is in "
#| "the Grey Woods. Provided that business causes nobody any harm."
msgid ""
"Help me overthrow Asheviere now, and once I am king I will ensure that none "
"of the crown’s agents interfere with whatever your business is in the Grey "
"Woods. Provided that business causes nobody any harm."
msgstr ""
"Entendo que queiras que te deixen en paz e non te quero facer ningún dano. "
"Harper avalou por min. Quizais poidamos chegar a un acordo?\n"
"\n"
"Axúdame a derrocar a Asheviere agora e, unha vez que sexa rei, asegurareime "
"de que ningún dos axentes da coroa interfira en calquera asunto que sexa o "
"teu nos Bosques Grises. Sempre que ese negocio non cause ningún dano a "
"ninguén."

#. [message]: speaker=Mya
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:694
msgid ""
"I have no interest in collaborating with you. But I admit that some of our "
"younger members care rather less about ideals and more about gold. They "
"might be willing to follow you, if you can pay."
msgstr ""
"Non teño ningún interese en colaborar contigo. Pero recoñezo que algúns dos "
"nosos membros máis novos se preocupan menos polos ideais e máis polo ouro. "
"Poderían estar dispostos a seguirte, se podes pagar."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:713
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "100 gold: learn to recruit Rogue Mages."
msgid "80 gold: learn to recruit Rogue Mages."
msgstr "100 de ouro: aprende a recrutar magos rebeldes."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:718
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:284
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:313
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:810
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/22_Glamdrol.cfg:513
msgid "Decline"
msgstr "Declive"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:734
msgid ""
"I would like to agree to your offer, but I don’t have enough gold right now. "
"I’ll return when I can afford to pay."
msgstr ""
"Gustaríame aceptar a túa oferta, pero non teño ouro dabondo agora mesmo. "
"Volverei cando poida pagar."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:747
msgid ""
"I agree to your offer. Thank you for your willingness to work with us — I "
"vow to keep my word."
msgstr ""
"Acepto a súa oferta. Grazas pola súa disposición a traballar con nós. "
"Prometo cumprir a miña palabra."

#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:749
msgid "Konrad can now recruit Rogue Mages!"
msgstr "Konrad agora pode reclutar magos salvaxes!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:761
msgid "Crossroads"
msgstr "Cruce de camiños"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:770
msgid "Crossroads - 5 turns remaining"
msgstr "Cruce de camiños - 5 quendas restantes"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:778
msgid "Crossroads - 4 turns remaining"
msgstr "Cruce de camiños - 4 quendas restantes"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:786
msgid "Crossroads - 3 turns remaining"
msgstr "Cruce de camiños - 3 quendas restantes"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:794
msgid "Crossroads - 2 turns remaining"
msgstr "Cruce de camiños - 2 quendas restantes"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:802
msgid "Crossroads - 1 turn remaining (last chance!)"
msgstr "Encrucillada - 1 quenda restante (derradeira oportunidade!)"

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:842
msgid ""
"Hello, “cousin” — if you really are Konrad and not an imposter. I am Li’sar, "
"princess of Wesnoth and my mother’s most able commander."
msgstr ""
"Ola, «curmán/curmá» — se de verdade es Konrad e non un impostor. Son Li’sar, "
"princesa de Wesnoth e a comandante máis capaz da miña nai."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:846
msgid ""
"I hear you are a man of the people, princeling. Will you rescue these "
"helpless dwarven prisoners before I have them executed?"
msgstr ""
"Din que es un home do pobo, príncipe. Rescatarás estes prisioneiros ananos "
"indefensos antes de que os execute?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:852
msgid ""
"Well, Konrad? Will you fight me, or leave my dwarven prisoners to a gruesome "
"fate?"
msgstr ""
"Pois, Konrad? Loitarás contra min ou deixarás os meus prisioneiros ananos a "
"un destino espantoso?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:863
msgid ""
"The princess Li’sar used to be here with some prisoners, but they have gone "
"now."
msgstr ""
"A princesa Li'sar estaba aquí con algúns prisioneiros, pero agora xa se "
"foron."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:890
msgid "You may have bested me today Konrad, but this isn’t over."
msgstr "Pode que me derrotaras hoxe, Konrad, pero isto non rematou."

#. [message]: speaker=Ulfdain
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:904
msgid ""
"Thank ye again for freein’ me! If I ever get my hands on that cowardly, "
"sniveling, sissy, waste-o-space princess..."
msgstr ""
"Grazas de novo por liberarme! Se algunha vez poño as mans enriba desa "
"princesa covarde, choraminosa, marica e desaproveitadora..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:916
msgid "Tath"
msgstr "Así"

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:955
msgid ""
"Konrad, you’ll remember I told you my family lives in Tath? Well, they’re "
"quite well off, financially speaking."
msgstr ""
"Konrad, lembrarás que che dixen ca miña familia vive en Tath? Ben, teñen "
"bastante diñeiro, por así dicilo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:961
msgid ""
"Konrad, I never got around to telling you this, but my family lives in Tath. "
"And they’re quite well off, financially speaking."
msgstr ""
"Konrad, nunca cheguei a dicircho, pero a miña familia vive en Tath. E teñen "
"bastante diñeiro, por así dicilo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:967
msgid ""
"Give me a moment to reconnect and let them know I’m still alive. Maybe I can "
"convince them to help support our cause."
msgstr ""
"Dáme un momento para reconectar e facerlles saber que sigo vivo. Quizais "
"poida convencelos de apoiar a nosa causa."

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:982
msgid "Great news! My grandparents have agreed to pledge 60 gold to our cause."
msgstr ""
"Boas novas! Os meus avós acordaron achegar 60 moedas de ouro á nosa causa."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:987
msgid ""
"Well done, and my thanks. That’s a great deal of wealth for a single family "
"to contribute. You and they have my gratitude for such a generous gift."
msgstr ""
"Ben feito, e grazas. É unha gran cantidade de riqueza para ca aporte unha "
"soa familia. Ti e eles tedes a miña gratitude por un agasallo tan xeneroso."

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:991
msgid ""
"Err, well, it’s really more of a loan than a gift. To be repaid plus "
"interest once you assume the throne. I had to offer very generous terms — "
"apparently you’re a “high-risk investment.”"
msgstr ""
"Eh, ben, en realidade é máis ben un préstamo ca un agasallo. Haberá que "
"devolvelo con xuros cando subas ao trono. Tiven que ofrecer condicións moi "
"favorables — ao parecer es un “investimento de alto risco”."

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:995
msgid ""
"You can accept the coin now, or wait for a more opportune time. Don’t worry "
"about repayment: that can be dealt with after we defeat the queen."
msgstr ""
"Podes aceptar as moedas agora, ou esperar a un momento máis oportuno. Non te "
"preocupes polo pago: xa nos encargaremos diso despois de derrotar á raíña."

#. [message]: speaker=Elrian
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1002
msgid "Are you ready to make use of my family’s coin?"
msgstr "Estás preparado para facer uso do diñeiro da miña familia?"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1009
msgid "Accept 60 gold from Elrian’s family"
msgstr "Aceptar 60 moedas de ouro da familia de Elrian"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1018
msgid ""
"I accept the gold, and am grateful for it. Their generosity will be repaid "
"in kind once I am king."
msgstr ""
"Acepto o ouro, e agradézoo. A súa xenerosidade será recompensada en igual "
"medida cando sexa rei."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1025
msgid "Not yet"
msgstr "Aínda non."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. referencing the tunnel used by Bazur and Isolde in Asheviere's Dogs
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1040
msgid ""
"Delfador says that there was once a tunnel connecting Tath and Dan’Tonk. "
"During the war it was used to great effect against the city defenders."
msgstr ""
"Delfador di que antes había un túnel que conectaba Tath e Dan’Tonk. Durante "
"a guerra empregouse con gran efecto contra os defensores da cidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1044
msgid ""
"But even if the tunnel still exists, and has not been deliberately collapsed "
"by Asheviere, it is surely too well-guarded for us to attempt to use it."
msgstr ""
"Pero mesmo se o túnel aínda existe e non foi derrubado deliberadamente por "
"Asheviere, seguramente está demasiado ben vixiado para que intentemos usalo."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. referencing the "discipline" scenario of Asheviere's Dogs
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1052
msgid ""
"Tath is a fine town, but not strategically significant enough to be worth "
"fighting over. It never fully recovered from the damage it took during "
"Asheviere’s rise to power."
msgstr ""
"Tath é unha vila estupenda, pero non é o suficientemente importante "
"estratexicamente como para que mereza a pena loitar por ela. Nunca se "
"recuperou totalmente dos danos sufridos durante a ascensión de Asheviere ao "
"poder."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1104
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1114
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1210
msgid "Dan’Tonk"
msgstr "Dan'Tonk"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1130
msgid ""
"Dan’Tonk. Delfador says this is the largest city in Wesnoth, and the source "
"of most of Asheviere’s footmen."
msgstr ""
"Dan’Tonk. Delfador di que esta é a cidade máis grande de Wesnoth e a orixe "
"da maioría dos soldados de Asheviere."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1135
msgid ""
"It was also a staging ground for Asheviere’s invasion of Elensefar. Now that "
"we’ve helped Maddock repel her attack, they’ve begun transporting soldiers "
"and weapons from the front back towards Dan’Tonk."
msgstr ""
"Tamén foi unha zona de concentración para a invasión de Elensefar por parte "
"de Asheviere. Agora que axudamos a Maddock a repeler o seu ataque, comezaron "
"a transportar soldados e armas desde a fronte cara a Dan'Tonk."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1141
msgid ""
"It was also a staging ground for Asheviere’s invasion of Elensefar. Now that "
"she’s taken the city, they’ve begun transporting soldiers and weapons from "
"the front back towards Dan’Tonk."
msgstr ""
"Tamén foi unha plataforma para a invasión de Elensefar por parte de "
"Asheviere. Agora que tomou a cidade, comezaron a transportar soldados e "
"armas desde a fronte cara a Dan'Tonk."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1147
msgid ""
"It’s also the staging ground for Asheviere’s invasion of the west. As her "
"attacks draw to a close, they’ve begun transporting soldiers and weapons "
"from the front back towards Dan’Tonk."
msgstr ""
"Tamén é o punto de partida para a invasión do oeste por parte de Asheviere. "
"A medida que os seus ataques chegan ao seu fin, comezaron a transportar "
"soldados e armas desde a fronte cara a Dan'Tonk."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1152
msgid ""
"Though the city itself is swarming with guards, if we strike fast we may be "
"able to intercept and pilfer some of those inbound sabers, spears, and bows "
"for our own arsenal!"
msgstr ""
"Aínda que a propia cidade está chea de gardas, se golpeamos rápido "
"poderiamos interceptar e espoliar algúns deses sabres, lanzas e arcos que se "
"achegan para o noso propio arsenal!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1158
msgid ""
"A fog has rolled in and several weapon shipments are approaching Dan’Tonk. "
"Everyone, are we ready?"
msgstr ""
"A néboa chegou e varios envíos de armas achéganse a Dan'Tonk. Todos, estamos "
"preparados?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1175
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We have ventured into the heart of Wesnoth, pillaged the queen’s weapons, "
#| "and lived to tell the tale! From the wagons we’ve gathered a large "
#| "collection of sabres, spears, and bows — everything we need to outfit new "
#| "Fencers, Spearmen, and Bowmen!"
msgid ""
"We have ventured into the heart of Wesnoth, pillaged the queen’s weapons, "
"and lived to tell the tale! From the wagons we’ve gathered a large "
"collection of sabers, spears, and bows — everything we need to outfit new "
"Fencers, Spearmen, and Bowmen!"
msgstr ""
"Aventurámonos no corazón de Wesnoth, saqueamos as armas da raíña e "
"sobrevivimos para contalo! Nos carros reunimos unha gran colección de "
"sables, lanzas e arcos: todo o que necesitamos para equipar novos "
"esgrimistas, lanzadeiros e arqueiros!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1177
msgid "Konrad can now recruit Fencers, Spearmen, and Bowmen!"
msgstr "Konrad agora pode reclutar esgrimistas, lanzadores e arqueiros!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1183
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We have ventured into the heart of Wesnoth and escaped — and with more "
#| "weapons than we had before! Although we lack the supplies to outfit and "
#| "promote Bowmen, we’ve pillaged a large collection of sabres and spears "
#| "for our Fencers and Spearmen!"
msgid ""
"We have ventured into the heart of Wesnoth and escaped — and with more "
"weapons than we had before! Although we lack the supplies to outfit and "
"promote Bowmen, we’ve pillaged a large collection of sabers and spears for "
"our Fencers and Spearmen!"
msgstr ""
"Aventurámonos no corazón de Wesnoth e escapamos — e con máis armas das que "
"tiñamos antes! Aínda que nos faltan víveres para equipar e promocionar os "
"arqueiros, saqueamos unha gran colección de sables e lanzas para os nosos "
"espadachíns e lanzas!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1185
msgid "Konrad can now recruit Spearmen and Fencers!"
msgstr "Konrad agora pode reclutar lanzadores e esgrimistas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1191
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We have ventured into the heart of Wesnoth and escaped — and with more "
#| "weapons than we had before! I wish we had managed to pillage more "
#| "caravans, but we’ve at least obtained a large collection of sabres — "
#| "perfect for training Fencers."
msgid ""
"We have ventured into the heart of Wesnoth and escaped — and with more "
"weapons than we had before! I wish we had managed to pillage more caravans, "
"but we’ve at least obtained a large collection of sabers — perfect for "
"training Fencers."
msgstr ""
"Aventurámonos no corazón de Wesnoth e escapamos — e con máis armas das que "
"tiñamos antes! Oxalá puidésemos saquear máis caravanas, pero polo menos "
"obtivemos unha gran colección de sables — perfectos para adestrar "
"esgrimistas."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1193
msgid "Konrad can now recruit Fencers!"
msgstr "Konrad agora pode reclutar esgrimistas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1199
msgid ""
"We have ventured into the heart of Wesnoth and escaped — but without enough "
"pillage to train even a single new soldier type! We shall have to make-do "
"with the weapons and fighters we already have."
msgstr ""
"Aventurámonos no corazón de Wesnoth e escapamos — pero sen saqueo abondo "
"para adestrar nin un só novo tipo de soldado! Teremos que apañarnos coas "
"armas e cos combatentes que xa temos."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1207
msgid ""
"No point going back — the city surroundings are better-fortified now than "
"ever, and we can’t expect the same trick to work twice."
msgstr ""
"Non ten sentido volver atrás: os arredores da cidade están mellor "
"fortificados agora ca nunca, e non podemos esperar que o mesmo truco "
"funcione dúas veces."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1216
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1221
msgid "The Ford of Abez"
msgstr "O Vado de Abez"

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1247
msgid ""
"Crossin’ through Stoneskin ford? Dat’ll be $bm_ford_cost gold for passage, "
"whelp."
msgstr "Cruzar o vao de Pel de Pedra? Custará ouro pola pasaxe, valioso."

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1254
msgid "You know da deal, softskin. Pay up."
msgstr "Xa sabes como vai isto, pelabranda. Paga."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1258
msgid "What!? But I already paid you!"
msgstr "Que!? Pero xa che paguei!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1263
msgid ""
"Fee works every time, both ways. Das why Dosh be givin’ you the membership "
"discount, see? Only $bm_ford_cost gold for repeat customers."
msgstr ""
"A taxa funciona sempre, en ambos os sentidos. Por que che dá o desconto por "
"ser socio, ves? Só ouro de $bm_ford_cost para clientes habituais."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1276
msgid "Pay ($bm_ford_cost gold)"
msgstr "Pagar (ouro de $bm_ford_cost)"

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1284
msgid "You don’t got ’nuff gold, softskin. Come back later."
msgstr "Non tes ouro abondo, pel branda. Volve máis tarde."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1297
msgid ""
"This is practically highway robbery, but we don’t have time to stop and "
"fight. Take your gold and let us through."
msgstr ""
"Isto é practicamente un roubo a man armada, pero non temos tempo para "
"deternos e loitar. Colle o teu ouro e déixanos pasar."

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1313
msgid ""
"Wow. Two-hunnerd fifty gold... you make me richest troll who ever lived! "
"Konrad good troll-friend."
msgstr ""
"Uau. Douscentos cincuenta de ouro... fas de min o troll máis rico que xamais "
"viviu! Konrad, bo amigo troll."

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1317
msgid ""
"Now that Dosh so rich, no point runnin’ ford toll no more. Might as well "
"join Konrad, help you out with throne. We done ’nuff time making friends. "
"Now’s time for smashing bad guys."
msgstr ""
"Agora que Dosh é tan rico, non ten sentido seguir correndo polo peaxe de "
"Ford. Mellor unirse a Konrad, axudarche co trono. Xa pasamos de tempo "
"facendo amigos. Agora é hora de esmagar aos malos."

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1332
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You a good customer, softskin. Das forty gold you done paid me so far."
msgid "You okay in da head, softskin? Das one-hunnerd gold you done paid me."
msgstr ""
"Ti es un bo cliente, pelacúmbrida. Xa me pagaches corenta ouro ata agora."

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1334
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You okay in da head, softskin? Das one-hunnerd gold you done paid me.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Maybe Dosh otta be charging more... fifty gold next time. Only a real "
#| "troll-friend would keep paying."
msgid ""
"Maybe Dosh otta be charging more... fifty gold next time. Only a real troll-"
"friend would keep paying."
msgstr ""
"Estás ben de cabeza, pelamolle? Son cen ouro o que me pagaches. Quizais Dosh "
"debería cobrar máis... cincuenta ouro a próxima vez. Só un verdadeiro amigo "
"troll seguiría pagando."

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1341
msgid ""
"You payin’ Dosh a lot o’ coins, Konrad. My retirement fund got seventy gold "
"in it now!"
msgstr ""
"Estás a pagar a Dosh moitas moedas, Konrad. O meu fondo de xubilación ten "
"agora setenta de ouro!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1347
msgid "You a good customer, softskin. Das forty gold you done paid me so far."
msgstr ""
"Ti es un bo cliente, pelacúmbrida. Xa me pagaches corenta ouro ata agora."

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1353
msgid "Pleasure doin’ business with you."
msgstr "É un pracer facer negocios contigo."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1364
msgid "Refuse"
msgstr "Rexeitar"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1369
msgid "The heir of Wesnoth does not bow to extortion. Have at you, troll!"
msgstr "O herdeiro de Wesnoth non se rende á extorsión. ¡A por ti, trol!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1375
msgid "Paying once was bad enough. I’m taking my gold back!"
msgstr "Pagar unha vez xa era bastante malo. Vou recuperar o meu ouro!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dosh
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1400
msgid ""
"Dosh glad Konrad and he didn’t have to fight. Fighting with Konrad much "
"better than fighting against him!"
msgstr ""
"Dosh alegrouse de que Konrad non tivese que loitar. Loitar con Konrad era "
"moito mellor que loitar contra el!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1417
msgid ""
"We taught those highwaymen a lesson they won’t soon forget. Now the ford is "
"free for all, as it should be."
msgstr ""
"Ensineilles a eses salteadores de estradas unha lección que non esquecerán "
"pronto. Agora o vado é libre para todos, como debe ser."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00b_central_wesnoth.cfg:1423
msgid "The ford is free for all to cross!"
msgstr "O vado está libre para que todos o crucen!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:11
msgid "Glamdrol Fortress"
msgstr "Glamdrol Fortaleza"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:19
msgid "Glamdrol"
msgstr "Glamdrol"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:22
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Item for Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>whenever one of Konrad’s living "
#| "soldiers dies,\n"
#| "all others gain regeneration for one turn.</b></span>"
msgid ""
"Item for Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>whenever one of Konrad’s living "
"allies dies,\n"
"all others gain regeneration for one turn.</b></span>"
msgstr ""
"Obxectivo para Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>sempre que un dos soldados "
"vivos de Konrad morra, todos os demais gañan rexeneración durante un turno.</"
"b></span>"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:70
msgid "We approach the walls of a great orcish fortress. Glamdrol!"
msgstr "Achegámonos ás murallas dunha gran fortaleza orca. Glamdrol!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:74
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Most orcish tribes live a nomadic lifestyle, but Delfador says they take "
#| "great pride in posessing Glamdrol — or in defeating the last posessor."
msgid ""
"Most orcish tribes live as nomads, but Delfador says they take great pride "
"in possessing Glamdrol — or in defeating the last possessor."
msgstr ""
"A maioría das tribos orcas viven un estilo de vida nómade, pero Delfador di "
"que se enorgullecen moito de posuír Glamdrol ou de derrotar o último posesor."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:80
msgid ""
"Orcs often raid Wesnoth’s villages and towns, stealing whatever gold and "
"valuables they can find. Perhaps it’s time we gave them a taste of their own "
"medicine!"
msgstr ""
"Os orcos adoitan saquear as aldeas e vilas de Wesnoth, roubando todo o ouro "
"e os obxectos de valor que poidan atopar. Quizais sexa hora de que lles "
"demos unha proba da súa propia medicina!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:150
msgid ""
"We have ventured into a great stronghold of the orcs and escaped! Now, after "
"paying our agreed-upon $bm_s22_gold_cost gold to our Stoneskin friends, we "
"still have $gold gold remaining for our next battle."
msgstr ""
"Aventurámonos nun gran baluarte dos orcos e escapamos! Agora, despois de "
"pagar o ouro acordado $bm_s22_gold_cost aos nosos amigos de Peleapiedra, "
"aínda nos queda $gold ouro para a nosa próxima batalla."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:155
msgid ""
"We have ventured into a great stronghold of the orcs and escaped! And we "
"have been well-rewarded for it! Even after paying our agreed-upon "
"$bm_s22_gold_cost gold to our Stoneskin friends, we still have $gold gold "
"remaining for our next battle."
msgstr ""
"Aventurámonos nun gran baluarte dos orcos e escapamos! E fomos ben "
"recompensados por iso! Mesmo despois de pagar o ouro acordado "
"$bm_s22_gold_cost aos nosos amigos de Peleapiedra, aínda nos queda $gold "
"ouro para a nosa próxima batalla."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:164
msgid ""
"We have ventured into a great stronghold of the orcs and escaped! Although "
"we only managed to pillage $gold gold for our next battle, at least we have "
"survived."
msgstr ""
"Aventurámonos nun gran baluarte dos orcos e escapamos! Aínda que só "
"conseguimos saquear $gold ouro para a nosa próxima batalla, polo menos "
"sobrevivimos."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:169
msgid ""
"We have ventured into a great stronghold of the orcs and escaped! And we "
"have been well-rewarded for it, for we now have $gold gold stockpiled for "
"our next battle."
msgstr ""
"Aventurámonos nun gran baluarte dos orcos e escapamos! E fomos ben "
"recompensados por iso, pois agora temos $gold gold apilado para a nosa "
"próxima batalla."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:178
msgid ""
"Perhaps most importantly, we defeated the orcs’ shaman and took her magical "
"horn! I shall wear it myself, and blow it whenever its magic is in need."
msgstr ""
"Quizais o máis importante sexa que derrotamos á xamán dos orcos e "
"colleitamos o seu corno máxico! Eu mesmo o levarei posto e soprarei sempre "
"que sexa necesaria a súa maxia."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:183
msgid "Horn of Glamdrol"
msgstr "Corno de Glamdrol"

#. "allies" includes both the player side and allied sides. "living" excludes Delfador's elementals. When one ally dies, other allies gain the "regenerates" ability for one turn.
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:185
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This nondescript horn is infused with powerful orcish magic. Whenever one "
#| "of Konrad’s living soldiers dies, all others gain regeneration for one "
#| "turn."
msgid ""
"This nondescript horn is infused with powerful orcish magic. Whenever one of "
"Konrad’s living allies dies, all others gain regeneration for one turn."
msgstr ""
"Este corno insignificante está impregnado cunha poderosa maxia orca. Cada "
"vez que un dos soldados vivos de Konrad morre, todos os demais gañan "
"rexeneración durante un turno."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:192
msgid ""
"If only we had been able to defeat the orcs’ shaman and claim her magical "
"horn..."
msgstr ""
"Oxalá puidésemos derrotar á xamán dos orcos e reclamar o seu corno máxico..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:205
msgid ""
"With the original orcish owners wiped out, our friends in the Stoneskin clan "
"now hold the city."
msgstr ""
"Coa aniquilación dos propietarios orcos orixinais, os nosos amigos do clan "
"Stoneskin agora controlan a cidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:210
msgid "Glamdrol has been wiped clean of orcs!"
msgstr "Limpamos de orcos Glamdrol!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:216
msgid ""
"We’d best keep our distance. The orcs will be watching for any more raids!"
msgstr ""
"É mellor que manteñamos a distancia. Os orcos estarán vixiantes ante "
"calquera nova incursión!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:233
msgid "Jotha"
msgstr "Jotha"

#. [message]: speaker=Jotha
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:251
msgid ""
"What do you want? You here to trade? Jotha’s got nothin’ to trade but some "
"old fish."
msgstr ""
"Que queres? Estás aquí para comerciar? Jotha non ten nada que intercambiar, "
"só algúns peixes vellos."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:255
msgid ""
"Is this your home, strange merman? The bay is warm, but fishing alone so far "
"north must make for a lonely life."
msgstr ""
"É esta a túa casa, estraño home sereíno? A baía é cálida, pero pescar só tan "
"ao norte debe ser unha vida solitaria."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:269
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Let me make you an offer. Come join my army, and fight for a righeous "
#| "cause instead of slaving away as a trawler! We already have merfolk among "
#| "our number — you’ll feel right at home."
msgid ""
"Let me make you an offer. Come join my army, and fight for a righteous cause "
"instead of slaving away as a trawler! We already have merfolk among our "
"number — you’ll feel right at home."
msgstr ""
"Deixa que che faga unha oferta. Únete ao meu exército e loita por unha causa "
"xusta en vez de traballar como escravo nun barco de arrastre! Xa temos "
"sereas entre nós; sentiráste como na casa."

#. [message]: speaker=Jotha
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:273
msgid ""
"Other merfolk, you say? Hmm... I’ll give you a discount for that, but I "
"still ain’t working fer free. 10 gold and I’ll join you, and you’ll still "
"have to pay to recall me each battle."
msgstr ""
"Outras sereas, dis? Mmm... Dareiche un desconto por iso, pero aínda así non "
"traballo de balde. 10 de ouro e uniréime a ti, e aínda terás que pagar para "
"chamarme en cada batalla."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:278
msgid "Pay 10 gold"
msgstr "Paga 10 ouro"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:298
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Let me make you an offer. Come join my army, and fight for a righeous "
#| "cause instead of slaving away as a trawler! I would be glad to welcome "
#| "one of the noble mermen to our ranks."
msgid ""
"Let me make you an offer. Come join my army, and fight for a righteous cause "
"instead of slaving away as a trawler! I would be glad to welcome one of the "
"noble mermen to our ranks."
msgstr ""
"Déixame facerche unha oferta. Únete ao meu exército e loita por unha causa "
"xusta en vez de escravizar como pescador de arrastre! Encantaríame dar a "
"benvida a un dos nobres sereínos ás nosas filas."

#. [message]: speaker=Jotha
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:302
msgid ""
"Join your army, you say? Hmm... I wouldn’t mind getting out o’ this pond, "
"but I still ain’t working fer free. 30 gold and I’ll join you, and you’ll "
"still have to pay to recall me each battle."
msgstr ""
"Únete ao teu exército, dis? Mmm... Non me importaría saír desta lagoa, pero "
"aínda así non traballo de balde. 30 de ouro e uniréime a ti, e aínda terás "
"que pagar para chamarme en cada batalla."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:307
msgid "Pay 30 gold."
msgstr "Paga 30 ouro."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:328
msgid ""
"I would like to agree to your offer, but I don’t have enough gold right now. "
"Would you consider lowering your price?"
msgstr ""
"Gustaríame aceptar a túa oferta, pero non teño ouro dabondo agora mesmo. "
"Considerarías baixar o prezo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Jotha
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:332
msgid "No gold, no Jotha. Now go away and stop bothering me."
msgstr "Sen ouro, sen Jotha. Agora vai e deixa de molestarme."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:348
msgid ""
"Welcome to the rebellion against Asheviere, friend merman. I am glad to have "
"you on our side."
msgstr ""
"Benvido á rebelión contra Asheviere, amigo sirenio. Alégrome de terche do "
"noso lado."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:361
msgid "Ashen’s Maw"
msgstr "A Boca de Ashen"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:370
msgid "Northern Spring"
msgstr "Primavera do Norte"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:371
msgid "Northern Summer"
msgstr "Verán do norte"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:372
msgid "Northern Autumn"
msgstr "Outono do Norte"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:373
msgid "Northern Winter"
msgstr "Inverno do Norte"

#. [message]: speaker=Jeniver
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:400
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "... three parts essense of bark, one part yeti tongue..."
msgid "... three parts essence of bark, one part yeti tongue..."
msgstr "... tres partes de esencia de cortiza, unha parte de lingua de yeti..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:404
msgid ""
"Hello, strange woman! What are you doing alone so far north? And in the "
"middle of a blizzard too!"
msgstr ""
"Ola, muller estraña! Que fas soa tan lonxe ao norte? E no medio dunha "
"nevada, ademais!"

#. [message]: speaker=Jeniver
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:408
msgid "... a distillation of fire, elixir of the right-eye..."
msgstr "... unha destilación de lume, elixir do ollo dereito..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:412
msgid ""
"Hello? Hello!? ...she’s very engrossed in something, and still hasn’t "
"noticed us."
msgstr "Ola? Ola!? ...está moi absorta en algo e aínda non se decatou de nós."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:419
msgid ""
"The Northlands are a dangerous place to be wandering alone, especially in "
"the center of such a fierce snowstorm, and <b><i>especially</i></b> in the "
"middle of winter. We should speak to this woman and see if she needs any "
"help."
msgstr ""
"As Terras do Norte son un lugar perigoso para vagar só, especialmente no "
"medio dunha tormenta de neve tan forte, e <b><i>sobre todo</i></b> en pleno "
"inverno. Deberíamos falar con esta muller e ver se precisa axuda."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:424
msgid ""
"The Northlands are a dangerous place to be wandering alone, especially in "
"the center of such a fierce snowstorm. We should speak to this woman and see "
"if she needs any help."
msgstr ""
"As Terras do Norte son un lugar perigoso para vagar só, especialmente no "
"medio dunha tormenta de neve tan forte. Deberíamos falar con esta muller e "
"ver se precisa axuda."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:456
msgid "Wesmere Forest"
msgstr "Bosque de Wesmere"

#. [message]: role=wesmere_guard {FILTER_ADJACENT id=Konrad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:487
msgid ""
"By order of the lady Chantal, Wesmere forest is closed to outsiders. Be off "
"with you."
msgstr ""
"Por orde de Lady Chantal, o bosque de Wesmere está pechado aos forasteiros. "
"Vaite contigo."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:491
msgid ""
"Good elf, I am Konrad, heir to the throne of Wesnoth, child of the "
"Aethenwood and ally of Wesmere. I am no outsider, but come as a friend!"
msgstr ""
"Bo elfo, son Konrad, herdeiro ao trono de Wesnoth, fillo do Bosque de Aethen "
"e aliado de Wesmere. Non son un forasteiro, pero veño como un amigo!"

#. [message]: role=wesmere_guard {FILTER_ADJACENT id=Konrad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:495
msgid ""
"Apologies, but I have my orders. None can enter here. Even you, Your Royal "
"Highness."
msgstr ""
"Desculpas, pero teño as miñas ordes. Ninguén pode entrar aquí. Nin sequera "
"vostede, Alteza Real."

#. [message]: role=wesmere_guard {FILTER_ADJACENT id=Konrad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:500
msgid ""
"By order of the lady Chantal, Wesmere forest is closed to outsiders. Even "
"you, Your Royal Highness."
msgstr ""
"Por orde de Lady Chantal, o bosque de Wesmere está pechado aos forasteiros. "
"Mesmo a vostede, Alteza Real."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:511
msgid "Even me, guard of Wesmere?"
msgstr "Eu mesmo, garda de Wesmere?"

#. [message]: role=wesmere_guard {FILTER_ADJACENT id=Konrad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:515
msgid "High Lord Kalenz! Speaking to me!?"
msgstr "Alto Señor Kalenz! Falándome!?"

#. [message]: role=wesmere_guard {FILTER_ADJACENT id=Konrad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:519
msgid ""
"Err, well, I was told not to let anyone in... but surely you and any "
"companions of yours are an exception. Go on, and speak to your granddaughter."
msgstr ""
"Eh, ben, dixéronme que non deixase entrar a ninguén... pero seguramente ti e "
"calquera dos teus acompañantes sodes unha excepción. Vai e fala coa túa neta."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:526
msgid "How strange..."
msgstr "Que estraño..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:547
msgid "An Old Friend"
msgstr "Un vello amigo"

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:565
msgid "Great-grandfather?! What is the meaning of this?"
msgstr "Bisavó?! Que significa isto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:569
msgid ""
"What is the meaning of this, indeed. The borders of Wesmere closed, even to "
"Konrad and his retinue? What sort of trouble ails you, Chantal?"
msgstr ""
"Que significa isto, de feito. As fronteiras de Wesmere pecháronse, mesmo "
"para Konrad e a súa comitiva? Que clase de problema che aflige, Chantal?"

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:573
msgid ""
"An old friend has returned, Kalenz.... I had hoped to put off this "
"confrontation, but I know it is for the best that you are here, and that my "
"hand is forced."
msgstr ""
"Un vello amigo volveu, Kalenz... Tiña a esperanza de adiar este "
"enfrontamento, pero sei que o mellor é que esteas aquí e que me obrigan a "
"facelo."

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:580
msgid ""
"This is a matter of a personal nature, Konrad. If you do not object, I would "
"prefer if Kalenz and I did this alone."
msgstr ""
"Isto é un asunto de carácter persoal, Konrad. Se non tes obxeccións, "
"preferiría que Kalenz e eu o fixésemos sós."

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:594
msgid ""
"This is a matter of a personal nature, Konrad. Kalenz is not here, and I "
"would rather handle things myself."
msgstr ""
"Isto é un asunto de carácter persoal, Konrad. Kalenz non está aquí, e "
"preferiría ocuparme eu mesmo."

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:615
msgid ""
"Thank you for your patience, Konrad. Kalenz and I are finished with our task."
msgstr ""
"Grazas pola túa paciencia, Konrad. Kalenz e eu rematamos coa nosa tarefa."

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:619
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "As my heart begins to heal, so shall we elves help to heal your army. "
#| "Though most of us must stay here to protect our domain, the shamans of "
#| "Wesmere are ready to follow you.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Or, if you wish, I can personally accompany you on your quest to "
#| "overthrow the dark queen."
msgid ""
"As my heart begins to heal, so shall we elves help to heal your army. Though "
"most of us must stay here to protect our domain, the shamans of Wesmere are "
"ready to follow you."
msgstr ""
"A medida que o meu corazón comece a curarse, nós, os elfos, axudaremos a "
"curar o teu exército. Aínda que a maioría de nós debe quedar aquí para "
"protexer o noso dominio, os xamáns de Wesmere están listos para seguirte.\n"
"\n"
"Ou, se o desexas, podo acompañarte persoalmente na túa misión para derrocar "
"á raíña escura."

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:621
msgid ""
"Or, if you wish, I can personally accompany you on your quest to overthrow "
"the dark queen."
msgstr ""
"Ou, se o desexas, podo acompañarte persoalmente na túa misión de destronar á "
"raíña escura."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:626
msgid "Learn to recruit Elvish Shamans"
msgstr "Aprende a reclutar chamanes elficos"

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:630
msgid ""
"I am glad we can help you, Konrad, for the dark queen has many deaths to "
"answer for. Asheviere will rue the day she made an enemy of the elves."
msgstr ""
"Alégrome de que poidamos axudarte, Konrad, porque a raíña escura ten que "
"responder por moitas mortes. Asheviere arrepentiráse do día en que se "
"converteu nun inimigo dos elfos."

#. [command]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:632
msgid "Konrad can now recruit Elvish Shamans!"
msgstr "Konrad agora pode reclutar chamanes elficos!"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:636
msgid "Gain Chantal as a loyal companion"
msgstr "Gaña a Chantal como compañeira leal"

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:640
msgid ""
"I am glad to join you on your quest, Konrad, for the dark queen has many "
"deaths to answer for. Asheviere will rue the day she made an enemy of the "
"elves."
msgstr ""
"Alégrome de unirme a ti na túa misión, Konrad, porque a raíña escura ten que "
"responder por moitas mortes. Asheviere arrepentiráse do día en que se "
"converteu nun inimigo dos elfos."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:669
msgid ""
"I would like to agree to your offer, but I don’t have enough gold! Perhaps "
"another time, lizard."
msgstr ""
"Gustaríame aceptar a túa oferta, pero non teño ouro dabondo! Quizais noutra "
"ocasión, lagarto."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:700
msgid ""
"Whew! This has been grueling, but I feel as light on my feet as a fencer. I "
"am grateful for your tutelage, Tirix."
msgstr ""
"Uf! Isto foi esgotador, pero síntome lixeiro nos pés coma un esgrimista. "
"Estou agradecido pola túa tutela, Tirix."

#. [object]: id=saurian_training, description={DESC}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:706
msgid "Saurian Footwork"
msgstr "Paso de saurio"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:720
msgid "Tirix"
msgstr "Tirix"

#. [message]: speaker=Tirix
#. Slow, slow! It is disgusting how all you tall ones are so slow!
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:740
msgid ""
"Ssslow, ssslow! It isss disssgusssting how you tall onesss are all ssso "
"ssslow!"
msgstr "Lento, lento! É repugnante o lentos que sodes, todos altos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:744
msgid ""
"What do you mean, lizard? Both my legs and my sword-arm are perfectly quick "
"— as you will soon find out if you wish me any ill-intent."
msgstr ""
"Que queres dicir, lagartixa? Tanto as miñas pernas como o meu brazo de "
"espada son perfectamente rápidos — como pronto descubrirás se me desexas "
"algún mal."

#. [message]: speaker=Tirix
#. Psssh... I know your kind; tall, and clumsy. Tirix can teach you speed... yes, speed... But only if you pay. It shall not be cheap.
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:749
msgid ""
"Psssh... I know your kind; tall, and clumsssy. Tirix can teach you "
"ssspeed... yesss, ssspeed... But only if you pay. It ssshall not be cheap."
msgstr ""
"Pssh... Coñezo a vosa especie; altos e torpes. Tirix pode ensinarvos "
"velocidade... si, velocidade... Pero só se pagas. Non será barato."

#. [message]: speaker=Tirix
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:754
msgid "Have you returned to learn the waysss of ssspeed, human?"
msgstr "Volviste para aprender os camiños da velocidade, humano?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:768
msgid ""
"You are kind to offer, but I am hurrying north to meet with my mentor, and "
"have no time to spare for lengthy training. Perhaps we will meet again "
"another day."
msgstr ""
"Es amable por ofrecérmo, pero estou a présa cara ao norte para reunirme co "
"meu mentor e non teño tempo para un adestramento prolongado. Quizais nos "
"vexamos outro día."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:778
msgid "50 gold; physical training: <b>Konrad gains +1MP</b>"
msgstr "50 de ouro; adestramento físico: <b>Konrad gaña +1 de PM</b>"

#. [command]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:781
msgid ""
"After rigorous physical training with the saurians of the Swamp of Dread, "
"Konrad has gained <b>+1MP</b>."
msgstr ""
"Tras un rigoroso adestramento físico cos saurios do Pantano do Terror, "
"Konrad gañou <b>+1 PM</b> ."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:787
msgid "100 gold; magical training: <b>Konrad gains +2MP</b>"
msgstr "100 de ouro; adestramento máxico: <b>Konrad gaña +2 MP</b>"

#. [command]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:790
msgid ""
"After rigorous physical and magical training with the saurians of the Swamp "
"of Dread, Konrad has gained <b>+2MP</b>."
msgstr ""
"Tras un rigoroso adestramento físico e máxico cos saurios do Pantano do "
"Terror, Konrad gañou <b>+2 PM</b> ."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:797
msgid ""
"150 gold; legendary training: <b>Konrad gains +2MP and <i>skirmisher</i></b>"
msgstr ""
"150 de ouro; adestramento lendario: <b>Konrad gaña +2 de PM e "
"<i>escaramuzador</i></b>"

#. [command]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:800
msgid ""
"After rigorous physical and magical training with the saurians of the Swamp "
"of Dread, Konrad has gained <b>+2MP</b> and the <b><i>skirmisher</i></b> "
"ability."
msgstr ""
"Tras un rigoroso adestramento físico e máxico cos saurios do Pantano do "
"Terror, Konrad gañou <b>+2 PM</b> e a habilidade <b><i>de escaramuzador</i></"
"b> ."

#. [message]: speaker=Tirix
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:823
msgid ""
"Good, good, much better. Not so ssslow any more! I have no time or "
"interessst in more training."
msgstr ""
"Ben, ben, moito mellor. Xa non tan lento! Non teño tempo nin interese en "
"adestrar máis."

#. [message]: speaker={KONRAD_OR_NOBODY}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:840
msgid ""
"What happened here was such a tragedy... do you know anything more than I "
"do, Ulfdain?"
msgstr ""
"O que pasou aquí foi unha auténtica traxedia... sabes algo máis ca min, "
"Ulfdain?"

#. [message]: speaker=Ulfdain
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:844
msgid ""
"Aye... ’twas a time of doom an’ great deeds, o’ fire an’ blood an’ "
"slaughter. My father an’ his father alike perished defendin’ th’ West Gate, "
"an’ soon after fell the Doors, an’ our King Thunedain with them."
msgstr ""
"Si... foi un tempo de desgraza e grandes fazañas, de lume, sangue e matanza. "
"Meu pai e o seu pai pereceron defendendo a Porta Oeste, e pouco despois "
"caeron as Portas, e o noso Rei Thunedain con eles."

#. [message]: speaker=Ulfdain
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:848
msgid ""
"The better part o’ our spirit died in those years. E’er since, us dwarves’ve "
"been a people in decline, sniveling in our tunnels, th’ dyin’ dregs of a "
"once-proud people. Or betrayin’ their kin to start anew in human lands, like "
"me..."
msgstr ""
"A maior parte do noso espírito morreu neses anos. Desde entón, nós, os "
"ananos, fomos un pobo en decadencia, choramingando nos nosos túneles, os "
"restos moribundos dun pobo que antes era orgulloso. Ou traizoando á súa "
"xente para comezar de novo en terras humanas, coma min..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:852
msgid ""
"I’ve never-before heard you speak so grimly, Ulfdain. I’m sorry for your "
"loss. Is there nothing we can do to restore Knalga to its former glory?"
msgstr ""
"Nunca antes te oín falar con tanta severidade, Ulfdain. Síntoo pola túa "
"perda. Non hai nada que poidamos facer para devolverlle a Knalga a súa "
"antiga gloria?"

#. [message]: speaker=Ulfdain
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:856
msgid ""
"Not lest ye’ can fight off all the orcs o’ the north, an’ trolls an’ undead "
"besides. No, there ain’t no use cryin’ over it. Ah’ve given up hope; it’s "
"only death in battle tha’ I wish fer now..."
msgstr ""
"Non para que non poidades loitar contra todos os orcos do norte, e tamén "
"contra os troles e os mortos viventes. Non, non ten sentido chorar por iso. "
"Perdin a esperanza; só desexo a morte na batalla agora..."

#. [message]: speaker={KONRAD_OR_NOBODY}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:871
msgid ""
"What happened here was such a tragedy... is there nothing we can do to "
"restore Knalga to its former glory? Do you know anything more than I do, my "
"dwarvish friend?"
msgstr ""
"O que pasou aquí foi unha auténtica traxedia... non hai nada que poidamos "
"facer para restaurar Knalga ao seu antigo esplendor? Sabes algo máis ca min, "
"amigo anano?"

#. [message]: speaker=$dwarf_id
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:875
msgid ""
"Aye, but ’tis not a time we dwarves like to talk about. The West Gate "
"fallen, the Dwarven Doors sacked..."
msgstr ""
"Si, pero non é un momento do que aos ananos nos guste falar. A Porta Oeste "
"caída, as Portas dos Ananos saqueadas..."

#. [message]: speaker=$dwarf_id
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:879
msgid ""
"No, there ain’t nothin’ ye can do, not unless ye’ can fight off all the orcs "
"o’ the north, an’ trolls an’ undead besides. Us dwarves’re doomed to be a "
"people in decline, sniveling in our tunnels, th’ dyin’ dregs of a once-proud "
"people..."
msgstr ""
"Non, non hai nada que poidades facer, a non ser que poidades loitar contra "
"todos os orcos do norte, e tamén contra os troles e os mortos viventes. Nós, "
"os ananos, estamos condenados a ser un pobo en decadencia, choramingando nos "
"nosos túneles, os restos moribundos dun pobo que outrora foi orgulloso..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:924
msgid "Dwarven Doors"
msgstr "Portas ananas"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:929
msgid "The Dwarven Doors"
msgstr "As portas ananas"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:974
msgid ""
"The once-thriving free city of Dwarven Doors is filled with slaves and their "
"orcish masters. We can fight our way north to reach the caves of Knalga, "
"while freeing as many slaves as possible on our way!"
msgstr ""
"A outrora próspera cidade libre de Portas Ananas está chea de escravos e os "
"seus amos orcos. Podemos loitar cara ao norte para chegar ás covas de "
"Knalga, mentres liberamos tantos escravos como sexa posible polo camiño!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:980
msgid ""
"The once-thriving free city of Dwarven Doors is filled with slaves and their "
"orcish masters. We can fight our way south to exit the caves of Knalga, "
"while freeing as many slaves as possible on our way!"
msgstr ""
"A outrora próspera cidade libre de Portas Ananas está chea de escravos e os "
"seus amos orcos. Podemos loitar cara ao sur para saír das covas de Knalga, "
"mentres liberamos tantos escravos como sexa posible polo camiño!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1011
msgid ""
"We have cleared the Doors of orcs! It sounds as though they mean to return "
"in the future, but at least for now we will be able to pass unmolested."
msgstr ""
"Liberamos as portas dos orcos! Parece que teñen intención de volver no "
"futuro, pero polo menos de momento poderemos pasar sen ser molestados."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1016
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We have fought our way through the Doors! The orcs know better than to "
#| "try and fight us again in the future, but neither can we rescue any more "
#| "of their slaves while they are on alert. At least we will henceforth be "
#| "able to pass unmolested."
msgid ""
"We have fought our way through the Doors! The orcs know better than to try "
"to fight us again in the future, but neither can we rescue any more of their "
"slaves while they are on alert. At least we will henceforth be able to pass "
"unmolested."
msgstr ""
"Luchamos ata abrírmonos camiño polas portas! Os orcos saben mellor que "
"intentar loitar contra nós de novo no futuro, pero tampouco podemos rescatar "
"máis escravos mentres estean en alerta. Polo menos, a partir de agora "
"poderemos pasar sen ser molestados."

#. [message]: role=doors_orc
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1041
msgid ""
"Get back to work, pinkskin! Show your masters a proper work ethic and maybe "
"you’ll be spared the lash!"
msgstr ""
"Volta ao traballo, pel rosa! Demóstralles aos teus amos unha ética de "
"traballo axeitada e quizais te aforres o azoute!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1046
msgid ""
"Slaves? This is a travesty! Weren’t the Dwarven Doors once a great center of "
"civilization?"
msgstr ""
"Escravos? Isto é unha parodia! Non foron as Portas dos Ananos noutro tempo "
"un gran centro de civilización?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1050
msgid ""
"Their alliance with Knalga was strong, but even man and dwarf together could "
"not stop the orcish war-horde. And now it’s a slave city under the heel of "
"the orcs!"
msgstr ""
"A súa alianza con Knalga era forte, pero nin o home nin o anano xuntos "
"puideron deter a horda de guerra orca. E agora é unha cidade de escravos "
"baixo o talón dos orcos!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1065
msgid "Caverns of Chaincolt"
msgstr "Covas de Chaincolt"

#. [scenario]: id=28_The_Lost_General
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1076
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/28_The_Lost_General.cfg:18
msgid "The Lost General"
msgstr "O Xeneral Perdido"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1080
msgid ""
"Weapon for Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>+3 melee damage, <i>drains</i> "
"special on melee attacks</b></span>"
msgstr ""
"Arma para Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>+3 de dano en corpo a corpo, "
"<i>drena</i> especial en ataques corpo a corpo</b></span>"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1099
msgid ""
"These old halls were ruined long ago, but there may still be something of "
"value inside."
msgstr ""
"Estas vellas salas foron arruinadas hai moito tempo, pero aínda pode haber "
"algo de valor no seu interior."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1114
msgid ""
"The trolls that used to inhabit these old halls have gone; either killed off "
"or merely moved. There might have been treasure here, once, but all that is "
"left now is rubble and excrement."
msgstr ""
"Os trols que antes habitaban estes vellos corredores marcharon; ou foron "
"eliminados ou simplemente se mudaron. Quizais houbera tesouros aquí noutro "
"tempo, pero agora só quedan escombros e excremento."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1127
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I’m glad to be out into the sun and fresh air again. I’m don’t despise "
#| "caves so much as an elf, but I’m no dwarf either."
msgid ""
"I’m glad to be out into the sun and fresh air again. I may not despise caves "
"so much as an elf, but I’m no dwarf either."
msgstr ""
"Alégrome de estar de novo ao sol e ao aire fresco. Non desprezo as covas "
"tanto como un elfo, pero tampouco son un anano."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1134
msgid ""
"There’s nothing more of value here — at least nothing that we have the time "
"or skill to unearth."
msgstr ""
"Non hai nada máis valioso aquí — polo menos nada que teñamos tempo ou "
"habilidade para desenterrar."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1153
msgid ""
"The West Gate of Knalga! I learned about this place... it was a terrible "
"tragedy when the kingdom of the dwarves was shattered by the orcs and their "
"allies. Now all that’s left here are trolls and ruins."
msgstr ""
"A Porta Oeste de Knalga! Descubrín este lugar... foi unha terrible traxedia "
"cando o reino dos ananos foi arrasado polos orcos e os seus aliados. Agora "
"só quedan aquí trols e ruínas."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1167
msgid "Greater Knalga"
msgstr "Gran Knalga"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1172
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/29_Digging_for_Dwarves.cfg:189
msgid "Geldar"
msgstr "Geldar"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1173
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/29_Digging_for_Dwarves.cfg:460
msgid "Relgorn"
msgstr "Relgorn"

#. [scenario]: id=29_Digging_for_Dwarves
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1184
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/29_Digging_for_Dwarves.cfg:9
msgid "Digging for Dwarves"
msgstr "Cavando para ananos"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1188
msgid ""
"New Recruits\n"
"<i><b>Choose Two</b></i>:"
msgstr "Novos recrutas, <i><b>escolla dous</b></i> :"

#. [message]: speaker=Geldar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1219
msgid ""
"What now, human? I already told ye, no-one gets in without someone to vouch "
"for ’em."
msgstr ""
"Que agora, humano? Xa vos dixen, ninguén entra sen alguén que avale por eles."

#. [message]: speaker=Geldar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1224
msgid "Another attack! Up axes, and make ready to repel the invaders!"
msgstr "Outro ataque! Machados arriba e prepárate para repeler os invasores!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1228
msgid ""
"Peace, dwarves of Knalga! I am a man of Wesnoth, not an orc or a troll, and "
"I come as a friend."
msgstr ""
"Paz, ananos de Knalga! Son un home de Wesnoth, non un orco nin un trol, e "
"veño como amigo."

#. [message]: speaker=Geldar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1232
msgid ""
"A man? Haven’t seen many o’ yer kind since our friends at the Doors fell, "
"an’ you ain’t one o’ their’s. Who says we should trust ye?"
msgstr ""
"Un home? Non vin moitos coma vós dende que caeron os nosos amigos dos Doors, "
"e ti non es un dos seus. Quen di que debamos confiar en vós?"

#. [message]: speaker=Ulfdain
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1248
msgid ""
"Let us in, ye chicken-hearted cad! Cannae a dwarf return to ’is home without "
"bein’ set upon like some horde o’ trolls?"
msgstr ""
"Déixanos entrar, canalla corazón de galiña! Non pode un anano volver á súa "
"casa sen ser atacado coma unha horda de troles?"

#. [message]: speaker=Geldar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1252
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1282
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1305
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1333
msgid "I dunno..."
msgstr "Non sei..."

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1257
msgid ""
"Ulfdain!? I ain’t seen you in years, not since you left fer Wesnoth— an’ yer "
"a Bloodaxe now too!? Get across th’ bridge then, quickly-now, afore th’ orcs "
"find ye."
msgstr ""
"Ulfdain!? Fai anos que non te vexo, dende que marchaches a Wesnoth— e agora "
"tamén es un Bloodaxe!? Pasa a ponte, axiña, antes de que os orcos che atopen."

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1262
msgid ""
"Ulfdain!? I ain’t seen you in years, not since you left fer Wesnoth! Get "
"across th’ bridge then, quickly-now, afore th’ orcs find ye."
msgstr ""
"Ulfdain!? Fai anos que non te vexo, dende que marchaches cara a Wesnoth! "
"Cruzade a ponte, axiña, agora, antes de que os orcos vos atopen."

#. [message]: speaker=Somf
#. [message]: role=doors_vouch_peasant
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1278
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1301
msgid ""
"I’m from the Doors, your old human allies! And I’m free now, thanks to this "
"boy Konrad and his army! They’re good people, and I’ll vouch for ’em."
msgstr ""
"Son dos Doors, os vosos antigos aliados humanos! E agora son libre, grazas a "
"este rapaz Konrad e ao seu exército! Son boa xente, e eu dou fe deles."

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1286
msgid ""
"Ah, let ’em in, Geldar. They ain’t orcs, trolls, or undead, an’ that’s good "
"enough for now."
msgstr ""
"Ah, déixaos entrar, Geldar. Non son orcos, troles nin mortos viventes, e iso "
"xa chega por agora."

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1309
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1337
msgid ""
"Ah, let ’em in, Geldar. They ain’t orcs, trolls, or undead, an’ that’s good "
"enough for me."
msgstr ""
"Ah, déixaos entrar, Geldar. Non son orcos, troles nin mortos viventes, e iso "
"xa está ben para min."

#. [message]: role=doors_vouch_peasant
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1329
msgid ""
"Ah’m a dwarf, gatekeeper, an’ I’ll vouch for them. Lower yer axes an’ let us "
"in, ye hear?"
msgstr ""
"Son un anano, porteiro, e eu dou fe deles. Baixa os teus machados e déixanos "
"entrar, escoitaste?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1350
msgid ""
"I am Konrad, nephew of Garard, son of Arand and heir to the throne of "
"Wesnoth! I give my word — you can trust me, dwarf."
msgstr ""
"Son Konrad, sobriño de Garard, fillo de Arand e herdeiro ao trono de "
"Wesnoth! Dou a miña palabra: podes confiar en min, anano."

#. [message]: speaker=Geldar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1354
msgid ""
"Hmph. So you say. We’ve had pretenders workin’ for th’ orcs try an’ sneak in "
"here before. Even if you really are a prince, you ain’t gettin’ ’cross the "
"east bridge lest ye’ve got someone to vouch for ye."
msgstr ""
"Hmph. Iso dis ti. Xa tivemos impostores que traballaban para os orcos que "
"intentaron entrar aquí ás agachadas. Mesmo se es un príncipe de verdade, non "
"cruzarás a ponte leste para non ter alguén que avale por ti."

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1369
msgid ""
"What brings you to th’ East Gate o’ Knalga, friends? You be wantin’ "
"somethin’ from us, don’t you?"
msgstr ""
"Que vos trae ata a Porta Leste de Knalga, amigos? Queredes algo de nós, non "
"si?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1373
msgid ""
"Well, to be honest, people usually want something from <i><b>me</b></i> "
"instead. I help with a problem someone is having, and then they send some "
"spare fighters to join my army. Can you and I arrange anything like that?"
msgstr ""
"Ben, para ser sincero, a xente adoita querer algo de <i><b>min</b></i> en "
"troques. Axudo cun problema que alguén ten, e logo envían algúns combatentes "
"de reserva para unirse ao meu exército. Podemos ti e eu organizar algo así?"

#. [message]: speaker=Geldar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1377
msgid ""
"Spare fighters? I ain’t heard a jest that good since th’ trolls got "
"Durrasil! Yer walkin’ through the corpse o’ our empire, fallen to rot an’ "
"ruin, an’ ye got the gall to ask if we have extra axe-arms to send out with "
"ye?"
msgstr ""
"Loitadores de sobra? Non escoitei unha broma tan boa desde que os troles "
"atraparon a Durrasil! Andas polo cadáver do noso imperio, caído na podremia "
"e na ruína, e tes a descaro de preguntar se temos machadas de sobra para "
"enviar contigo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1381
msgid ""
"I’m afraid Geldar’s right. But problems — now problems we’ve got plenty of. "
"Orc attacks, troll attacks, undead attacks. ’an now down in th’ mines—"
msgstr ""
"Teño medo de que Geldar teña razón. Pero problemas... agora temos moitos "
"problemas. Ataques de orcos, ataques de troles, ataques de mortos viventes. "
"E agora abaixo nas minas..."

#. [message]: speaker=Geldar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1385
msgid "Relgorn, hush. That ain’t somethin’ fer outsiders to hear about."
msgstr "Relgorn, cala. Iso non é algo que oian os de fóra."

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1389
msgid ""
"Do ye got a better idea? We already tried t’ split ourselves up an’ help, "
"an’ tha’s when trolls took the gatehouse!"
msgstr ""
"Tes algunha idea mellor? Xa intentamos separarnos e axudar, e foi entón "
"cando os troles tomaron a portaría!"

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1394
msgid ""
"Listen, human... I’m only trustin’ you ’cause you been vouched for, "
"unnerstand? All ye need to know is that some o’ our people’re trapped in a "
"cave-in down in th’ old mines. You get ’em out, we’ll make it worth yer "
"while."
msgstr ""
"Escoita, humano... Só confío en ti porque te avalaron, entendes? O único que "
"necesitas saber é que algúns dos nosos están atrapados nun derrubamento nas "
"vellas minas. Sácaos de aí e faremos que pague a pena."

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1406
msgid ""
"Some o’ our people’re trapped in a cave-in down in th’ old mines. Tha’s all "
"ye need to know. You get ’em out, an’ we’ll make it worth yer while."
msgstr ""
"Algúns dos nosos están atrapados nun derrubamento nas vellas minas. Iso é "
"todo o que precisades saber. Sacádeos de aí e faremos que pague a pena."

#. [message]: speaker=Ragaril
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1424
msgid ""
"Thank ye again, Konrad. May ye have better luck saving your home than we’ve "
"had for ours."
msgstr ""
"Grazas de novo, Konrad. Oxalá teñas máis sorte salvando a túa casa que nós "
"tivemos coa nosa."

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1458
msgid ""
"What’s this? Konrad, ye’ve chased the orcs out o’ the Doors, wiped out th’ "
"trolls an’ undead squattin’ in our halls, and e’en trustworthily helped us "
"in the heart o’ Knalga itself."
msgstr ""
"Que é isto? Konrad, expulsaches os orcos das Portas, eliminaches os trols e "
"os mortos viventes que se agochaban nos nosos corredores, e mesmo nos "
"axudaches de xeito digno de confianza no propio corazón de Knalga."

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1462
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I know that the troll’ll return. I know that the orcs’ll return, an’ that "
#| "many o’ the Doors-folk are still with ’em, enslaved. But ye’ve given us "
#| "dwarves more breathin’ room than we’ve had in many a year."
msgid ""
"I know that the trolls’ll return. I know that the orcs’ll return, an’ that "
"many o’ the Doors-folk are still with ’em, enslaved. But ye’ve given us "
"dwarves more breathin’ room than we’ve had in many a year."
msgstr ""
"Sei que o trol volverá. Sei que os orcos volverán, e que moitos dos da xente "
"das Portas aínda están con eles, escravizados. Pero déchesnos aos ananos "
"máis espazo para respirar do que tivemos en moitos anos."

#. [message]: speaker=Relgorn
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1467
msgid ""
"I know ye said ye dinnae want any reward fer helpin’ us, but yer gettin’ one "
"anyway. I’m sendin’ the best lads in Knalga to help you fight that queen o’ "
"yers."
msgstr ""
"Sei que dixeches que non querías ningunha recompensa por axudarnos, pero vas "
"recibir unha de todos os xeitos. Vou enviar os mellores rapaces de Knalga "
"para axudarche a loitar contra esa raíña dos teus."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1471
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Konrad can now recruit Dwarvish Fighters, Guardsmen, Thunderers, and "
#| "Ulfserkers!"
msgid ""
"Konrad can now recruit Dwarvish Steelclads, Stalwarts, Thunderguards, and "
"Berserkers!"
msgstr ""
"Konrad agora pode recrutar guerreiros ananos, gardas, tronos e ulfserkers!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1496
msgid "???"
msgstr "???"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1497
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Passing through this whirlpool will warp reality,\n"
#| "giving Konrad unlimited time to explore and \n"
#| "disabling timed events that force him to move on.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "For each extra scenario you play over the normal \n"
#| "number, Asheviere will gain a +$s50_extra_income_per_scenario bonus \n"
#| "to income in the final scenario.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Using the whirlpool will also disable achievements,\n"
#| "except for <i>“Asleep at the Wheel”</i>. Are you sure?"
msgid ""
"Passing through this whirlpool will warp reality,\n"
"letting Konrad play an unlimited number of scenarios\n"
"and disabling timed events that force him to move on.\n"
"\n"
"For each extra scenario you play over the normal \n"
"number, Asheviere will gain +$s50_extra_income_per_scenario bonus income\n"
"in the final scenario.\n"
"\n"
"Using the whirlpool is probably not balanced, and\n"
"will disable all achievements (except for <i>“Asleep\n"
"at the Wheel”</i>). Are you sure?"
msgstr ""
"Pasar a través deste remuíño distorsionará a realidade, dándolle a Konrad "
"tempo ilimitado para explorar e desactivando eventos cronometrados que o "
"obrigan a seguir adiante. Por cada escenario adicional que xogues por riba "
"do número normal, Asheviere obterá unha bonificación de +"
"$s50_extra_income_per_scenario aos ingresos no escenario final. Usar o "
"remuíño tamén desactivará os logros, agás <i>\"Adurmido ao volante\"</i> . "
"Seguro?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1522
msgid ""
"There is a strange whirlpool here, clearly magical in nature... I wonder "
"what would happen if we allowed ourselves to be pulled in?"
msgstr ""
"Hai aquí un estraño remuíño, claramente de natureza máxica... Pregúntome que "
"pasaría se nos deixásemos arrastrar cara dentro?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1543
msgid "Oh... my head! What just happened?"
msgstr "Oh... a miña cabeza! Que acaba de pasar?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00c_northlands.cfg:1550
msgid "There is nothing here of note. Was there ever?"
msgstr "Non hai nada de destacable aquí. Houbo algunha vez?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:25
msgid ""
"There are countless caves and lava tunnels here, twisting and turning for "
"miles on end. There’s no reason to wander any deeper this way, at least not "
"right now."
msgstr ""
"Hai aquí innumerables covas e túneles de lava que se enroscan e retórcense "
"durante millas e millas. Non hai motivo para internarse máis por aquí, polo "
"menos non agora."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:36
msgid ""
"The Sceptre is quite real, I assure you. Perhaps you have forgotten our "
"lessons..."
msgstr "O cetro é ben real, asegúroche. Quizais esquezas as nosas leccións..."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador {DELFADOR_VARIATION mentoring}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:54
msgid ""
"The Ruby— now Sceptre of Fire is the symbol of the kings of Wesnoth, forged "
"by the dwarves of Knalga at the behest of King Haldric II. It took their "
"finest smiths years to make it, but soon after it was completed, the makers "
"were chased underground, attacked by the elves."
msgstr ""
"O Rubí — agora Cetro de Fogo — é o símbolo dos reis de Wesnoth, forxado "
"polos ananos de Knalga por mandato do rei Haldric II. Aos seus mellores "
"ferreiros custoulles anos facelo, pero pouco despois de rematalo, os seus "
"creadores foron perseguidos baixo terra e atacados polos elfos."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador {DELFADOR_VARIATION mentoring}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:58
msgid ""
"None know exactly what occurred, but the Sceptre was lost somewhere in the "
"great caverns. Years have passed, and the fortunes of the dwarves have waxed "
"and waned, but the Sceptre has never been found."
msgstr ""
"Ninguén sabe exactamente o que ocorreu, pero o Cetro perdeuse nalgún lugar "
"das grandes cavernas. Pasaron anos, e a fortuna dos ananos variou e minguou, "
"pero o Cetro nunca foi atopado."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:69
msgid ""
"Until now. The strands of prophecy are moving, Konrad — it has been foretold "
"that if your mentor searches for the Sceptre here, his magic is sure to find "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Ata agora. Os fíos da profecía están a moverse, Konrad — foi profetizado que "
"se o teu mentor busca aquí o Cetro, a súa maxia sen dúbida o atopará."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:74
msgid ""
"Until now. The strands of prophecy are moving, Konrad — it was foretold that "
"if your mentor searched for the Sceptre here, his magic would be sure to "
"find it. And he has."
msgstr ""
"Ata agora. Os fíos da profecía están a moverse, Konrad — estaba profetizado "
"que se o teu mentor buscaba aquí o Cetro, a súa maxia sen dúbida o atoparía. "
"E así foi."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:79
msgid ""
"And though I know not how nor exactly why, it has similarly been revealed "
"that you must someday hold the Sceptre if peace is ever to find Wesnoth... "
"or the elves."
msgstr ""
"E aínda que non sei como nin exactamente por que, revelouse do mesmo xeito "
"que algún día debes suxeitar o Cetro se queres que a paz atope algunha vez "
"Wesnoth... ou os elfos."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:84
msgid ""
"Until now. The strands of prophecy are moving, Konrad — it has been foretold "
"that if I searched for the Sceptre here, my magic would be sure to find it. "
"And I have."
msgstr ""
"Ata agora. Os fíos da profecía están a moverse, Konrad — foi profetizado que "
"se eu procurase o Cetro aquí, a miña maxia sen dúbida o atoparía. E atopeino."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:103
msgid ""
"Well, all right then. What’re we waiting for? Let’s scour these caverns, get "
"the Sceptre, and reclaim the kingdom! If there’s augury about it we’re "
"guaranteed to succeed, right?"
msgstr ""
"Ben, pois entón. Que estamos a esperar? Imos rexuntar estas covas, conseguir "
"o Cetro e reclamar o reino! Se hai augurio, temos éxito garantido, non?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:108
msgid ""
"Well, all right then. What’re we waiting for? Let’s get the Sceptre and "
"reclaim the kingdom! If there’s augury about it we’re guaranteed to succeed, "
"right?"
msgstr ""
"Ben, pois entón. Que estamos a esperar? Imos buscar o Cetro e reclamar o "
"reino! Se hai augurio, temos éxito garantido, non si?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:113
msgid ""
"No, no, no! This is <b><i>precisely</i></b> what I was worried about. You "
"are not guaranteed to succeed, nor are you invincible!"
msgstr ""
"Non, non, non! Isto era <b><i>precisamente</i></b> o que me preocupaba. Non "
"tes garantido o éxito, nin es invencible!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:117
msgid ""
"When I was young I found myself in a similar situation. Through my arrogance "
"and my haste, I ruined quite nearly everything. You already know the story "
"of my folly."
msgstr ""
"Cando era novo atopeime nunha situación semellante. Pola miña arrogancia e a "
"miña présa case arruinei todo. Xa coñeces a historia da miña tolemia."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:121
msgid "My father, Prince Arand."
msgstr "Meu pai, o príncipe Arand."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:126
msgid ""
"Quite right. Do not become overconfident, Konrad. I am searching for the "
"Sceptre now. Once it is found, I promise you shall most certainly have it."
msgstr ""
"Moi ben. Non te confíes demasiado, Konrad. Estou buscando o Cetro agora. "
"Unha vez que o atope, prométoche que o terás con toda seguridade."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:131
msgid ""
"Quite right. Do not become overconfident, Konrad. We may be about to claim "
"the Sceptre, but we have not done so yet. And you are not yet king."
msgstr ""
"Moi ben. Non te confíes demasiado, Konrad. Pode que esteamos a piques de "
"reclamar o Cetro, pero aínda non o fixemos. E aínda non es rei."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:136
msgid ""
"But no matter what, please — be forgiving, be wise, and above all be kind. "
"For that is where I failed."
msgstr ""
"Pero pase o que pase, por favor, sexas indulxente, sabio e, sobre todo, "
"amable. Porque aí é onde fallei."

#. [scenario]: id=30_The_Sceptre_of_Fire
#. [object]: id=sceptre_of_fire, type=fire, type=fire, type=fire, type=fire
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:152
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/30_The_Sceptre_of_Fire.cfg:33
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/specials_and_abilities.cfg:196
msgid "The Sceptre of Fire"
msgstr "O Cetro de Fogo"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:156
msgid ""
"Weapon for Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>The Sceptre of Fire</b></span>"
msgstr "Arma para Konrad: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>O Cetro de Fogo</b></span>"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:178
msgid ""
"Hello, Konrad! I am most glad to see you again. Have you and Kalenz been "
"taking good care of yourselves?"
msgstr ""
"Ola, Konrad! Alégrome moito de verte de novo. Ti e Kalenz estivestes "
"coidando ben de vós?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:182
msgid ""
"Delfador, at last! So this is where you went off to! What quest could "
"possibly bring you into this maze of tiny caves and tunnels?"
msgstr ""
"Delfador, por fin! Entón, aquí é onde fuches! Que misión podería levarte a "
"este labirinto de pequenas covas e túneles?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:186
msgid ""
"Well, I suppose I must tell you eventually... Konrad, I am searching for the "
"Sceptre of Fire."
msgstr ""
"Ben, supoño que che teño que dicirllo tarde ou cedo... Konrad, estou a "
"buscar o Cetro de Fogo."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:190
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The Scepter of Fire? The youngfolk at Blackwater Port always said that "
#| "was just an old myth."
msgid ""
"The Sceptre of Fire? The youngfolk at Blackwater Port always said that was "
"just an old myth."
msgstr ""
"O Cetro de Fogo? Os mozos de Porto Negro sempre dicían que iso era só un "
"vello mito."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:200
msgid ""
"I have come, Delfador! So this is where you went off to! It is good to see "
"you again, even if it is in such an unpleasant maze of caves and tunnels."
msgstr ""
"Vin, Delfador! Entón, aquí é onde fuches! É bo verte de novo, mesmo que sexa "
"nun labirinto tan desagradable de covas e túneles."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:204
msgid ""
"You say you are searching for the Sceptre of Fire? The youngfolk at "
"Blackwater Port always said that was just an old myth!"
msgstr ""
"Dices que estás a buscar o Cetro de Fogo? A xente nova do Porto Negro sempre "
"dicía que iso era só un vello mito!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:219
msgid ""
"I am glad to see you have returned, Konrad. Are you ready to proceed onto "
"the next phase of your adventures?"
msgstr ""
"Alégrome de verte de volta, Konrad. Estás preparado para pasar á seguinte "
"fase das túas aventuras?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:230
msgid ""
"I have not located the Sceptre yet, but I am making progress. I shall send a "
"messenger once we are ready to retrieve it — perhaps after your next battle."
msgstr ""
"Aínda non atopei o Cetro, pero estou a facer progresos. Enviarei un "
"mensaxeiro en canto esteamos listos para recuperalo, quizais despois da vosa "
"próxima batalla."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:235
msgid ""
"I have not located the Sceptre yet, but I am making progress. I shall send a "
"messenger once we are ready to retrieve it — perhaps in $"
"( $bm_milestone_scepter - $bm_turns ) battles’ time."
msgstr ""
"Aínda non localicei o Cetro, pero estou a facer progresos. Enviarei un "
"mensaxeiro unha vez que esteamos listos para recuperalo, quizais en tempo de "
"$( $bm_milestone_scepter - $bm_turns ) batallas."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:240
msgid ""
"Finding the Sceptre will mark a major turning point in our adventure, "
"Konrad. Before that happens, I urge you to take advantage of your freedom "
"and continue exploring the Great Continent. You have done much good already, "
"but there are countless others who still need your help."
msgstr ""
"Atopar o Cetro marcará un punto de inflexión importante na nosa aventura, "
"Konrad. Antes de que iso aconteza, instoche a que aproveites a túa liberdade "
"e continues explorando o Gran Continente. Xa fixeches moito ben, pero hai "
"moitas outras persoas que aínda precisan da túa axuda."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:244
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You may join me and hurry along the search if you so desire, but know "
#| "that doing so will mark the end of your deeds in this region."
msgid ""
"You may join me and hurry along the search if you so desire, but know that "
"although doing so may afford us more time for our future endeavors, it will "
"also mark the end of your deeds in this region."
msgstr ""
"Podes unirte a min e axudar a acelerar a procura se así o desexas, pero "
"debes saber que facelo marcará o fin das túas accións nesta rexión."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:254
msgid ""
"Excellent, you have come swiftly. Thank you, Konrad. I am certain I have "
"located the object of our search, but we will need to work together to "
"retrieve it."
msgstr ""
"Excelente, chegaches rápido. Grazas, Konrad. Estou seguro de que atopei o "
"obxecto da nosa busca, pero teremos que traballar xuntos para recuperalo."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:260
msgid ""
"Here is the tunnel down which lies the Sceptre of Fire; the symbol of kings. "
"The surrounding caverns are crawling with all manner of monsters, doubtless "
"drawn by its power."
msgstr ""
"Aquí está o túnel no que se atopa o Cetro de Lume; o símbolo dos reis. As "
"cavernas circundantes están cheas de todo tipo de monstros, sen dúbida "
"atraídos polo seu poder."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:264
msgid ""
"Together, we shall clear the tunnels and claim your birthright once and for "
"all."
msgstr ""
"Xuntos limparemos os túneles e reclamaremos o teu dereito de nacemento de "
"unha vez por todas."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador {DELFADOR_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:336
msgid ""
"The lava continues to rise! Hurry, Konrad — I have cast a spell to hasten "
"our flight, but you must decide in which direction we go!"
msgstr ""
"A lava segue subindo! Apresúrate, Konrad. Lancei un feitizo para acelerar a "
"nosa fuxida, pero debes decidir en que dirección imos!"

#. [scenario]: id=31_Plunging_Into_Darkness
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:355
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/31_Plunging_into_Darkness.cfg:5
msgid "Plunging Into Darkness"
msgstr "Sumergíndose na escuridade"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:383
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "<b>Replacement Weapons</b> — Permament Modifier"
msgid "<b>Replacement Weapons</b> — Permanent Modifier"
msgstr "<b>Armas de substitución</b> : modificador permanente"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:384
msgid ""
"Your veteran recalls cost <span color='red'>twice as much</span>.\n"
"Your level 0-1 recruits refund <span color='#00FF00'>half their cost</span>."
msgstr ""
"Os teus recordos de veterano custan <span color='red'>o dobre</span>.\n"
"Os teus reclutas de nivel 0-1 reembolsan <span color='#00FF00'>a metade do "
"seu custo</span>."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:386
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This archway opens into an old dwarvish armory, long-ago fallen into "
#| "ruin. Troll excrement coats the walls while insects and vermin churn in "
#| "the dirt, all with a horrifying buzz of flies and smell of rot.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "If we flee in this direction we can gather countless low-quality weapons, "
#| "but the specialized equipment wielded by our veteran soldiers will surely "
#| "suffer from decay."
msgid ""
"This archway opens into an old dwarvish armory, long-ago fallen into ruin. "
"Troll excrement coats the walls while insects and vermin churn in the dirt, "
"all with a horrifying buzz of flies and smell of rot."
msgstr ""
"Esta arcada abre a unha vella armería anana, hai moito tempo caída en "
"ruínas. O excremento de trol cobre as paredes mentres insectos e vermes "
"revolven na terra, todo acompañado dun zumbido horríbel de moscas e dun "
"cheiro a podredume. Se fuximos nesta dirección podemos recoller incontábeis "
"armas de baixa calidade, pero o equipamento especializado dos nosos soldados "
"veteranos sen dúbida sufrirá o deterioro."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:388
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This archway opens into an old dwarvish armory, long-ago fallen into "
#| "ruin. Troll excrement coats the walls while insects and vermin churn in "
#| "the dirt, all with a horrifying buzz of flies and smell of rot.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "If we flee in this direction we can gather countless low-quality weapons, "
#| "but the specialized equipment wielded by our veteran soldiers will surely "
#| "suffer from decay."
msgid ""
"If we flee in this direction we can gather countless low-quality weapons, "
"but the specialized equipment wielded by our veteran soldiers will surely "
"suffer from decay."
msgstr ""
"Esta arcada abre a unha vella armería anana, hai moito tempo caída en "
"ruínas. O excremento de trol cobre as paredes mentres insectos e vermes "
"revolven na terra, todo acompañado dun zumbido horríbel de moscas e dun "
"cheiro a podredume. Se fuximos nesta dirección podemos recoller incontábeis "
"armas de baixa calidade, pero o equipamento especializado dos nosos soldados "
"veteranos sen dúbida sufrirá o deterioro."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:396
msgid "No permanent modifier."
msgstr "Non hai modificador permanente."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:398
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This passageway is broad and even, with clear air and a gentle upwards "
#| "slope. I even feel a slight breeze!\n"
#| "\n"
#| "This seems the perfect path for our escape — if we flee in this direction "
#| "we shall gain no boon but suffer no penalty."
msgid ""
"This passageway is broad and even, with clear air and a gentle upwards "
"slope. I even feel a slight breeze!"
msgstr ""
"Este corredor é amplo e plano, con aire limpo e unha suave pendente "
"ascendente. Ata sinto unha lixeira brisa! Este semella o camiño perfecto "
"para a nosa fuxida — se fuximos nesta dirección non obteremos ningún "
"beneficio nin sufriremos ningunha penalidade."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:400
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This passageway is broad and even, with clear air and a gentle upwards "
#| "slope. I even feel a slight breeze!\n"
#| "\n"
#| "This seems the perfect path for our escape — if we flee in this direction "
#| "we shall gain no boon but suffer no penalty."
msgid ""
"This seems the perfect path for our escape — if we flee in this direction we "
"shall gain no boon but suffer no penalty."
msgstr ""
"Este corredor é amplo e plano, con aire limpo e unha suave pendente "
"ascendente. Ata sinto unha lixeira brisa! Este semella o camiño perfecto "
"para a nosa fuxida — se fuximos nesta dirección non obteremos ningún "
"beneficio nin sufriremos ningunha penalidade."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:408
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "<b>Memory Magic</b> — Permament Modifier"
msgid "<b>Memory Magic</b> — Permanent Modifier"
msgstr "<b>Maxia da memoria</b> — Modificador permanente"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:409
msgid ""
"Your max-level units require <span color='#00FF00'>75% less XP</span> to "
"advance.\n"
"Your other units require <span color='red'>75% more XP</span> to advance."
msgstr ""
"As túas unidades de nivel máximo precisan <span color='#00FF00'>75% less de "
"XP</span> para progresar.\n"
"As túas outras unidades precisan <span color='red'>un 75% máis de XP</span> "
"para progresar."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:411
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "In this direction there are motes of light dancing on the walls, with a "
#| "faint smell of lavender and cinnamon in the air. Is this magic? Some "
#| "remnant of the Sceptre’s internment, perhaps?\n"
#| "\n"
#| "I am not sure what will happen if we flee this way, but already I can "
#| "feel something moving within my mind... affecting my memories..."
msgid ""
"In this direction there are motes of light dancing on the walls, with a "
"faint smell of lavender and cinnamon in the air. Is this magic? Some remnant "
"of the Sceptre’s internment, perhaps?"
msgstr ""
"Nesta dirección hai motas de luz bailando nas paredes, cun leve cheiro a "
"lavanda e canela no aire. É isto maxia? Algún vestixio do internamento do "
"Cetro, quizais?\n"
"\n"
"Non estou seguro do que pasará se fuximos por aquí, pero xa sinto algo "
"moverse dentro da miña mente... afectando as miñas lembranzas..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:413
msgid ""
"I am not sure what will happen if we flee this way, but already I can feel "
"something moving within my mind... affecting my memories..."
msgstr ""
"Non estou seguro do que pasará se fuximos por aquí, pero xa podo sentir algo "
"movéndose na miña mente... afectando aos meus recordos..."

#. [floating_text]
#. $recruit_cost will be half of unit's value unit; likely between 10 and 25
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:486
msgid "$recruit_cost gold refunded"
msgstr "Ouro $recruit_cost reembolsado"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:503
msgid "The Swamp of Dread"
msgstr "O pantán do espanto"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:514
msgid ""
"Finally! Our journey under the mountains has been long and difficult, but at "
"last we return to the open continent — and with a powerful new ally!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin! A nosa viaxe baixo as montañas foi longa e difícil, pero por fin "
"volvemos ao continente aberto... e cun novo e poderoso aliado!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:518
msgid ""
"If you’re serious about overthrowing my mother, just my support won’t be "
"enough. And she’s certainly not about to give up the throne just for my sake."
msgstr ""
"Se vas en serio sobre derrocar á miña nai, o meu apoio non será suficiente. "
"E ela, desde logo, non vai renunciar ao trono só por min."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:522
msgid ""
"No, we need to start by dismantling her allies. Dan’Tonk, the Horse Clans, "
"the orcish tribes — all these bolster Weldyn’s armies. The more we can "
"defeat, the weaker Asheviere will become."
msgstr ""
"Non, temos que comezar por desmantelar os seus aliados. Dan’Tonk, os Clans "
"de Cabalos, as tribos orcas... todo isto reforza os exércitos de Weldyn. "
"Cantos máis poidamos derrotar, máis débil se volverá Asheviere."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:526
msgid ""
"Or elsewise, we must acquire more allies of our own! We may find friends "
"among the elves of the Lintanir — I have spent time there before. There are "
"woses in the east as well, and drakes; who knows what else may await us!"
msgstr ""
"Ou se non, debemos conseguir máis aliados nosos! Pode que atopemos amigos "
"entre os elfos do Lintanir; xa pasei tempo alí antes. Tamén hai woses no "
"leste e dragóns; quen sabe que máis nos pode agardar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00d_sceptre_scenarios.cfg:539
msgid ""
"This was a difficult battle, but without it we would never have become "
"allied with Li’sar. We should count ourselves lucky to have fought it."
msgstr ""
"Esta foi unha batalla difícil, pero sen ela nunca nos teriamos aliñado con "
"Li'sar. Debemos considerarnos afortunados por telo combatido."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:13
msgid "Snow Plains"
msgstr "Planos de neve"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:16
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:113
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1106
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1213
msgid "Defeated Faction:"
msgstr "Facción derrotada:"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=leader2
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:27
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:75
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/41_Snow_Plains.cfg:36
msgid "Urag Fell-Handed"
msgstr "Urag de Máns de Pedra"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:47
msgid "Look there, in the cage! Is that who she seems to be?"
msgstr "Mira alí, na gaiola! Parece que é ela?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mirya
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:52
msgid ""
"Then it’s agreed? You’ll release and repatriate me to my queen’s service, in "
"return for a to-be-negotiated ransom from the royal treasury?"
msgstr ""
"Entón está acordado? Me liberarás e repatriarás ao servizo da miña raíña, a "
"cambio dun rescate por negociar do tesouro real?"

#. [message]: speaker=urag_tifer
#. "witch" is a derogatory term here. Mirya (a Silver Mage) would probably prefer to be called a mage, or maybe a wizard.
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:57
msgid ""
"Rrr... deal. No more mucking around in these freezing mountains while the "
"other chiefs feed like pigs in Wesnoth. Ha! Lucky for me that we happened to "
"run into each other, witch."
msgstr ""
"Mrrr... acordo. Non máis andar por aí nestas montañas xeadas mentres os "
"outros xefes comen coma porcos en Wesnoth. Ha! Que sorte teño que nos "
"atopamos por casualidade, meiga."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:63
msgid ""
"The fates must have a sense of humor — here is imprisoned the very mage who "
"tried to burn us alive back in the volcano."
msgstr ""
"O destino debe ter sentido do humor: aquí está preso o mesmo mago que "
"intentou queimarnos vivos no volcán."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:67
msgid ""
"It sounds as though she stands on the verge of freedom. But if we strike "
"now, we can prevent her from ever rejoining Asheviere."
msgstr ""
"Parece que está a piques de ser liberada. Pero se atacamos agora, podemos "
"evitar que se reincorpore a Asheviere."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:84
msgid "An ignominious end for a mage who’s caused us so much trouble."
msgstr "Un final indigno para un meigo que nos causou tantos problemas."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:86
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "An ignominious end for a mage who’s caused us so much "
#| "trouble.                \n"
#| "\n"
#| "From what Li’sar tells me, Mirya has recruited orcish clans for Asheviere "
#| "in the past. It is good that we stopped her before she could bring this "
#| "one into their fold too."
msgid ""
"From what Li’sar tells me, Mirya has recruited orcish clans for Asheviere in "
"the past. It is good that we stopped her before she could bring this one "
"into their fold too."
msgstr ""
"Un final ignominioso para un mago que nos causou tantos problemas.\n"
"\n"
"Polo que me dixo Li'sar, Mirya recrutou clans orcos para Asheviere no "
"pasado. É bo que a detivemos antes de que puidese traer tamén a este ao seu "
"redil."

#. [message]: speaker=urag_tifer
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:92
msgid "Get out of here, humans. You already got what you came for!"
msgstr "Ide de aquí, humanos. Xa tedes o que viñestes buscar!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:102
msgid "Whitefang Mountains"
msgstr "Montañas Dente Branco"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:110
msgid "A Crisis of Leadership"
msgstr "Unha crise de liderado"

#. [event]
#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:145
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/42_A_Crisis_of_Leadership.cfg:270
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1923
msgid "Fagh-mok the Flattered"
msgstr "Fagh-mok o Adulado"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador {DELFADOR_VARIATION mentoring}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:158
msgid ""
"Be cautious, Konrad. We approach the Whitefang mountains, home to a vast "
"orcish clan of the same name. They are allies of Asheviere’s, and powerful "
"enemies of ours."
msgstr ""
"Ten coidado, Konrad. Achegámonos ás montañas Brancocolmo, fogar dun vasto "
"clan orco do mesmo nome. Son aliados de Asheviere e poderosos inimigos nosos."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador {DELFADOR_VARIATION mentoring}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:162
msgid ""
"Even the great armies of yesteryear lacked the strength to defeat them in "
"their home. We should do our best to slip quietly past."
msgstr ""
"Mesmo os grandes exércitos de antano carecían da forza para derrotalos no "
"seu fogar. Deberíamos facer todo o posible por pasar discretamente."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:166
msgid ""
"Your warning comes too late, Delfador. One of their leaders has already "
"spotted us!"
msgstr ""
"A túa advertencia chega demasiado tarde, Delfador. Un dos seus líderes xa "
"nos viu!"

#. [message]: speaker=Faghmok
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:172
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Peace, pinkski— humans! Hah, don’t you look scared to see me. You must be "
#| "the great prince Konrad!"
msgid ""
"Peace, pinkski— humans! Hah, don’t you look scared to see me. You must be "
"the great Prince Konrad!"
msgstr ""
"Paz, pinkski... humanos! Ha, non pareza que teñas medo de verme. Debes ser o "
"gran príncipe Konrad!"

#. [message]: speaker=Faghmok
#. his real name is Fagh-mok the Flattered, but he's lying to make himself sound better.
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:177
msgid ""
"I am Fagh-mok the Honorable, honest warrior of the chief’s guard. The nasty "
"queen Asheviere told us all sorts of things about you, prince. But I’m sure "
"it’s all lies."
msgstr ""
"Son Fagh-mok, o Honorable e honesto guerreiro da garda do xefe. A "
"desagradable raíña Asheviere contounos todo tipo de cousas sobre ti, "
"príncipe. Pero estou seguro de que todo son mentiras."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:181
msgid ""
"You are no friend of the dark queen, then? Yet your clan fights alongside "
"her as an ally."
msgstr ""
"Entón non es amigo da raíña escura? Con todo, o teu clan loita xunto a ela "
"como aliado."

#. [message]: speaker=Faghmok
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:185
msgid ""
"They have been misled! Our foolish chief dares to oppose you, oh mighty "
"Konrad! But if there were to be a new chief... myself, for example..."
msgstr ""
"Foron enganados! O noso tolo xefe atreve a opoñerse a ti, oh poderoso "
"Konrad! Pero se houbera un novo xefe... eu mesmo, por exemplo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Faghmok
#. [message]: role=weldyn3
#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. [message]: speaker=Delurin
#. [message]: speaker=Moremirmu
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#. [message]: speaker=Harper
#. [message]: speaker=Lisar {LISAR_VARIATION defeat}
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#. [message]: speaker=Mirya
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:189
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1499
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/00_The_Great_Continent.cfg:1198
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/08a_Isle_of_the_Damned_part1.cfg:207
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/15b_Valley_of_Death_part2.cfg:401
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/24_An_Old_Friend.cfg:349
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/26_The_Dwarven_Doors.cfg:445
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/32_The_Swamp_of_Dread.cfg:421
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/32_The_Swamp_of_Dread.cfg:620
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/32_The_Swamp_of_Dread.cfg:746
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/32_The_Swamp_of_Dread.cfg:1195
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/41_Snow_Plains.cfg:230
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/41_Snow_Plains.cfg:347
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50x_Overlook.cfg:120
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50x_Overlook.cfg:207
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. [message]: speaker=Faghmok
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:193
msgid "If you’re interested, come meet me just outside our camp."
msgstr ""
"Se estás interesado/a, vén atoparte comigo xusto fóra do noso campamento."

#. [message]: speaker=Faghmok
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:203
msgid "Ha ha ha, I knew you’d come find me. Very good."
msgstr "Ha ha ha, sabía que virías buscarme. Moi ben."

#. [message]: speaker=Faghmok
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:207
msgid ""
"I’m prepared to sneak you and three of your best soldiers into the center of "
"our camp. Once you’re there, it’ll be up to you to kill the old chief — and "
"then I can take over!"
msgstr ""
"Estou preparado para meterte ás agachadas a ti e a tres dos teus mellores "
"soldados no centro do noso campamento. Unha vez alí, dependerá de ti matar o "
"vello xefe... e entón poderei tomar o control!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:211
msgid ""
"Or, once we’re separated from our army you will capture us and turn us over "
"to Asheviere. Why should I take such a great risk on the word of a stranger?"
msgstr ""
"Ou, unha vez que nos separemos do noso exército, capturarásnos e "
"entregarásnos a Asheviere. Por que debería correr un risco tan grande por "
"palabra dun descoñecido?"

#. [message]: speaker=Faghmok
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:215
msgid ""
"Bah, I don’t get to be chief unless you kill the old chief! But if you must "
"have some guarantee... fine, I’ll stay prisoner with your army until you "
"safely return. Now what do you say?"
msgstr ""
"Bah, non podo ser xefe a menos que mates o vello xefe! Pero se queres ter "
"algunha garantía... está ben, permanecerei prisioneiro co teu exército ata "
"que volvas san e salvo. Agora que dis?"

#. [message]: speaker=Faghmok
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:220
msgid ""
"When you’re ready, I can sneak you and three of your best soldiers into the "
"center of our camp. And then you can kill the chief! What do you say?"
msgstr ""
"Cando esteas listo, podo facer que ti e tres dos teus mellores soldados "
"entredes sigilosamente no centro do noso campamento. E entón podes matar ao "
"xefe! Que dis?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:225
msgid ""
"Hmm... If this is to be an assassination, we will need veterans with enough "
"accuracy and power to quickly defeat enemies even within their own "
"fortifications. Are we prepared?"
msgstr ""
"Mmm... Se isto vai ser un asasinato, precisaremos veteranos con suficiente "
"precisión e poder para derrotar rapidamente os inimigos mesmo dentro das "
"súas propias fortificacións. Estamos preparados?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:269
msgid ""
"With the Whitefangs embroiled in civil war, Asheviere is more vulnerable "
"than ever! I wonder who the eventual victor will be..."
msgstr ""
"Coa familia Whitefang inmersa nunha guerra civil, Asheviere é máis "
"vulnerable que nunca! Pregúntome quen será o vencedor final..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:275
msgid ""
"With the Whitefangs embroiled in civil war, Asheviere is more vulnerable "
"than ever."
msgstr ""
"Coa familia Whitefang inmersa nunha guerra civil, Asheviere é máis "
"vulnerable que nunca."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:285
msgid "Arkan-Thoria"
msgstr "Arkan-Thoria"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:293
msgid "Cliffs of Thoria"
msgstr "Penínsulas de Thoria"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:296
msgid "New Companion for Li’sar:"
msgstr "Novo compañeiro para Li'sar:"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:299
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Reinforcements: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>Lisar will start future "
#| "scenarios with double income and +50 gold.</b></span>"
msgid ""
"Reinforcements: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>Li’sar will start future scenarios "
"with double income and +50 gold.</b></span>"
msgstr ""
"Reforzos: <span color='#EFBF04'><b>Lisar comezará os escenarios futuros con "
"ingresos dobres e +50 de ouro.</b></span>"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:315
msgid ""
"Look — winged shapes swooping on the horizon. And I hear the shouts and "
"screams of men! A battle is being fought on the river!"
msgstr ""
"Mirade... formas aladas voando no horizonte. E escoito os berros e os "
"alaridos dos homes! Está a librarse unha batalla no río!"

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:322
msgid ""
"That is the river that is known as Longlier to men, called Arkan-thoria in "
"my people’s ancient tongue. Its name means ‘The River of Bones’. Great and "
"evil creatures lurk along its banks, its waters are not fit to drink, and it "
"runs over the Cliffs of Thoria."
msgstr ""
"Ese é o río que os homes coñecen como Longlier, chamado Arkan-thoria na "
"antiga lingua do meu pobo. O seu nome significa \"O Río dos Ósos\". "
"Criaturas grandes e malvadas acechan nas súas beiras, as súas augas non son "
"potables e corre polos cantís de Thoria."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:326
msgid ""
"It has been many centuries since any man or elf has passed over the Cliffs "
"and survived. Be cautious, prince."
msgstr ""
"Pasaron moitos séculos dende que ningún home ou elfo cruzou os Cantís e "
"sobreviviu. Ten coidado, príncipe."

#. [message]: speaker=Warven
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:347
msgid ""
"I can’t thank you enough for saving me, Your Highness. I would have been "
"dead a dozen times over."
msgstr ""
"Non lle podo agradecer dabondo por salvarme, Alteza. Tería estado morto unha "
"ducia de veces."

#. [message]: speaker=Warven
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:351
msgid ""
"The rest of the survivors are a week’s march upriver. They’re in a pretty "
"bad state right now, but give me a few animals and some supplies to go "
"relieve them, and we’ll be ready to reinforce you for your next battles."
msgstr ""
"O resto dos superviventes atópase a unha semana de camiño río arriba. Están "
"nun estado bastante malo agora mesmo, pero dame uns cantos animais e "
"provisións para ir aliviálos, e estaremos preparados para reforzarte nas "
"túas próximas batallas."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:358
msgid "Reinforcements"
msgstr "Reforzos"

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:359
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Lisar will start future scenarios with double income and +50 gold."
msgid "Li’sar will start future scenarios with double income and +50 gold."
msgstr "Lisar comezará escenarios futuros con ingresos dobres e +50 de ouro."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:365
msgid ""
"There are still some drakes here, but there’s no longer any reason to fight. "
"We did a good thing by rescuing Warven and his allies."
msgstr ""
"Aínda quedan algúns patos macho aquí, pero xa non hai motivo para loitar. "
"Fixemos algo bo ao rescatar a Warven e aos seus aliados."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:387
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We’re approaching the outskirts of Lintanir forest. Delfador once told me "
#| "about a grove of woses living here, but today the trees are silent. "
#| "Wherever the woses are, I expect the elves of Lintanir will have much to "
#| "speak with us about."
msgid ""
"We’re approaching the outskirts of Lintanir Forest. Delfador once told me "
"about a grove of woses living here, but today the trees are silent. Wherever "
"the woses are, I expect the elves of Lintanir will have much to speak with "
"us about."
msgstr ""
"Estamos achegándonos aos arredores da selva de Lintanir. Delfador contoume "
"unha vez que aquí vivía un bosque de woses, pero hoxe as árbores están en "
"silencio. Onde estean os woses, agardo que os elfos de Lintanir teñan moito "
"que dicirnos."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:402
msgid "Underground Channels"
msgstr "Canles subterráneas"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:406
msgid "New Recruit for Delfador:"
msgstr "Novo recluta para Delfador:"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:427
msgid ""
"The river travels underground here, and there is an awful stench of rot and "
"decay. Has some undead creature taken up residence inside?"
msgstr ""
"O río discorre aquí baixo terra, e hai un fedor espantoso de podredume e "
"descomposición. ¿Alguén criatura non morta tomou residencia alí dentro?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:431
msgid ""
"I am not sure what benefit we could gain from fighting in such a place, but "
"it is always our duty to destroy evil."
msgstr ""
"Non estou seguro de que beneficio poderiamos obter loitando nun lugar así, "
"pero sempre é o noso deber destruír o mal."

#. [side]: id=Haralamdum, type=Ancient Wose
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:439
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/44_Underground_Channels.cfg:158
msgid "Haralamdum"
msgstr "Haralamdum"

#. [message]: speaker=Haralamdum
#. Goodbye young Master Delfador, and Prince Konrad. Good luck. I hope my gift will be useful to you.
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:446
msgid ""
"Goodbye ... young Master Delfador ... Prince Konrad ... hum dum da dum ... "
"and good luck. I hope my gift will be useful to you."
msgstr ""
"Adeus... mozo mestre Delfador... príncipe Konrad... hum dum da dum... e boa "
"sorte. Espero que o meu agasallo che sexa útil."

#. [message]: speaker=Haralamdum
#. Hello again.
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:453
msgid "Hello ... again. Har alam dum ..."
msgstr "Ola... de novo. Har alam dum..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:463
msgid "Lintanir Forest"
msgstr "Bosque de Lintanir"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:471
msgid "Eloreis"
msgstr "Eloreis"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:472
msgid "Parandra"
msgstr "Parandra"

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:509
msgid ""
"At last! Friends, we have finally reached the Lintanir Forest, home of the "
"North Elves. I was born not far east of here... more years ago than I care "
"to remember."
msgstr ""
"Por fin! Amigos, chegamos por fin ao bosque de Lintanir, fogar dos elfos do "
"norte. Nacín non moi ao leste de aquí... hai máis anos dos que me gustaría "
"lembrar."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:513
msgid ""
"Hail, elves! I am Konrad, heir to the throne of Wesnoth and son of the "
"Aethenwood. Lord Kalenz has told me much about his home in the Lintanir. I "
"am honored to meet you."
msgstr ""
"Saúde, elfos! Son Konrad, herdeiro ao trono de Wesnoth e fillo do Bosque de "
"Aethen. Lord Kalenz faloume moito sobre o seu fogar no Lintanir. É unha "
"honra para min coñecervos."

#. [message]: speaker=Eloreis
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:517
msgid ""
"Greetings, Konrad. I have heard much about you as well. Welcome to the "
"Lintanir Forest."
msgstr ""
"Saúdos, Konrad. Eu tamén oín falar moito de ti. Benvido ao bosque de "
"Lintanir."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION glad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:526
msgid ""
"Hail, elves! I am Konrad, heir to the throne of Wesnoth, son of the "
"Aethenwood and friend of Lord Kalenz."
msgstr ""
"Saúde, elfos! Son Konrad, herdeiro ao trono de Wesnoth, fillo do Bosque de "
"Aethen e amigo de Lord Kalenz."

#. [message]: speaker=Eloreis
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:530
msgid ""
"Greetings, Konrad. I have heard much about you. Welcome to the Lintanir "
"Forest, home of the North Elves."
msgstr ""
"Saúdos, Konrad. Xa oín falar moito de ti. Benvido ao bosque de Lintanir, "
"fogar dos elfos do norte."

#. [message]: speaker=Parandra
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:542
msgid ""
"How quickly does the race of men mature! Only seventeen winters have passed "
"since I last laid eyes on you, Konrad, yet you are now a grown man. A proven "
"warrior stands before me!"
msgstr ""
"Que rápido madura a raza dos homes! Só pasaron dezasete invernos dende a "
"última vez que te vin, Konrad, e aínda así agora es un home feito e feito. "
"Un guerreiro probado está diante de min!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:546
msgid "Forgive me, Elf, but I’m afraid I do not recall meeting you before. "
msgstr "Perdóame, Elf, pero temo que non recordo coñecerte antes."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador {DELFADOR_VARIATION mentoring}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:550
msgid ""
"Konrad, this is Parandra. When Asheviere first took power and her orcs began "
"rampaging across Wesnoth, Parandra helped me rescue you from the royal "
"palace."
msgstr ""
"Konrad, son Parandra. Cando Asheviere tomou o poder por primeira vez e os "
"seus orcos comezaron a arrasar Wesnoth, Parandra axudoume a rescatarte do "
"palacio real."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:554
msgid "I had no idea! Thank you, my lady. It is a pleasure to meet you again."
msgstr "Non tiña nin idea! Grazas, miña señora. É un pracer volver a velo."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:558
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Rescued him from my mother? Seventeen years ago Konrad would’ve been an "
#| "infant. What is this you’re talking about? "
msgid ""
"Rescued him from my mother? Seventeen years ago Konrad would’ve been an "
"infant. What is this you’re talking about?"
msgstr ""
"Rescatáchelo da miña nai? Hai dezasete anos Konrad sería un neno. De que "
"estás a falar?"

#. [message]: id=Kalenz,Eloreis
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:562
msgid ""
"Your mother has much blood upon her hands, child. She has had many killed "
"unjustly. When Konrad was an infant, she ordered all the princes put to "
"death, so she could seize control."
msgstr ""
"A túa nai ten moito sangue nas mans, neno. Fixo matar a moitos inxustamente. "
"Cando Konrad era un bebé, ordenou que matasen a todos os príncipes para "
"poder facerse co control."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:566
msgid ""
"Not long ago I would’ve decried such an obvious lie. But Konrad and Delfador "
"have shown me many things of which I didn’t wish to believe regarding my "
"mother. I trust that you speak the truth."
msgstr ""
"Non hai moito tempo tería denunciado unha mentira tan obvia. Pero Konrad e "
"Delfador mostráronme moitas cousas que non quería crer sobre a miña nai. "
"Confío en que digas a verdade."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:576
msgid ""
"But now I hold the Sceptre — our symbol of rulership — and my mother’s time "
"as queen draws short. I have a chance to do better!"
msgstr ""
"Pero agora teño o cetro (o noso símbolo de goberno) e o tempo da miña nai "
"como raíña achégase. Teño a oportunidade de facelo mellor!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:580
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Though you have the Sceptre, my lady, it is not your place to rule. Your "
#| "line was tainted when Asheveire orchestrated her husband’s downfall."
msgid ""
"Though you have the Sceptre, my lady, it is not your place to rule. Your "
"line was tainted when Asheviere orchestrated her husband’s downfall."
msgstr ""
"Aínda que tes o Cetro, miña señora, non che corresponde reinar. A túa liñaxe "
"quedou manchada cando Asheveire orquestrou a caída do seu marido."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:585
msgid ""
"But that is why I must take the Sceptre from you, Konrad — it is our symbol "
"of rulership. My mother’s time as queen draws short. With the Sceptre, as "
"queen, I have a chance to do better."
msgstr ""
"Pero é por iso que debo quitarche o Cetro, Konrad: é o noso símbolo de "
"goberno. O tempo da miña nai como raíña achégase. Co Cetro, como raíña, teño "
"a oportunidade de facelo mellor."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:589
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "My lady, there is some good in you, but the throne is not yours to claim. "
#| "Your line was tainted when Asheveire orchestrated her husband’s downfall."
msgid ""
"My lady, there is some good in you, but the throne is not yours to claim. "
"Your line was tainted when Asheviere orchestrated her husband’s downfall."
msgstr ""
"Miña señora, hai algo bo en vostede, pero o trono non é seu para reclamalo. "
"A súa liñaxe foi contaminada cando Asheveire orquestrou a caída do seu "
"marido."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:594
msgid ""
"Konrad is the rightful heir; the son of Arand and nephew of Garard. I have "
"raised him as my own, as penance for my part in Garard’s fall. Konrad shall "
"be king."
msgstr ""
"Konrad é o lexítimo herdeiro; fillo de Arand e sobriño de Garard. Crieino "
"como meu propio fillo, como penitencia pola miña participación na caída de "
"Garard. Konrad será rei."

#. [message]: speaker=Parandra
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:604
msgid "(gestures to Delfador)"
msgstr "(xesticula cara a Delfador)"

#. [message]: speaker=Parandra
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:610
msgid ""
"Delfador, you have raised Konrad to be skillful and wise, honorable and "
"just. A warrior who has respect, and appreciates peace. Yet the throne is "
"not the place for him. You know of what I speak, Delfador."
msgstr ""
"Delfador, criaches a Konrad para ser hábil e sabio, honorable e xusto. Un "
"guerreiro que respecta e aprecia a paz. Porén, o trono non é o lugar "
"axeitado para el. Sabes do que falo, Delfador."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:614
msgid ""
"Parandra, what you say may seem right to some, but as long as you and I "
"speak to no-one of what we know, I see no reason why Konrad would not best "
"have the throne."
msgstr ""
"Parandra, o que dis pode parecerlle correcto a algúns, pero mentres ti e eu "
"non falemos con ninguén do que sabemos, non vexo ningunha razón pola que "
"Konrad non debería ter o trono."

#. [message]: speaker=Parandra
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:618
msgid ""
"In so many things you are right, Delfador, and your wisdom is unmatched in "
"the world of men. But in this, you are mistaken. Li’sar is the heir. She "
"should take the throne. Now that I have met her for myself, I am sure of it."
msgstr ""
"En moitas cousas tes razón, Delfador, e a túa sabedoría non ten rival no "
"mundo dos homes. Pero nisto estás equivocado. Li'sar é a herdeira. Debería "
"ocupar o trono. Agora que a coñecín por min mesmo, estou seguro diso."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:622
msgid "Hmph. Perhaps you are right, perhaps not. We shall see."
msgstr "Hmph. Se cadra tes razón, se cadra non. Xa veremos."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:632
msgid "*Ahem*"
msgstr "*Ejem*"

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:640
msgid ""
"... Konrad, I once promised you aid from my home, should we ever reach it. "
"Now we have. The Lintanir has magic to offer you and your companions; aid on "
"your quest against the dark queen."
msgstr ""
"... Konrad, unha vez che prometín axuda dende o meu fogar, se algunha vez "
"chegásemos a el. Agora témolo. O Lintanir ten maxia para ofrecerche a ti e "
"aos teus compañeiros; axuda na túa misión contra a raíña escura."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:645
msgid ""
"... Konrad, you have proven yourself an enemy of Asheviere’s and a friend to "
"the elves. The Lintanir has magic to offer you and your companions; aid on "
"your quest against the dark queen."
msgstr ""
"... Konrad, demostraches que es un inimigo de Asheviere e un amigo dos "
"elfos. O Lintanir ten maxia para ofrecerche a ti e aos teus compañeiros; "
"axuda na túa misión contra a raíña escura."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:650
msgid ""
"We hold in our possession three objects of legend: a tome of wose lore, a "
"chestplate of black steel, and a great sword of fire. Choose one, and it "
"shall be yours."
msgstr ""
"Temos en nosa posesión tres obxectos lendarios: un tomo de sabedoría escura, "
"unha peza de armadura de aceiro negro e unha gran espada de lume. Elixe un, "
"e será teu."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:654
msgid ""
"You are as generous as you are wise, Lord Kalenz. Please, tell us more about "
"these artifacts you offer."
msgstr ""
"Es tan xeneroso como sabio, Señor Kalenz. Por favor, dinos máis sobre estes "
"artefactos que ofreces."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:659
msgid ""
"Now I wish you luck, Konrad, and you Li’sar. Let us rest, and then once more "
"go forth. Fortune has smiled upon us so far, despite great dangers. Perhaps "
"she will continue to do so."
msgstr ""
"Agora deséxoche sorte, Konrad, e a ti, Li'sar. Descansemos e logo volvamos "
"adiante. A fortuna sorriunos ata agora, a pesar dos grandes perigos. Quizais "
"siga facéndoo."

#. [message]: speaker=Eloreis
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:668
msgid ""
"But enough introductions. Konrad, is the Lord Kalenz with you? There is much "
"that the three of us ought to speak about."
msgstr ""
"Pero abonda de presentacións. Konrad, está o señor Kalenz contigo? Hai moito "
"do que nós tres deberiamos falar."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:672
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The good lord was injured in battle some time ago, and retreated "
#| "eastwards towards Lintanir forest. He has not arrived safely? That is ill "
#| "news, for he seemed a wise elf and a staunch ally."
msgid ""
"The good lord was injured in battle some time ago, and retreated eastwards "
"towards Lintanir Forest. He has not arrived safely? That is ill news, for he "
"seemed a wise elf and a staunch ally."
msgstr ""
"O bo señor foi ferido en batalla hai algún tempo e retirouse cara ao leste, "
"en dirección ao bosque de Lintanir. Non chegou san e salvo? Iso son malas "
"noticias, xa que parecía un elfo sabio e un aliado leal."

#. [message]: speaker=Eloreis
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:676
msgid ""
"That bodes ill indeed. I do not believe he has perished, for Kalenz "
"represents the best of us, and has survived many trials in times past. But I "
"fear he has been waylaid by some mischief."
msgstr ""
"Iso augura mal, de verdade. Non creo que morrese, porque Kalenz representa o "
"mellor de nós e sobreviviu a moitas probas no pasado. Pero temo que algunha "
"travesura o asaltou."

#. [message]: speaker=Eloreis
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:680
msgid ""
"I can do little but wish you luck, Konrad, and you Li’sar. Rest, and then go "
"forth. Fortune has smiled upon you so far, despite great dangers. Perhaps "
"she will continue to do so."
msgstr ""
"Non podo facer moito máis que desexarche sorte, Konrad, e a ti, Li'sar. "
"Descansa e logo adiante. A fortuna sorriuche ata agora, a pesar dos grandes "
"perigos. Quizais siga facéndoo."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:703
msgid ""
"I know little of woses, but I know they are not warriors. What secret lore "
"might they have that could be of use on the battlefield?"
msgstr ""
"Sei pouco sobre os woses, pero sei que non son guerreiros. Que coñecementos "
"secretos poderían ter que poderían ser útiles no campo de batalla?"

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:707
msgid ""
"The ways of the wood; the art of moving quickly and unseen among the trees. "
"It is a magical tome; a record of the life-sap of Elilmaldur-Rithrandil, "
"eldest of the Green Isle."
msgstr ""
"Os camiños do bosque; a arte de moverse con rapidez e sen ser visto entre as "
"árbores. É un tomo máxico; un rexistro da seiva de vida de Elilmaldur-"
"Rithrandil, o maior da Illa Verde."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:711
msgid ""
"To many, this tome would seem filled with meaningless tales of sticks and "
"leaves. But you were raised in woods, Konrad. Should you choose to take it, "
"I believe you will gain great affinity with the forest, its nature and ways, "
"and all the creatures within it."
msgstr ""
"Para moitos, este tomo semellaría cheo de contos sen sentido de paus e "
"follas. Pero ti criácheste no bosque, Konrad. Se decides levalo, creo que "
"adquirirás unha gran afinidade co bosque, coa súa natureza e coas súas "
"maneiras, e con todas as criaturas que nel habitan."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:718
msgid ""
"Taking the tome of Wose Lore will grant <b>Konrad</b> the <i>ambush</i> "
"ability — invisibility in forest — as well as improved forest movement and "
"70% forest defense."
msgstr ""
"Coller o tomo de Wose Lore outorgaralle <b>a Konrad</b> a habilidade <i>de "
"emboscada</i> (invisibilidade no bosque), así como un movemento mellorado no "
"bosque e unha defensa do bosque do 70% f."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:732
msgid ""
"You called this a sword of fire, Kalenz, but it looks little different from "
"my own. Is there a command word, perhaps?"
msgstr ""
"Chamaches isto espada de lume, Kalenz, pero semella pouco diferente da miña. "
"Hai algunha palabra de mando, quizais?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:738
msgid ""
"This is a wizard’s sword, Konrad; I sense its power. With such an enchanted "
"weapon, even one as old as me would make a capable swordsman."
msgstr ""
"Esta é a espada dun feiticeiro, Konrad; sinto o seu poder. Cunha arma así "
"encantada, mesmo alguén tan vello coma min sería un espadachín capaz."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:742
msgid ""
"Yes, it once belonged to Ila’alion, a mighty sorceresses. It was enchanted "
"as a boon to her by your elvish friends in the south, but it brought her "
"only disaster."
msgstr ""
"Si, pertenceu a Ila’alion, unha poderosa feiticeira. Foi encantado como un "
"agasallo dos teus amigos elfos do sur, pero só lle trouxo desgraza."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:744
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes, it once belonged to Ila’alion, a mighty sorceresses. It was "
#| "enchanted as a boon to her by your elvish friends in the south, but it "
#| "brought her only disaster.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Her fellow enchantresses... well, one could say they were slow to come to "
#| "Ila’alion’s aid as she held this very forest against an orcish incursion. "
#| "They resented her arrogance as the bearer of the sword, and indignation "
#| "is a powerful force amongst my people at times."
msgid ""
"Her fellow enchantresses... well, one could say they were slow to come to "
"Ila’alion’s aid as she held this very forest against an orcish incursion. "
"They resented her arrogance as the bearer of the sword, and indignation is a "
"powerful force amongst my people at times."
msgstr ""
"Si, un día pertenceu a Ila'alion, unha poderosa feiticeira. Foi encantado "
"como un don para ela polos teus amigos elfos do sur, pero só lle trouxo "
"desastres.\n"
"\n"
"As súas compañeiras encantadoras... ben, pódese dicir que foron lentas en "
"acudir en axuda de Ila'alion mentres ela defendía este mesmo bosque fronte a "
"unha incursión orca. Resentían a súa arrogancia como portadora da espada, e "
"a indignación é unha forza poderosa entre o meu pobo ás veces."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:751
msgid ""
"Taking the Flaming Sword will grant <b>Delfador</b> a new melee attack, "
"hitting for 7-4 fire damage."
msgstr ""
"Coller a Espada Flameante outorgará <b>a Delfador</b> un novo ataque corpo a "
"corpo, que inflixe 7-4 de dano de lume."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:765
msgid ""
"That’s a spectacular piece of armor, Kalenz, and I don’t think it is elf-"
"made. Not even among the best smiths of Weldyn have I seen its like. How did "
"the Lintanir come by it?"
msgstr ""
"É unha peza de armadura espectacular, Kalenz, e non creo que sexa feita por "
"elfos. Nin sequera entre os mellores ferreiros de Weldyn vin unha igual. "
"Como a conseguiron os Lintanir?"

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:769
msgid ""
"Many years ago, we were troubled by an undead lord of great power. Its axe "
"clove our steel blades as if they were saplings, and its enchanted armor "
"deflected our strongest magics and hottest fires."
msgstr ""
"Hai moitos anos atrás, un señor morto vivente de gran poder nos atormentou. "
"O seu machado fendeu as nosas láminas de aceiro coma se fosen árbores novas, "
"e a súa armadura encantada desviou as nosas maxias máis fortes e os lumes "
"máis intensos."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:773
msgid ""
"Only at great length and great cost did we emerge triumphant, destroying the "
"lord of the undead and taking its armor as spoil. If you choose to wear it, "
"Li’sar, do so humbly — it was paid for in blood."
msgstr ""
"Só con moito esforzo e a un gran custo conseguimos saír triunfantes, "
"destruíndo o señor dos mortos viventes e levando a súa armadura como botín. "
"Se decides levala, Li'sar, faino con humildade: foi pagada con sangue."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:780
msgid ""
"Taking the Void Armor will grant <b>Li’sar</b> immunity to slows, poison, "
"fire damage, cold damage, and arcane damage."
msgstr ""
"Tomar a Armadura do Baleiro outorgará <b>a Li'sar</b> inmunidade a "
"ralentizacións, veleno, dano por lume, dano por frío e dano arcano."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:795
msgid "As you wish. The wose lore is yours."
msgstr "Agora podes erguer cadáveres de Arboáns!"

#. [event]: id=boon_wose_lore
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:801
msgid ""
"This massive book is filled with the Lore and Legends of the Wose. Konrad "
"gains the <i>ambush</i> ability, improved forest movement, and 70% forest "
"defense."
msgstr ""
"Este enorme libro está cheo do Saber e das Lendas dos Wose. Konrad adquire a "
"habilidade <i>de emboscada</i>, movemento mellorado no bosque e 70% fdefensa "
"no bosque."

#. [dummy]: id=wose_lore
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:806
msgid "wose lore"
msgstr "sabedoría do arboán"

#. [dummy]: id=wose_lore
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:807
msgid "This unit has 70% defense, full movement, and invisibility in forest."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidade ten 70% defensa, movemento completo e invisibilidade no bosque."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:841
msgid "As you wish. The flaming sword is yours."
msgstr "Como desexes. A espada en chama é túa."

#. [event]: id=boon_flaming_sword # used in smalltalk.cfg, type=fire
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:847
msgid ""
"This massive blade was created centuries ago by long-forgotten elvish "
"forgemasters, who imbued the bluish steel with an inner magical fire. "
"Delfador gains a new melee attack, dealing 7-4 fire damage."
msgstr ""
"Esta enorme espada foi creada hai séculos polos esquecidos mestres forxeiros "
"elficos, que infundiron ao aceiro azulado un lume máxico interior. Delfador "
"obtén un novo ataque corpo a corpo, que causa 7-4 puntos de dano de lume."

#. [event]: id=boon_flaming_sword # used in smalltalk.cfg, type=fire
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:851
msgid "flaming sword"
msgstr "Espada flamíxera"

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:866
msgid "As you wish. The void armor is yours."
msgstr "Estás seguro de que queres cancelar?"

#. [event]: id=boon_void_armor
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:872
msgid ""
"This beautiful chest plate is crafted from shimmering black steel. Li’sar "
"gains immunity to slows, poison, fire damage, cold damage, and arcane damage."
msgstr ""
"Esta fermosa placa pectoral está forxada en aceiro negro relucente. Li'sar "
"adquire inmunidade a ralentizacións, veleno, dano de lume, dano de frío e "
"dano arcano."

#. [dummy]: id=void_armor
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:877
msgid "void armor"
msgstr "armadura do baleiro"

#. [dummy]: id=void_armor
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:878
msgid ""
"This unit has immunity to slows, poison, fire damage, cold damage, and "
"arcane damage."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidade ten inmunidade a ralentizacións, veleno, dano de lume, dano de "
"frío e dano arcano."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:903
msgid "Fort Garard"
msgstr "Fort Garard"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:918
msgid "The ruins of Fort Garard. This is where my father died."
msgstr "As ruínas de Fort Garard. É aquí onde morreu o meu pai."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:922
msgid ""
"Yes. You know the story. The darkest hour of my darkest day; a crime born of "
"my haste and my arrogance. Had I been but a breath wiser that night, all "
"might have been different..."
msgstr ""
"Si. Xa coñeces a historia. A hora máis escura do meu día máis escuro; un "
"crime xurdido da miña présa e da miña arrogancia. Se esa noite fose só un "
"alento máis sabio, todo podería ter sido diferente..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:934
msgid "Estmark Hills"
msgstr "Estmark Hills"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:937
msgid "N. Outpost"
msgstr "N. Avanzado"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:939
msgid "S. Outpost"
msgstr "S. Avanzado"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:950
msgid "Parthyn"
msgstr "Parthyn"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:951
msgid "Soradoc"
msgstr "Soradoc"

#. [message]: role=soradoc_guard
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:986
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Halt! Your Highness Li’sar, by order of Queen Asheviere you are branded a "
#| "traitor and an enemy of the state. Prepare to be apprehended."
msgid ""
"Halt! Your Highness Li’sar, by order of Her Majesty The Queen you are "
"branded a traitor and an enemy of the state. Prepare to be apprehended."
msgstr ""
"Alto! Alteza Li'sar, por orde da raíña Asheviere foi cualificado de traidor "
"e inimigo do estado. Prepárese para ser detido."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar # no variation; use her default portrait (which now includes the Sceptre)
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:998
msgid ""
"A traitor? This is the Sceptre of Fire, symbol of the kings of Wesnoth, and "
"I return after claiming it at great cost from the caverns of the north."
msgstr ""
"Un traidor? Este é o Cetro de Lume, símbolo dos reis de Wesnoth, e regreso "
"despois de reclamalo a un gran custo das cavernas do norte."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1002
msgid ""
"You know that Asheviere has proven a poor ruler. You know that I have been a "
"just general. And now I hold the Sceptre, not my mother. Stand aside or die, "
"soldier."
msgstr ""
"Xa sabes que Asheviere demostrou ser un gobernante inepta. Xa sabes que eu "
"fun un xeneral xusto. E agora sostén o cetro eu, non a miña nai. Apártate ou "
"morre, soldado."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1012
msgid ""
"Leave my cousin out of this. You know who I am. And now you see I hold the "
"Sceptre."
msgstr ""
"Deixa fóra disto ao meu primo. Xa sabes quen son. E agora ves que eu teño o "
"Cetro."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1016
msgid ""
"You have heard lies about my war from Asheviere — now hear the truth. This "
"land is suffering. I know it, you know it, even Li’sar knows it; Asheviere’s "
"own daughter driven to revolt."
msgstr ""
"Escoitastes mentiras sobre a miña guerra de Asheviere — agora escoitade a "
"verdade. Esta terra está a padecer. Eu sáboo, ti sábelo, mesmo Li'sar "
"sábelo; a propia filla de Asheviere levada á revolta."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1026
msgid ""
"Together the princess and I have claimed the Sceptre of Fire, the staff of "
"kings. In Haldric’s hands, it was our salvation from the Lich Lords. In "
"mine, it shall save you and I both from the terror that is Asheviere. You "
"will let us pass."
msgstr ""
"Xuntos, a princesa e eu reclamamos o Cetro de Fogo, o cetro dos reis. Nas "
"mans de Haldric, foi a nosa salvación fronte aos Señores Liches. Nas miñas, "
"salvará tanto a ti como a min do terror que é Asheviere. Deixarédesnos pasar."

#. [message]: role=soradoc_guard
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1036
msgid "(whispering back and forth)"
msgstr "(murmurando de ida e volta)"

#. [message]: role=soradoc_guard
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1043
msgid "Go. You were never here."
msgstr "Vai. Nunca estiviches aquí."

#. [message]: role=soradoc_guard
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1048
msgid ""
"... and if you do win against Asheviere, please remember our actions today."
msgstr "... e se gañas contra Asheviere, lembra as nosas accións de hoxe."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1068
msgid "The Horse Plains"
msgstr "As Chairas dos Cabalos"

#. [event]
#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1071
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/47_Test_of_the_Clans.cfg:105
msgid "Sir Alric"
msgstr "Señor Alric"

#. [event]
#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1075
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/47_Test_of_the_Clans.cfg:106
msgid "Sir Daryn"
msgstr "Sir Daryn"

#. [event]
#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1079
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/47_Test_of_the_Clans.cfg:107
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:2002
msgid "Lord Bayar"
msgstr "Señor Bayar"

#. [event]
#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1083
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/47_Test_of_the_Clans.cfg:108
msgid "Sir Ruga"
msgstr "Sr. Ruga"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1103
msgid "Test of the Clans"
msgstr "Proba dos Cláns"

#. [message]: speaker=Alric
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1120
msgid "So! The young prince has found his way to the lands of the Horse Lords."
msgstr ""
"Entón! O mozo príncipe atopou o camiño cara ás terras dos Señores dos "
"Cabalos."

#. [message]: speaker=Daryn
#. "old stick" refers to the sceptre of fire
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1128
msgid ""
"Do not expect us, too, to bend the knee just because the princess holds an "
"old stick."
msgstr ""
"Non esperedes que nós tamén dobremos o xeonllo só porque a princesa sostén "
"un pau vello."

#. [message]: speaker=Daryn
#. "old stick" refers to the sceptre of fire
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1136
msgid ""
"Do not expect us, too, to bend the knee just because you hold an old stick."
msgstr ""
"Non esperes que nós tamén dobremos o xeonllo só porque ti sostés un pau "
"vello."

#. [message]: speaker=Ruga
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1141
msgid ""
"You are two children and an old man. What right have you to challenge the "
"throne?"
msgstr "Sodes dous nenos e un vello. Que dereito tedes para desafiar o trono?"

#. [message]: speaker=Haldiel
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1156
msgid ""
"We have come to the Horse Plains, Konrad — the lands of my birth and the "
"home of my kin. Perhaps I can persuade them where you could not."
msgstr ""
"Chegamos ás Chairas dos Cabalos, Konrad — as terras onde nacín e o fogar da "
"miña xente. Quizais poida convencelos onde ti non puideches."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1168
msgid ""
"The Horse Clans are powerful and proud. If we cannot prove ourselves to them "
"now, we shall surely have to battle them later, when we attack Weldyn."
msgstr ""
"Os Clans dos Cabalos son poderosos e orgullosos. Se non podemos "
"demostrarlles o noso valor agora, seguramente teremos que loitar contra eles "
"máis tarde, cando ataquemos Weldyn."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1190
msgid ""
"Do not forget your pledge, lords of the clans. When Asheviere calls you for "
"aid, let her pleas fall upon deaf ears."
msgstr ""
"Non esquezades o voso xuramento, señores dos clans. Cando Asheviere vos "
"chame axuda, deixade que as súas súplicas caian en oídos xordos."

#. [message]: id=Alric,Daryn,Bayar,Ruga
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1196
msgid ""
"You have proven yourselves worthy, Your Royal Highnesses, worthy even to "
"claim the throne. I bow my head."
msgstr ""
"Demonstrastes ser dignos, Vosas Altezas Reais, mesmo para reclamar o trono. "
"Inclino a miña cabeza."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1263
msgid ""
"Hold! We approach the walled city of Dan’Tonk. This was the crowning "
"conquest of my mother’s early days. Its conscripts have made up the bulk of "
"her footmen ever since."
msgstr ""
"Agarda! Achegámonos á cidade amurallada de Dan'Tonk. Esta foi a conquista "
"máis importante dos primeiros días da miña nai. Os seus recrutas "
"constituíron o groso dos seus soldados de infantaría desde entón."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1268
msgid ""
"Are those... gryphons swooping over the city walls? Asheviere must have "
"tried again to seize their eggs, but thanks to our help the gryphons have "
"become strong enough to fight back!"
msgstr ""
"Son eses... grifóns que están a revolcarse sobre as murallas da cidade? "
"Asheviere debeu intentar de novo apoderarse dos seus ovos, pero grazas á "
"nosa axuda os grifóns volvéronse o suficientemente fortes como para loitar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1273
msgid ""
"That was a dark day... I remember it well. I urged the baron to flee, but in "
"the end we chose to stand and fight — and it cost him his life. So many "
"regrets..."
msgstr ""
"Foi un día escuro... Lémbroo ben. Instei ao barón a fuxir, pero ao final "
"decidimos plantarnos e loitar, e custoulle a vida. Tantos arrepentimentos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1282
msgid ""
"When we someday lay siege to Weldyn, Asheviere will surely call upon "
"Dan’Tonk’s footmen to flank us. If we strike now, we can do enough damage to "
"prevent them from marching against us later."
msgstr ""
"Cando algún día asedemos Weldyn, Asheviere sen dúbida chamará aos peóns de "
"Dan'Tonk para flanquearnos. Se atacamos agora, podemos causar o suficiente "
"dano para impedir que marchen contra nós máis tarde."

#. [message]: role=dantonk_contain_guard
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1324
msgid ""
"We’re all set up, my lady, and we’ve blocked the roads with rubble. They "
"won’t get through easily."
msgstr ""
"Xa estamos todos preparados, miña señora, e bloqueamos os camiños con "
"escombros. Non pasarán con facilidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1328
msgid ""
"Well done, everyone — our flank is secure. Asheviere’s position in Weldyn "
"grows weaker each day."
msgstr ""
"Ben feito, a todos — o noso flanco está seguro. A posición de Asheviere en "
"Weldyn debilítase cada día."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1334
msgid ""
"Although Dan’Tonk remains in the hands of the enemy, it is much diminished. "
"We have neither the time nor the supplies for a protracted siege, so we’ve "
"blocked the road and have left behind enough guards to make any sortie "
"difficult."
msgstr ""
"Aínda que Dan’Tonk segue en mans do inimigo, está moi diminuída. Non temos "
"nin tempo nin subministracións para un asedio prolongado, polo que "
"bloqueamos o camiño e deixamos gardas dabondo para dificultar calquera saída."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1375
msgid "Stockpiles"
msgstr "Reservas"

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1401
msgid ""
"Konrad, we’re now deep within the heartland of Wesnoth. While the western "
"farms suffer under Mother’s exorbitant taxes, those surrounding Weldyn — the "
"core of her power base — have grown rich and fat."
msgstr ""
"Konrad, agora estamos no corazón de Wesnoth. Mentres as granxas occidentais "
"sofren os impostos exorbitantes da Nai, as que rodean Weldyn (o núcleo da "
"súa base de poder) enriquecéronse e engordaron."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1405
msgid ""
"It’s an unsavory proposal, but I believe our best strategy is to burn the "
"locals’ farms to deprive my mother of their resources."
msgstr ""
"É unha proposta pouco agradable, pero penso ca nosa mellor estratexia é "
"queimar as granxas dos locais para privar á miña nai dos seus recursos."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1407
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "It’s an unsavory idea, but if we’re desperate, we may need to consider "
#| "burning the locals’ farms to deprive my mother of their resources.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "I’m not suggesting we conscript or kill anyone — these are innocents. But "
#| "a wealthy farmer can survive losing a few herds or a single year’s "
#| "harvest. We won’t, if Asheviere defeats us in the end."
msgid ""
"I’m not suggesting we conscript or kill anyone — these are innocents. But a "
"wealthy farmer can survive losing a few herds or a single year’s harvest. We "
"won’t, if Asheviere defeats us in the end."
msgstr ""
"É unha idea desagradable, pero se estamos desesperados, quizais teñamos que "
"considerar queimar as granxas da xente do lugar para privar á miña nai dos "
"seus recursos.\n"
"\n"
"Non estou a suxerir que recrutemos nin matemos a ninguén; estes son "
"inocentes. Pero un granxeiro rico pode sobrevivir perdendo uns poucos "
"rabaños ou a colleita dun só ano. Non o faremos se Asheviere nos derrota ao "
"final."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1418
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "An unsavory idea indeed. Razing the region’s farms might be sound "
#| "military strategy, but I’d still only consider it if we cannot defeat "
#| "Asheviere otherwise. Weldyn will surely pose a frightenly difficult "
#| "challenge either way..."
msgid ""
"An unsavory idea indeed. Razing the region’s farms might be sound military "
"strategy, but I am not enthused about the prospect. Of course, Weldyn will "
"surely pose a frighteningly difficult challenge if we do not..."
msgstr ""
"Unha idea desagradable, sen dúbida. Arrasar as granxas da rexión pode ser "
"unha boa estratexia militar, pero eu só a consideraría se non podemos "
"derrotar a Asheviere doutro xeito. Weldyn seguramente suporá un desafío "
"terriblemente difícil de calquera xeito..."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1420
msgid "Burn the farms (default difficulty)"
msgstr "Queimar as granxas (dificultade por defecto)"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1438
msgid "Don’t (extra difficulty)"
msgstr "Non facelo (dificultade extra)"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1451
msgid "★Weldyn"
msgstr "★Weldyn"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1459
msgid "The Battle for Wesnoth"
msgstr "A batalla polo Noroeste"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1503
msgid "No turning back now."
msgstr "Agora non hai volta atrás."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1531
msgid ""
"The capital of Wesnoth stands before us. We can challenge Asheviere now, if "
"we choose, but it may be wiser to first fight elsewhere and cut off her "
"allies."
msgstr ""
"A capital de Wesnoth está diante de nós. Podemos desafiar Asheviere agora, "
"se o desexamos, pero pode ser máis sabio loitar primeiro noutro lugar e "
"illar os seus aliados."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:1535
msgid ""
"I suspect that no matter what we do, we will be forced into a final "
"confrontation eventually."
msgstr ""
"Sospeito que, fagamos o que fagamos, verémonos obrigados a un enfrontamento "
"final ao final."

