msgstr "Xinvan"

#. [unit]: id=Haldiel, type=Horseman
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:471
msgid "Haldiel"
msgstr "Haldiel"

#. [unit]: type=Knight, id=Simyr
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:486
msgid "Simyr"
msgstr "Simyr"

#. [message]: speaker=Simyr
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:513
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:554
msgid ""
"Your promised reinforcements have arrived! Time to drive back the false "
"queen’s troops from the port!"
msgstr ""
"Os teus reforzos prometidos chegaron! É hora de expulsar as tropas da falsa "
"raíña do porto!"

#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:518
msgid ""
"Our promised reinforcements have arrived! Time to drive back the false "
"queen’s troops from the port!"
msgstr ""
"Chegaron os nosos reforzos prometidos! É hora de repeler as tropas da falsa "
"raíña do porto!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mokolo Qimur
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:523
msgid ""
"So many foul humans riding on horses! Asheviere isn’t paying me nearly "
"enough for this. Let’s get out of here!"
msgstr ""
"Tantos humanos repugnantes montados a cabalo! Asheviere non me paga o "
"suficiente por isto. Vaimonos de aquí!"

#. [message]: speaker=enemy1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:528
msgid "The enemy has been reinforced! Quick, we must make our escape!"
msgstr "Reforzáronse os inimigos! Depresa, debemos escapar!"

#. [message]: speaker=enemy2
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:533
msgid "Retreat! Fall back!"
msgstr "Retirada! Atrás!"

#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:559
msgid ""
"Reinforcements have arrived, but lo! Together we have already managed to "
"repel the false queen’s attack!"
msgstr ""
"Chegaron os reforzos, pero mirade! Xuntos xa conseguimos repeler o ataque da "
"falsa raíña!"

#. [message]: speaker=Simyr
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:586
msgid ""
"Victory is ours — but at such cost! Where is the lord of the town? What has "
"become of Sir Kaylan?"
msgstr ""
"A vitoria é nosa — pero a que custo! Onde está o señor da vila? Que foi de "
"Sir Kaylan?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:590
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Uncle Kaylan— <b>Sir</b> Kaylan fought bravely... but in the end he fell, "
#| "piereced by Asheviere’s spears. It is thanks to his sacrifice that "
#| "Blackwater Port still stands free."
msgid ""
"Uncle Kaylan— <b>Sir</b> Kaylan fought bravely... but in the end he fell, "
"pierced by Asheviere’s spears. It is thanks to his sacrifice that Blackwater "
"Port still stands free."
msgstr ""
"Tío Kaylan — <b>Sir</b> Kaylan loitou con valentía... pero ao final caeu, "
"atravesado polas lanzas de Asheviere. É grazas ao seu sacrificio que o Porto "
"Negro segue libre."

#. [message]: speaker=Simyr
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:597
msgid ""
"Alas, this is ill news indeed. A hero’s death, but a death nonetheless. "
"Kaylan had hoped to send some of our number with you on your journey, but "
"with his passing we cannot afford to send the Horsemen and Cavalrymen he had "
"hoped to."
msgstr ""
"Por desgraza, estas son malas noticias. A morte dun heroe, pero unha morte "
"ao fin e ao cabo. Kaylan esperaba enviar algúns dos nosos convosco na vosa "
"viaxe, pero co seu falecemento non podemos permitirnos o luxo de enviar os "
"xinetes e os soldados de cabalería que el esperaba."

#. [message]: speaker=Haldiel
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:601
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Yet with Asheveire’s armies defeated today, surely we can spare at least "
#| "a few of our number? Though it is true that the bulk of our forces must "
#| "remain behind to guard the port, we can still partially fufill Sir "
#| "Kaylan’s last wish, Sir Simyr."
msgid ""
"Yet with Asheviere’s armies defeated today, surely we can spare at least a "
"few of our number? Though it is true that the bulk of our forces must remain "
"behind to guard the port, we can still partially fufill Sir Kaylan’s last "
"wish, Sir Simyr."
msgstr ""
"Con todo, coas tropas de Asheveire derrotadas hoxe, ¿non podemos liberar "
"polo menos a algúns dos nosos? Aínda que é certo que a maior parte das nosas "
"forzas debe quedar para vixiar o porto, aínda podemos cumprir parcialmente o "
"último desexo de Sir Kaylan, Sir Simyr."

#. [message]: speaker=Simyr
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:605
msgid ""
"Very well. Haldiel and I shall join you on your quest, Your Royal Highness."
msgstr ""
"Moi ben. Haldiel e eu uniremosnos a vostede na súa procura, Vosa Real Altura."

#. [message]: speaker=Simyr
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:615
msgid ""
"Alas, this is ill news indeed. A hero’s death, but a death nonetheless. "
"Kaylan had hoped to send some of our number with you on your journey, but "
"with his passing we can no longer afford to. Konrad, you will have to "
"journey on from here with only Peasants and Woodsmen by your side."
msgstr ""
"Por desgraza, estas son malas noticias. A morte dun heroe, pero unha morte "
"ao fin e ao cabo. Kaylan esperaba enviar algúns dos nosos contigo na túa "
"viaxe, pero co seu falecemento xa non podemos permitilo. Konrad, terás que "
"seguir viaxando desde aquí só con Campesiños e Leñadores ao teu carón."

#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:623
msgid ""
"A glorious victory — thank you for your help, compatriots! I must remain "
"here to safeguard the port, but with the false queen’s troops repelled many "
"of my riders are free to accompany you on your quest. Konrad, may they serve "
"you well!"
msgstr ""
"Unha gloriosa vitoria. Grazas pola vosa axuda, compatriotas! Debo permanecer "
"aquí para protexer o porto, pero coas tropas da falsa raíña repelidas, "
"moitos dos meus xinetes son libres para acompañarvos na vosa misión. Konrad, "
"que vos sirvan ben!"

#. [else]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:625
msgid "Konrad can now recruit Cavalrymen and Horsemen!"
msgstr "Konrad agora pode reclutar cabalaríz e xinetes!"

#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:634
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "... and with the invading force so thoroughly defeated, I can afford to "
#| "give you more riders than I had originally planned. I place two of my "
#| "city’s finest warriors in your service."
msgid ""
"... and with the invading force so thoroughly defeated, I can afford to give "
"you more riders than I had originally planned. Haldiel, Simyr, step forward! "
"I place your lances in the service of His Highness here. May you help him "
"restore order to the country."
msgstr ""
"... e coa forza invasora tan completamente derrotada, podo permitirme o luxo "
"de darvos máis xinetes dos que tiña planeado orixinalmente. Poño dous dos "
"mellores guerreiros da miña cidade ao voso servizo."

#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:639
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "... and with the invading force so thoroughly defeated, I can afford to "
#| "give you more riders than I had originally planned. I place two of my "
#| "city’s finest warriors in your service."
msgid ""
"... and with the invading force so thoroughly defeated, I can afford to give "
"you more riders than I had originally planned. Haldiel, step forward! I "
"place your lance in the service of His Highness here. May you help him "
"restore order to the country."
msgstr ""
"... e coa forza invasora tan completamente derrotada, podo permitirme o luxo "
"de darvos máis xinetes dos que tiña planeado orixinalmente. Poño dous dos "
"mellores guerreiros da miña cidade ao voso servizo."

#. [message]: speaker=Haldiel
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:652
msgid "Greetings, young master. I pledge myself to your service."
msgstr "Saúdos, mozo amo. Comprométome ao seu servizo."

#. [message]: speaker=Simyr
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:657
msgid "It is my pleasure and honor to serve, my liege."
msgstr "É un pracer e unha honra servirvos, meu señor."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:676
msgid "I have failed in my duty to protect the rightful heir and the port..."
msgstr "Fallei no meu deber de protexer o herdeiro lexítimo e o porto..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:683
msgid "Kaylan, no! Please, you have to get back up! You have to keep fighting!"
msgstr ""
"Kaylan, non! Por favor, tes que volver levantarte! Tes que seguir loitando!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:690
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "I'm sorry, Konrad. He is lost to us now... Today we mourn a good man..."
msgid "I’m sorry, Konrad. He is lost to us now... Today we mourn a good man..."
msgstr "Síntoo, Konrad. Agora perdémolo... Hoxe choramos a un bo home..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad {KONRAD_VARIATION concerned}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/03_Blackwater_Port.cfg:697
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "He's gone, isn't he... Today we mourn a good man."
msgid "He’s gone, isn’t he... Today we mourn a good man."
msgstr "Xa se foi, non si... Hoxe choramos a un bo home."

#. [message]: speaker=1Mer1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:133
msgid ""
"Are you coming to liberate us? Finally, we stand a chance against the orcs!"
msgstr "Vés liberarnos? Por fin, temos unha oportunidade contra os orcos!"

#. [message]: speaker=4Mer1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:140
msgid "Now that we are free, together we can defeat our oppressors!"
msgstr "Agora que somos libres, xuntos podemos derrotar os nosos opresores!"

#. [message]: speaker=5Mer1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:147
msgid "Let’s take back the Trident the orcs stole from us!"
msgstr "Recuperemos o Tridente que nos roubaron os orcos!"

#. [message]: speaker=6Mer1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:154
msgid ""
"Death to the orcs! Come, my brethren, let us fight the orcs and drive them "
"from our shores!"
msgstr ""
"Morte aos orcos! Acudide a min, meus irmáns, loitemos contra os orcos e "
"botémolos da nosa ribeira!"

#. [message]: speaker=8Mer1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:161
msgid "Thank you for rescuing us! Now we can help you fight the evil orcs!"
msgstr ""
"Grazas por rescatarnos! Agora podemos axudarche a loitar contra os orcos "
"malvados!"

#. [message]: speaker=9Mer1
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:168
msgid "Freedom! Now where are those orcs? Let me at ’em!"
msgstr "Liberdade! Onde están eses orcos? Déixame enganalos!"

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/04_The_Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:277
msgid "scenario name^The Bay of Pearls"
msgstr "A Baía das Perlas"

