#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:427
msgid "Raag!"
msgstr "Raag!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:434
msgid ""
"That orc’s keep will make a perfect staging ground for our attack on the "
"city, Konrad. I’ll move forward and recruit from there once it’s clear. "
"You’re welcome to share, of course."
msgstr ""
"A fortaleza dese orco será unha base perfecta para o noso ataque á cidade, "
"Konrad. Avanzarei e recrutarei desde alí en canto estea despexado. Por "
"suposto, podes compartilo."

#. [event]: id=sapper_ability_object
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1164
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1165
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1166
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1167
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1168
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1169
msgid "Bridge Guard"
msgstr "Guardia do Puente"

