msgstr "Raíña Escura"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dark Queen, gender=female, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Human_Dark_Queen.cfg:27
msgid ""
"The evil Queen Asheviere has terrorized Wesnoth for many years. Her "
"knowledge of magic makes her a worthy foe in combat, although her power is "
"mostly derived from those she commands."
msgstr ""
"A malvada raíña Asheviere leva moitos anos aterrorizando Wesnoth. O seu "
"coñecemento da maxia convértea nunha inimiga digna en combate, aínda que o "
"seu poder provén principalmente daqueles aos que comanda."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Human_Dark_Queen.cfg:32
msgid "scepter"
msgstr "cetro"

#. [attack]: type=blade
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Human_Dark_Queen.cfg:43
msgid "stiletto"
msgstr "estilete"

#. [attack]: type=cold
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Human_Dark_Queen.cfg:58
msgid "raging blizzard"
msgstr "tremenda ventisca"

#. [variation]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Human_Dark_Queen.cfg:141
