#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Human_Konrad_L1.cfg:4
msgid "Fighter"
msgstr "Loitador"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Human_Konrad_L1.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Young and brash, Fighters attack with a sword, and are vulnerable to more "
"seasoned enemies. At this early age, their greatest value is their potential."
msgstr ""
"Novos e imprudentes, os Luchadores atacan cunha espada e son vulnerables a "
"inimigos máis experimentados. A esta idade temperá, o seu maior valor é o "
"seu potencial."

#. [variation]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Human_Konrad_L1.cfg:87
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Human_Konrad_L2.cfg:128
