#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/specials_and_abilities.cfg:277
msgid ""
"Masterfully crafted by Weldyn smiths, then magically duplicated and enhanced "
"by Delfador, this armor grants Konrad +40% resistance to all damage."
msgstr ""
"Maxistralmente elaborada polos ferreiros de Weldyn, e logo duplicada e "
"mellorada maxicamente por Delfador, esta armadura outorga a Konrad +40% r de "
"resistencia a todos os danos."

