#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:788
msgid "We are vanquished, for I have been defeated!"
msgstr "Estamos vencidos, pois fun derrotado!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:789
msgid "This is the end! Without me, who will guide the prince?"
msgstr "Isto é o fin! Sen min, quen guiará o príncipe?"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:790
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:791
msgid "Fight on without me, friends! The Light shall always prevail!"
msgstr "Loitade sen min, amigos! A Luz sempre prevalecerá!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:792
msgid "Ah’m not wounded! Jus’ need a moment... ta catch my breath..."
msgstr "Non estou ferido! Só preciso un momento... para recuperar o alento..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:793
msgid "Well, this is a new experience..."
msgstr "Ben, isto é unha nova experiencia..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:794
msgid "Harper! No!"
msgstr "Harper, non!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:794
msgid "Unngh... Sorry Baldras..."
msgstr "Unngh... Desculpa Baldras..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:795
msgid "Ack! I tried my best..."
msgstr "Ai! Intentei o meu mellor..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:795
msgid "Somf! No!"
msgstr "Somf! Non!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:796
msgid "Chantal! A dark shadow falls upon my soul..."
msgstr "Chantal! Unha sombra escura cae sobre a miña alma..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:796
msgid "—Oh!"
msgstr "—Oh!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:797
msgid "Dosh don’ feel so good..."
msgstr "Dosh non se sente tan ben..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:798
msgid "Krawww..."
msgstr "Que rabia..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:800
msgid "Send word of my fall to Sir Kaylan, Konrad! I fought my best..."
msgstr ""
"Envíalle a noticia da miña caída a Sir Kaylan, Konrad! Loitei o mellor que "
"puiden..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:801
msgid ""
"Tell Sir Kaylan of my demise, Konrad... I have served you as best I could..."
msgstr ""
"Cóntalle a Sir Kaylan o meu falecemento, Konrad... Servinte o mellor que "
"puiden..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:802
msgid "Oh... I suppose I deserve this..."
msgstr "Oh... supoño que merezo isto..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:803
msgid "Ow!"
msgstr "Ai!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:804
msgid "Jotha regrets nothing..."
msgstr "Jotha non se arrepinte de nada..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:805
msgid "Bury me back home in the Dulatus..."
msgstr "Enterráme na casa, no Dulatus..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:809
msgid "At least I die an honorable death..."
msgstr "Polo menos morro unha morte honorable..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:811
msgid "Gah! At least I die a death worthy of the Horse Lords of old..."
msgstr ""
"Buf! Polo menos morro dunha morte digna dos Señores Cabalos de antano..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:812
msgid "Argh! I may fall, but the Clans shall always endure!"
msgstr "Argh! Eu podo caer, pero os Clans sempre perdurarán!"

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:813
msgid "Ack! Bury me under the Horse Plains..."
msgstr "Ai! Entérrame baixo as Chairas dos Cabalos..."

#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:814
msgid "Bah! Tell the Clans I died fighting..."
msgstr "Bah! Dille aos clans que morrín loitando..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galdrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:822
msgid "I have met my match..."
msgstr "Atopei a miña parella..."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:828
msgid ""
"Tie him up and bind his wounds. The queen will want to make an example of "
"this one."
msgstr "Átalo e venda as súas feridas. A raíña querrá facer deste un exemplo."

#. [message]: speaker=Ethiliel
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:838
msgid "I have given all in defense of my home..."
msgstr "Dei todo na defensa do meu fogar..."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:844
msgid "Bind her arms and wings! The queen wants their leaders taken alive."
msgstr ""
"Atadelle os brazos e as ás! A raíña quere que os seus líderes sexan "
"capturados vivos."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:858
msgid ""
"Argh! I am nearly finished! But if I were to die here, my people would be "
"left leaderless."
msgstr ""
"Argh! Case rematei! Pero se eu morrese aquí, a miña xente quedaría sen líder."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:862
msgid ""
"I have aided you in what ways I could, Konrad. Now I must leave your party, "
"and retreat eastwards to Lintanir Forest. May we someday meet again there."
msgstr ""
"Axudeiche no que puiden, Konrad. Agora debo deixar o teu grupo e retirarme "
"cara ao leste, ao bosque de Lintanir. Oxalá algún día nos volvamos atopar "
"alí."

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar {LISAR_VARIATION defeat}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:880
msgid "I can’t believe it should end like this!"
msgstr "Non podo crer que remate así!"

#. [message]: speaker=Warven
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:894
msgid "At least I die alongside my princess..."
msgstr "Polo menos morro xunto á miña princesa..."

#. [objective]: condition=lose
