#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/utils/unified_characters.cfg:934
msgid "Death of Konrad, Delfador, or Li’sar"
msgstr "Morte de Konrad, Delfador ou Li'sar"

